\id MAT - Sanga Language Project (xns)
\h Matiyu
\toc3 Mat
\toc2 Mat
\toc1 Matiyu
\mt1 Matiyu
\imt2 Oroka o lebo aa surea
\imt1 Matiyu
\imt1 Masanto
\im Ondooka wa wele angmǝ aa lebo aana waya Matiyu, wai o Yahuda wai, ondo aa nyimi atoma a Yeso.
\ip \bk Angmǝ lebo aaka Matiyu wa wele\bk* Wa wore ro na Yeso kaya Almasipu kanname, kamea kaya orona o pena otono ooka Ashili aye aromo a ai Otono oo Kozo. Kaya kamea maYahuda ne eke lenyong oo bena kaya deya. Ewela eena e tikǝrǝ ekoro mawo ma Ashili aa nyimi Otono o Kozo adorana a wore nangka Yeso ka panza e. Ewela me ee kang wore obena Yeso karomo ka akora Ibraheng kai. Kangza ka rare Yeso na “Kena ka Daoda”. Obena Yeso ka de aa bengmǝ be Almasipu naname, aa kap nangka maYahuda ne eke lenyong a Ashili. Ewela eena e wore na Yeso ondo baala ogong ooka o baala ka angmǝ a kai ne wore o bena kaye ka o bare maleo o kala o Mosa.
\ip Aa nyimi ewela eena, a tareze o baala o Yeso aa madǝkǝni esu nanna: O bora, o zoola azaa oyara, omea wa wore nangka wa gwara aromo Ashili cikǝ (masono 5-7). O Leere kangza, nangka otoma Almasipu yo eza ogole o wai (osono 10). O taaro, angmǝ aa gerpo zene azaa togomo te Ashili (osono 13). O naaze, o baala azaa ombela o cikǝ ondo o tare Ashili yo eza (osono 18). O esu, o baala azaa o maro awere aana kaa o deya togomo te Ashili (masono 24-25). O maare, Matiyu wa wore letoma lee gong ka Yeso ka nya, azaa o zoola azaa orooka oo lebo.
\iot Beyo be epa eeka eya nyimi
\io1 Beting kaa o ngemengha Yeso Kiristi 1:1-2:23
\io1 Ozoola o Yohana o batisma 3:1-12
\io1 O batisma ka o kedeya Yeso 3:13-4:11
\io1 Ogole o Yeso a nyimi makeke ma Galili 4:12-18:35
\io1 O kurǝ a Galili aa alea Urshalima 19:1-20:34
\io1 Ogole o Yeso o maare Urshalima 21:1-27:66
\io1 O gendare o Yeso kaa o gbwǝ o kai 27:32-66
\io1 O era aa malo gwǝ kaa o wore o kpwai kai 28:1-20
\c 1
\s1 Abuudu a Yeso
\r (Luk 3:23-38)
\p 
\v 1 Enna ewela azaa beting be Yeso Kiristi, kena ka Daoda, kena ka Ibraheng.
\li1 
\v 2 Ibraheng ate a Ishaku,
\li2 Ishaku ate a Yakubu, a Yakubu ate a Yahuda kaa arone awai alome.
\li1 
\v 3 Yahuda ate a Perez kaa Zera andaaka iini onea waye Tamar,
\li1 Perez ate a Hezron,
\li1 a Hezron ate a Aram.
\li1 
\v 4 Aram ate a Aminadab,
\li3 Aminadab ate a Nashon, aa Nashon ate a Salmon.
\li1 
\v 5 Salmon ate a Bowaza ka iini wai waye Rahab.
\li1 Bowaza ate a Obed ka iini wai waye Rut,
\li1 Obed ate a Yese,
\li1 
\v 6 a Yese ate a Ogomo Daoda.
\li1 Daoda ate a Suleimanu ka iini wai waye Batsheba, ondaye Uriya o samba.
\li1 
\v 7 Suleimanu ate a Rehobowam,
\li1 Rehobowam ate a Abija, Abija ate a Asa,
\v 8 Asa ate a Yehoshapat, Yehoshapat ate a Yehoram,
\li1 Yehoram ate a Uziya,
\li1 
\v 9 Uziya ate a Yotam,
\li1 Yotam ate a Ahaz,
\li1 Ahaz ate a Hezekiya,
\li1 
\v 10 Hezekiya ate a Manase,
\li1 Manase ate a Amon, Amon ate a Yosiya,
\li1 
\v 11 aa Yosiya ate a Yekoniya ka arone awai, a were aka a bese maYahuda a ale a lezara a Babila.
\li4 
\v 12 Malo besa one a lezara a Babila,
\li1 Yekoniya ate a Sheyaltiyel, Sheyaltiyel ate a Zerubabel,
\li1 
\v 13 Zerubabel ate a Abihud,
\li1 Abihud ate a Eliyakim, Eliyakim ate a Azor,
\v 14 Azor ate a Zadok,
\li1 Zadok ate a Akim,
\li1 Akim ate a Aliyud,
\li1 
\v 15 Aliyud ate a Eleyazar,
\li1 Eleyazar ate a Mattan,
\li1 Mattan ate a Yakubu,
\li1 
\v 16 aa Yakubu ate a Yusupu ondaleme Mariya, Mariya kamea ka ngmeng Yeso ka a beya kai na Kiristi.
\p 
\v 17 Obena pate sepeza a era Ibraheng a alea Daoda, sepeza betuurua ka she naaze. O era Daoda a alea awere amea a bese maYahuda a alea lezara a Babila, sepeza betuurua ka she naaze, o era were lezara a Babila kangza a ale o ngmenga Kiristi, sepeza betuurua ka she naaze.
\s1 Ongmenga o Yeso Kiristi
\r (Luk 2:1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Nannaa ongmenga o Yeso Kiristi waze. Awere aka Yusupu waya caasa Mariya kamea ka ngmeng Yeso, zongka wa ana kai, na manaa ka ana etumǝ a surǝ a Obere Ashili.
\v 19 Yusupu ondasau kai waye ka boome ba Ashili na wata yeme o kare okai ezǝng a nyimi aromone, nawa eze madoola ma baya kai a suk.
\v 20 Nangka waya madoola ma nyimi, na otoma Ashili o dera lepung o Ateokora deya awai atolau. Awa bena, “Yusupu kena ka Daoda, tana okone boome bo ana Mariya ka ka itǝ ondaye one, obena etumǝ ka ka ana, e surea Obere Ashilia.
\v 21 Kayo ngmenga kena ka lome, oyo nya kai leze na Yeso, o bena kayo boza aromo aza madinǝ mane.”
\p 
\v 22 A eze pate nyimia adorana angmǝ Ateokora pene ka Ondo beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Ishaya beke.
\v 23 “Laka! Kagala yo ya etumǝ, ka ka ngmeng kena kalome, ka ayo nya kai leze na Emanuwel, o wore obena Ashili ya legwa ka ro.”\x - \xo 1:23 \xt Ish 7:14. \x*
\p 
\v 24 Nangka Yusupu wa ere atolau, nawa tare epaaka otoma Ashili o dera lepung me wa ote wai na waye, aa wa ana Mariya naka itǝ ondaye wai.
\v 25 Pate ka nyimi, wata wa more ka kai ne, se malo ngmenga kena ka kai. Nawa nya kena kame leze na Yeso.
\c 2
\s1 Begere be ana orosa kane surǝa dizi
\p 
\v 1 Malo ngmenga Yeso a Baitalami o makeke ma Yahudiya, awere togomo te Hiridus ogomo Ogong, ana orosa ne surea adizi nane deya a Urushalima ane pirkǝ na,
\v 2 “Ondooka a ngmeng, ogomo ma Yahuda ya babaa? Te laka bewerewere be wai a dizi na te deya kate eze kai makili ma Ashili.”
\p 
\v 3 Nangka Ogomo Hiridus wa kone nyimi nawa kone oburǝ ka apate aromo a Urushalima.
\v 4 Nawa kurki pate andaamoole magame ma Ashili ka ana obaala angmǝ aka Ashili a nya Mosa, awa pirkǝ ne na, a ruwǝme abena aya ngmenga Kiristi?
\v 5 Nane kabare wai na, “Apeng Betalami a makeke ma Yahudiya,” Ane kang bena, “Nyimia ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wa wele,
\q1 
\v 6 “‘Bo Betalami o makeke ma Yahudiya
\q2 ota baate ne a nyimi makeke ma togomo ma Yahudiya,
\q1 ka ogomo yo surǝa nyimi au ka waya eza togomo
\q2 azaa aromo ang maIsrela.’\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Mek 5:2.\x*”’
\p 
\v 7 Na Hiridus rare ana orosa name asuk adorana wa rose awere aka bewerewere beme be suri.
\v 8 Nawa tong ne a Betalami na, “Ale na ka esoole kena kame a dede. Eedate ka ecǝ kai, deyana ka ebeleng, adorana mima ang ale kang eze makili ma Ashili a begeshe be kai.”
\p 
\v 9 Malooka ne mara okona angmǝ ogomo, nane lya izi ka teweno tene, a bewerewere beeka be surǝ ane obora kale ane ba izi a ale araaka kena kame zane.
\v 10 Nangka ne laka bewerewere beme, nane pene ka okona oleba maleu.
\v 11 Ko lyǝ a kwilǝ me ane laka kena kame ka iini kai Mariya, nane girwǝ aa ne eze kai makili ma Ashili. Zaa nyimi nane pǝri majeketa ma emate mane ane nya kai magogoro, mazenare, madangku ma lubban kaa ma omur.
\v 12 Aza obena Obere Ashili wa windi ne toto a nyimi tolau na tana ne kuri ara Hiridus ne, nane tare orona yende a kurǝ a makeke mane.
\s1 O alea wogo a Masar
\p 
\v 13 Malooka ana orosa me ne ale, otoma Ashili o dera lepung wa suri a Yusupu a tolau. Awa bekaana, “Era o ana kena kame ka iini kai o alea wogo a Masar. Oo cikǝ a saname seena ba kone eyapa mi, aza obena Hiridus ya gera kena kame kawa wong kai.”
\p 
\v 14 Na Yusupu ere a lelyaare leme, nawa ana kena kame ka iini kai a alea Masar,
\v 15 arakanamea ne cikǝ ne a ale ogwǝ o Hiridus. Nyimi apanza angmǝ Ashili ka a beke o ngmǝ otoma ai o lepung na, “Ma rare kena kang ka ka suri a Masar.”\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Hos 11:1.\x*
\s1 O wongha a bana ayana a Masar
\p 
\v 16 Nangka Hiridus wa laka obena ana orosa ne kala wai a izi, na o nyong caro wai maleu. Nawa ote na a wongze pate ayana a batebate alome ka neya Betalami ka oringǝri o ai, aa deya senai se leere aa jǝpi, a akap nangka ne kone ara ana orosa name.
\v 17 Awere namea angmǝ Ashili ka Irimiya beke a pena na,
\q1 
\v 18 “A kona lengmelo a Rama,
\q2 lengmelo le okona oburǝ ka oruuzi a jǝng,
\q1 Rahila ya ruuzi azaa ayana kai
\q2 aka nyana kona okoo ogwǝ,
\q2 aza obena a wongza ne.”\x - \xo 2:18 \xt Irim 31:15.\x*
\s1 O surǝ a Masar a ale a Nazarat
\p 
\v 19 Malooka Hiridus wa gbwi, na otoma Ashili o dera lepung deya a Yusupu a nyimi tolau a Masar
\v 20 awa bekaana, “Era, ka o ana kena ka iini kai o ale a makeke ma Isrela, andaaka neya yeme o wongnga kena kame ne gbwizǝ.”
\p 
\v 21 Nawa ere, aa wa ana kena kame ka iini kai aa wa ale a makeke ma Isrela.
\v 22 Nangka wa kone obena oyana o Hiridus, Arkilayus wa zala togomo a bengmǝ ba ate wai, nawa kone boome bo ale a saname. Azaa obena a windi wai teto a nyimi tolau, nawa dare awa ale a makeke ma Galili,
\v 23 Wa ale nawa cikǝ a kapeng ka yende ka a rareze kai na Nazarat. Adorana apanza angmǝ Ashili ka ana obeya a ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili ne beke, “Ayo rara kai karomo ka Nazarat.”
\c 3
\s1 Ozoola o Yohana o batisma
\r (Mar 1:1-8; Luk 3:1-18; Yoh 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 A nyimi tomore tonname a Yohana o batisma wa suri awa ya zoola a nyimi wake o makeke ma Yahudiya,
\v 2 aa wa beyana, “Kurǝ na Ashili, obena togomo te shili te amara\f + \fr 3:2 \fq togomo te shili te amara \ft Anna wore obena togomo teeka Ashili ya ezaa me azaa aromo. \f*.”
\v 3 Ondoonaa Ishaya ondo beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wa beke angmǝ azaa wai na:
\q1 “Lengmelo ya rara owake ale beya na,
\q2 ‘Babara Ateokora orona,
\q2 babara na marona ma wai.’ ”
\p 
\v 4 A soo madibi ma Yohana ka sezǝru se orongkoomea, awa tera o tinǝ owai ka lejǝng le ongma. A epaolya wai eya ekangdang ka mato ma esheng.
\v 5 Na aromo a Urushalima, kaa a makeke ma Yahudiya a pate, kaa a pate ana makeke ma Obeno Urdung ne deese ara a kai,
\v 6 ane beeze madinǝ mane, aa wa ezene obatisma Obeno Urdung.
\p 
\v 7 Pate ka nyimi nangka Yohana wa laka maParisa ka maSadukiya araaka waya eza aromo obatisma, nawa bekaa ne na, “Ying okurkǝnǝng ewa eburu! Mana wa zoola aying na esong o gǝǝzǝ o Ashili ka waya deya?
\v 8 Ezana epaaka eyo ale akap ka ewore obena e kurǝ Ashili aying.
\v 9 Kangza tane ole begeshe na, ‘Ibraheng waya ate aro ne.’ Ang bele ying na, Ashili aye ka obare o sǝǝrǝ Ibraheng ayana a nyimi a caleena.
\v 10 A samba o eke betemo aa madǝrǝ ma o mati, kangza pate uti ka wata ngmengza ayana a rerene, ayo genda wai ka tare a nyimi ola.
\p 
\v 11 “Mi ang ezeze ying o batisma ka manyia o wore o kurǝ a Ashili aying. Malo ong ondo ya deya kawa kalang o bare, tekakau te wai ma era anta bare ang monte ne. Wayo eza ying o batisma ka Obere Ashili ka ola.
\v 12 Waya onta upkwi owai a taara, aa wa keleke epaolya wai, aa wa kare o eyo me a nyimi lebengga, aa wa ese masuni mame ka ola ka wata lambuzu ne.”
\s1 A eze Yeso obatisma
\r (Mar 1:9-11; Luk 3:21-23)
\p 
\v 13 A were name na Yeso deya ka suri a Galili a ale a Urdung ara Yohana adorana wa eze kai o batisma.
\v 14 Na Yohana yeme o nara kai, awa bekaana, “Mi ang gwara obekaana bo oyeng o batisma, eyaaka bo ba deya ara ang?”
\p 
\v 15 Na Yeso kabare wai na, “Baya wa itǝ nyimi nanname, aza obena nyimi a kala orera ka te panza epa e sangsang eeka Ashili ya yeme me.” Na Yohana kabare, aa wa ye kai o batisma.
\p 
\v 16 Malo o eza Yeso o batisma, ka osurǝ kai a nyimi manyi naname, a saseya na zaa shili banggalanu, aka laka Obere o Ashili a jǝpi na kagoma, aka jǝpi ukpwei kai.
\v 17 Na kone lengmelo a surǝ zaa shili na, “Kannaa kena kang, kamea ang yeme, kamea ang kone oleba kai maleu.”\x - \xo 3:17 \xt Obo 22:2; Sel 2:7; Ish 42:1; Mat 12:18; 17:5; Mar 1:11; Luk 9:35. \x*
\c 4
\s1 O kedeya Yeso
\r (Mar 1:12-13; Luk 4:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Na Obere Ashili tare kaa Yeso a ale owake ka ogomo o bere o buru kedeya kai.
\v 2 Aka meke ongmǝ o tomore tuuru naaze, lelyaare ka letereme, na ekomo meke kai.
\v 3 Na ogomo obere o buru deya kai awa bekaana, “Boa baaya Kena ka Ashili, ote lecale leena ka le itǝ oborode.”
\p 
\v 4 Na Yeso kabare na, “Angmǝ Ashili a bekaana, “Epaolya belle ta ongtaza oromo ne, seena ka koonang angmǝ ka susi ongmǝ Ashili.”\x - \xo 4:4 \xt Otik 8:3.\x*
\p 
\v 5 Na ogomo o bere oburu, ale ka kai a Urushalima apeng a odera madinǝ, nawa zalara kai araa o kala bezaati a akwilǝ Ashili.
\v 6 Na wa bena, “Bo kena ka Ashili kaaza, cangko ka otaru a deze, obena a wele na,
\q1 ‘Wayo ote atoma wai a kazo o,
\q2 kane woboo ka taara tene
\q2 nangka oto jukǝ tobona to ocale ne.”\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Sel 91:11-12.\x*
\p 
\v 7 Na Yeso kabare wai na, “A wele na, ‘Tana okedeya Ateokora Ashili au ne.’ ”\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Otik 6:16.\x*
\p 
\v 8 Kangza na ogomo obere oburu ale ka kai oyara o zaati awa wore kai pate togomo te lerambo leena ka o gongha te.
\v 9 Awa kang bena, “Pate tenna eyang nyau, ba girwǝ a begeshe beng o ezeng makili ma Ashili.”
\p 
\v 10 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Era arakaana, Shetan! A wele na, ‘Eza Ashili Ateokora au makili ma ai, kangza aiya belle oyo saba.’ ”\x - \xo 4:10 \xt Otik 6:13.\x*
\p 
\v 11 Na ogomo obere o buru ale awa baya kai, na atoma Ashili o dera lepung de nane kangkama kai.
\s1 Obora ogole o Yeso aa Galili
\r (Mar 1:14-15; Luk 4:14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Nangka Yeso ka kone obena a meke Yohana na apate akwilǝ andaleme, naka ere naka ale a Galili.
\v 13 Ko baya Nazarat, naka ale a Kaparnahum ka ocikǝ, apeng amea aya bengmǝ bo beno, a bekazo be makeke ma Zebulung ka Naptali,
\v 14 adorana a panza epaaka ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Ishaya wa beke,
\q1 
\v 15 “A makeke ma Zebulung ka ma Naptali,
\q2 orona o alea obeno ogong a alea bekazo be obeno Urdung,
\q2 a makeke ma Galili araaka a worme acake cikǝ ne,
\q1 
\v 16 aromo kane cikǝ amaring,
\q2 ne laka masanto ma gong,
\q1 ana ocikǝ makeke ma o ululu o gbwǝ kangza\x - \xo 4:16 \xt Ish 9:1-2.\x*,
\q2 masanto ma tara ane.”
\p 
\v 17 O era were name, na Yeso bore ozoola aka beyaana, “Kurǝ na Ashili aza obena togomo te shili te amara.”
\s1 Yeso ka rare atoma kai o bora
\r (Mar 1:16-20; Luk 5:1-11)
\q1 
\v 18 Yeso kaya yenga edǝki o beno gong o Galili naname, naka laka arone a leere, Siman ka a rare wai na Biturusu ka orone owai Andarawus. Neya tara majara ma o meese ekwala obeno, obena ogole one o meese ekwala waze.
\v 19 Na Yeso bekaane na, “Deyana ka etareng, eyang ote ying ka e itǝ ana o deesa ka aromo a mi.”
\v 20 A saseya nane baya majara mane aa ne tare kai.
\p 
\v 21 Ko lya izi a baate, naka laka arone leere kangza, Yakubu kena ka Zabadi, ka orone kai Yohana. Neya nyimi o onggo o manyi ka ate ane Zabadi, aneya babara majara mane ma o meese ekwala. Na Yeso rare ne.
\v 22 A saseya nane baya o onggo o manyi mame ka ate ane, aa ne tare kai.
\s1 Yeso ka womza ana makono
\r (Luk 6:17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Yeso ka ringgari pate makeke ma Galili, aka baale a nyimi odandaro o gwarzanang maYahuda, aka zoole aa ne aza angmǝ a lebo a togomo te Ashili. Kangza aaka womza pate makono ka odera o kona zake ka aromo ya zitǝ ka mai.
\v 24 Na orooka azaa kai ale a kurǝwǝ a nyimi makeke ma Suriya pate. Na aromo casa kai pate andaaka neya kono ka andaaka neya zitǝ ka kombela makono, ka ana o kona o poba a jǝng, andaaka obere o buru wa taba ne, ana letaranggi, andaaka apung ane aa gbwǝ a sara yende, pate naka womza ne.
\v 25 Na aromo a cake ne tare kai, kane suri a Galili, ka ana o surǝ a Dekapolis\f + \fr 4:25 \fq Dekapolis \ft Onnaa topepeng betuuru.\f*, ka Urushalima, ka makeke ma Yahudiya, a ale cakate obeno Urdung.
\c 5
\s1 O zoola ka Yeso ka eze azaa oyara
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka laka aromo ane kurkǝnǝng, naka zale oyara aa ka cikǝ a saname. Na atoma kai deya kai,
\v 2 aka bore o baala one na.
\s1 O wala o kona oleba
\q1 
\v 3 “Ana okona olebaa aromo aaka ne rose o sawa one a nyimi o tare Ashili,
\q2 aza o bena togomo te shili taate nea te.
\q1 
\v 4 Ana okona oleba ana o caro anyong,
\q2 ayo nata ne anyong.
\q1 
\v 5 Ana okona olebaa ana o nata ukpwei,
\q2 lerambo leena yo itǝ lalene.
\q1 
\v 6 Ana okona olebaa andaaka neya kona ekomo ka lewe le cikǝ o sangsang,
\q2 obena neyo tiyǝ.
\q1 
\v 7 Ana okona olebaa andaaka ne kone egonegone,
\q2 ayo wore ne egonegone.
\q1 
\v 8 Ana okona olebaa andaaka neya sangsang a nyimia nyong,
\q2 obena neyo laka Ashili.
\q1 
\v 9 Ana okona olebaa andaaka ne gere o cikǝ o cammo,
\q2 obena ayo rara ne na ayana Ashili.
\q1 
\v 10 Ana okona olebaa andaaka a nyana ne azaa be sangsang bene,
\q2 obena togomo te shili taa tene te.
\p 
\v 11 Ana okona olebaa ying awere aka aromo ne eske ying, ane nyalang ka ying ane kang beya kombela rendaza ma buru aza oying, obena ying e tareng.
\v 12 Konana oleba e zante ajǝng, o bena bengmǝ bee ying yo gongha aa cak azaa shili, nyimia aromome ne gǝǝzǝ ana obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili kane kaana ying.”
\s1 O baala azaa ogalu ka masanto
\r (Mar 9:50; Luk 14:34-35)
\p 
\v 13 Yingnga ogalu makeke maana. A ogalu wa arnang ka olento owai, eya ayo ya ka wa kang olento? Wa itǝ wata kang ya ka edang ne, soona a oke wai a itǝzǝ ne.
\p 
\v 14 Yingnga masanto ma lerambo. Apeng aka a sowa ai azaa ka zalo, a era ta baasa ne.\x - \xo 5:14 \xt Yoh 8:12; 9:5.\x*
\v 15 Nyimi a aromo ne era neta diki beru be masanto aa ne pate be ka oso ne. Seena eke be ara azaati o eese be, nangka beyo nya pate aromo akwilǝ me masanto.
\v 16 Nyimi a kangza bayana ee itǝ ana masanto a aromo, adorana nee laka teweno teying te rere ka eya ezame, aa ne sabe Ate aying ooka waya nyimi azaa shili.
\s1 O baala azaa makili
\p 
\v 17 Tane laka na ma deya kang dinggi makili ma Mosa ka ewela ana obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili. Anta ma deya kang dinggi ne soona ang panza mai.
\v 18 Eyang dongdong bele oying, azaa shili ka makeke maana yo maro, otengke o baate ewela makili ma Mosa wato maro ne, seeka a panza ekeeya apat.
\v 19 A zaa nyimi pate ondooka wa cakate o yende o kala a bebaate a nyimi makili ma Ashili maana, aa wa baale ana ondo na neye nyimi, ayo beka ondo me na wa kala be baate a nyimia togomo te o zaa shili. Ondooka wa tare mai kangza aa wa baale ana ondo o tare o mai, ayo rara wai na ondo ogong a togomo te shili.
\v 20 Eyang baalo ying eta kala ana obaala angmǝ ka Ashili anya Mosa ka maParisa aa eza epa e sangsang ne, eto lyǝ a togomo te ozaa shili ne.
\s1 O baala azaa lemunggi
\r (Luk 12:57-59)
\p 
\v 21 “E kone obena a beka aromo ko rabo na, ‘Tano wong ondo ne, pate ondooka wa wongngha ondo, ayo gǝǝzǝ wai.’
\v 22 Mi eyang bele oying, ondooka wa munggi ka arone wai, ayo gǝǝzǝ wai. Ondooka wa rare arone wai na, eta ka edang ne, ayo ale ka wai ara o cora angmǝ. Komana kangza wa rare arone wai na, eta ka edang ne, wa itǝ kap ka akwilǝ ola.
\p 
\v 23 “Nyimia kangza, baya nya Ashili eyapa a nyimi akwilǝ ai ara o esaza Ashili mapapa ma owaze, o ringtǝ o bena arone au neye ka bo a lenyong,
\v 24 baya epaaka oya nya Ashili a ting ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mo waze. Bora ka o ale ka o babare kane, o ama o de ka onya Ashili epaaka baaya nyame.
\p 
\v 25 Ondo wa ale ka bo ara o cora angmǝ, yangkanna a saseya ka ebabare ka wai e tata o orona o ale zongka e dukǝ. Bata ya nyimi ne, wayo gwaarau ka ondoo cora angmǝ, aa ondoo cora angmǝ kangza wayo gwaarau ka ana o tesa geza ka a pateo a akwilǝ andaleme.
\v 26 Ang dongdong bele o epeng, zongka o sǝǝrǝu arakaname, seena ba are pate emate eeka ataro.
\s1 O baala azaa leyau
\p 
\v 27 “Ba kone a bekaana, ‘Tana o eze leyau ne.\x - \xo 5:27 \xt Osur 20:14; Otik 5:18. \x*’
\v 28 Eyang beya ying na, pate ondooka wa gonta ondaaye, kawa kone o eza leyau ka wai, wa samba o eza me ka wai naname a nyimi lenyong le wai.
\v 29 Liizi le oree leo leeyo ote ka o rizi, lopa le ka o pere. Mara o dere sara yende a lepung leo ko bena a tare pate lepung leo a nyimi akwilǝ ola.
\v 30 O ara oree wa ote ka o rizi, core wai ka o pere. Mara o dere sara yende a lepung leo ko bena a tare pate lepung leo a nyimi akwilǝ ola.
\s1 O baala azaa opere ondaaye
\r (Mat 19:9; Mar 10:11-12; Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 31 “Akang samba obena, ‘Ondooka wa pere ondaaye wai, awa dongdong nya wai ewela o pere o awai.
\v 32 Aa maa bekaa ying na pate ondooka wa pere ondaaye wai, aa wata wa meke wai ka leyau ne, wa ote wai orona o leyau naname, kangza pate ondooka wa ana wai, wa eza leyau naname.
\s1 O baala azaa otono
\p 
\v 33 “Kangza, ekone a samba o bekea aromo ko rabo na, ‘Tana o tono a rendaza ne, o eze epaaka ba tono ne aa begeshe Ateokora.’\x - \xo 5:33 \xt Mag 19:12; Abal 30:2; Otik 23:21.\x*
\v 34 Mi eyang beya yingna, tana e tono dakememe ne, ka azaa shili, obena arakanamea lǝdǝngdǝ le Ashili zene,
\v 35 nyimia tane tono ka adeze ne, arakaname Ashili eeshe tobona te ai ne, koona ka Urushalima obena aya apeng ogomo ogong.
\v 36 Kangza tana otono ka ukpwei o ne, azaa obena ba era ota ote lepkwai le yende kale itǝ leepeng koona leebo ne.
\v 37 Pate epaaka wa gwara o beke belle eya ‘Eeye’ koona ‘Aa,’ eyapa e kala nyimi, e surea ara ondoo burua.
\s1 O baala azaa otaasa
\r (Luk 6:29-30)
\p 
\v 38 “E kone a samba o bekaa me na, ‘Liizi a bengmǝ be liizi, a liini a bengmǝ be liini.’\x - \xo 5:38 \xt Osur 21:24; Mag 24:20; Otik 19:21.\x*
\v 39 Na mi eyang beya ying na, tana enyane ondoo eza oying epa eburu ne. Ondo wa tabau a letamo lo ore wanggare wai lo guri kawa tabe kangza.
\v 40 Ondo wa ale ka bo ara o cora angmǝ ka wa jeke odibi o, nya wai ulǝ o urnǝzǝ o kangza.
\v 41 A ondo wa oteu na o eze teweno te omele yende, o ale ka wai o mamele maleere.
\v 42 Ondo wa bosa eyapa abo, o nya wai. Ondo kangza wa deya aa kope eyapa abo, tana o nare wai ne.
\s1 Oyeme ana onyana o
\r (Luk 6:27-28,32-36)
\p 
\v 43 “E kone a samba o bekaa na, ‘Yeme ondooka waya ating o, o nyane ondooka wata yeme oo ne.’\x - \xo 5:43 \xt Mag 19:18.\x*
\v 44 A mi eyang beya aying na, yeme na ana o nyana oying e bosazana Ashili azaa andaaka ne gǝǝzǝ ying,
\v 45 adorana e itǝ ayana Ate aying o zaa shili. Ondooka wa oteze ongme ka wa ye masanto ara ana edang kaa ana o dera edang, awa kang deesa ka olyi ara ana nyong a sangsang ka ana nyong a buru.
\v 46 Ba yeme ana o yeme owa belle, aya taasa o ka eya? Ana o eesa emate makeke kaa ana madinǝ, nyimia ne ezeze.
\v 47 Ba beeza aromo au okoo belle, eya o ezeze erere ke kala ena ondo? Andaame maYahuda taza ne nyimia ne ezeze.
\v 48 Azaa nyimi, itǝ na ana edang nangka Ate aying o zaa shili waye ka edang.
\c 6
\s1 O baala azaa o nyaza
\p 
\v 1 “Ezana a sauwo tana ogole oying orere wa itǝ ogongta a yizi ne. Azaa obena e eza nyimi, eto cǝ o taasa o woma araa Ate aying o zaa shili ne.
\p 
\v 2 “Nyimia baaya nya ana odera, tana o ara lengmelo ajǝng ka komana kone ne, ana o ara ukpwei ezeze nyimi odandaro o gwarzanang maYahuda ka azaa marona adora aromo sabe ne. Eyang dongdong bele oying, ne samba ocǝ o taasa o woma one pat.
\v 3 Aa bayaa nya ondo odera eyapa, tana o baya o ara oguri wa rose epaaka o ara ore ya eza me ne,
\v 4 adorana nyaza oying itǝ epa esuk. Arakaname Ate aying, ka wa gongte epaaka aya ezaa me aa asuk, wayo taasau akap.
\s1 O baala azaa o beya angmǝ ka Ashili
\r (Luk 11:2-4)
\p 
\v 5 “Aa baaya beya angmǝ ka Ashili, tana oye na ana o ara ukpwei ne, ne yeme o beya angmǝ ka Ashili a itǝ a madandaro ma ogwarzanang maYahuda ka edǝki marona ka aromo laka ne. Eyang dongdong bele oying epeng, ne samba o emba o taasa one a pat.\x - \xo 6:5 \xt Luk 18:10-14.\x*
\v 6 Nyimia waaza, baya beya angmǝ ka Ashili, ale a nyimi odo o, pate abuudu me o beye angmǝ ka Ate au aaka ata gonta ai ne, aa Ate au ka agonte pate epaaka a eze a suk, ayo taasau.
\p 
\v 7 “A eeya beya angmǝ ka Ashili, tana wa eweo na aworme ka neta rosa Ashili ne, andaame neya gonta na ne beya angmǝ a ewo waya yo ote ka kone ne.
\v 8 Tane itǝ na nee ne, Ate ying rosa epaaka e gwara ka ying zongka e pirkǝ ai.
\p 
\v 9 E beya angmǝ ka Ashili nanna,
\q1 “Ate aro ozaa shili,
\q1 a monte leze leo a sangsang.
\q1 
\v 10 A togomo to de,
\q1 aa eze epaaka oya yeme me
\q2 a lerambo leena,
\q2 nangka ezeze azaa shili.
\q1 
\v 11 Nyaro epaolya o ngmeengme.
\q1 
\v 12 O pisi ro madinǝ maro,
\q2 nangka te pisizi andaaka ne ezeze ro madinǝ.
\q1 
\v 13 Tana o ale kaaro ara o kedeya ne,
\q2 o wobe ro a taara te ogomo o bere o buru ona.’
\p 
\v 14 “E pisǝ aromo aaka ne ezeze ying epa eburu, Ate aying o zaa shili yo pisǝ maying’.
\v 15 Aa eeta pisǝ ana ondo madinǝ mane ne, Ate ying to pisǝ epa eburu eeying ne.”
\s1 O baala azaa o pate ongmǝ
\p 
\v 16 “Eeya meke o ngmǝ, tane care mayinu nangka ana o ara ukpwei ezeze ne. Ne care mayinu kane wore aromo bekaana neya eza opate o ngmǝ. Ang dongdong bele oying, ne samba ocǝ o taasa one naname.
\v 17 Aa baaya pate o ngmǝ, kwizǝ mayinu mau, o saane mai manau,
\v 18 adorana tana rosa o bena oya eza o pate o ngmǝ ne. Ate au kaa ta gonta ne, ooka kangza wa gonte pate epaaka a ezeze a suk, wayo taasau.
\s1 O baala azaa o eke ocǝ azaa shili
\r (Luk 12:33-34)
\p 
\v 19 “Tana e kuri tukpwei toying ocǝ a lerambo leena araaka egau kaa orengkaka yo cara wai ne, araaka akǝri neyo pora ka ne lyǝ ne kpwi.
\v 20 Soona e kuri tukpwei toying ocǝ azaa shili, araaka egau ka orengkaka to cara wai ne, araaka kangza, akǝri to lyǝ ka ne eze bekǝri ne.
\v 21 Araaka ocǝ o zene, sanamea lenyong leo zene kangza.
\s1 Masanto ma lepung
\r (Luk 11:34-36)
\p 
\v 22 “Liizi leya beru be masanto ma lepung, liizi leo leeya cammo, pate lepung leo yo pena ka masanto.
\v 23 A liizi leo leeta cammo ne, pate lepung leo yo dera masanto. Masanto ma lepung leo ma itǝ maring, maring yo dongdong gongha!
\s1 O eza lezara aa ateokora a leere
\r (Luk 16:13)
\p 
\v 24 “Ondo wa era wata eza lezara ateakoro leere ne, baya nyimi oyo nyana o yende o yeme o yende, koona o tare o yende o zeele o leere me. Ba era ota tare Ashili kaa emate awere yende ne.”
\s1 O werno a Ateokora
\r (Luk 12:22-31)
\p 
\v 25 Azaa nyimi eyang bele oying, tana e gare tukpwei toying azaa epaaka eya lyame, koona eya sa me, koona nangka eyo cǝ madibi ma o amba. Ebeene kala epaolya sang? Aa lepung kangza kala madibi sang?
\v 26 Laka na engmeng o zaa shili, neta eza o shebeka koona ne shende kane eke a bengga ne. Pate ka nyimi Ate ying o zaa shili lyeeze ka ne. Ying e kala ne edang sang?
\v 27 Mana a nyimi oying a kazo gara ukpwei wai wa era wa wale lemore le yende a nyimi tomore to wai\f + \fr 6:27 \fq wa era wa wale lemore le yende a nyimi tomore to wai \ft Ewele angmǝ Ashili yende, aye ka, “Waleke opkwai o meke yende o ewa o wai.”\f*?
\p 
\v 28 “Na eyaka eya gara tukpwei toying azaa madibi ma o amba? Laka nangka eburu o wake e gongze, neta eza gole yende ne.
\v 29 Pate ka nyimi eyang belo oying na ogomo Suleimanu ka ocǝ wai wata wa amba madibi maa gong na ondo a nyimi one ne.\x - \xo 6:29 \xt 1 Agom 10:4-7; 2 Oash 9:3-6.\x*
\v 30 Nyimia Ashili eze mawake ma owake bejaga nanna, maaka maya arakana o ngmeengme, a leere a ese mai ka ola, shibari ying? Ying ana o dera o kabare kaa Ashili!
\v 31 Azaa nyimi tana e gare tukpwei toying a beyana, ‘Eya taya lya me?’ Koona ‘Eya teya sa me?’ Koona ‘Eya teya amba me?’
\v 32 A worme ana o dera o rosa Ashili neya gare tukpwei tone azaa o gera nyimi. Kangza Ate aying o zaa shili a rose o bena eya yeme mapapa maana.
\v 33 Epa e woma o bora eya, e nya Ashili tukpwei toying, e eze epa e togomo te Ashili, ka o gera epa ee sangsang ai, ayo nya ying kaa pate ma mapapa maana kangza.
\v 34 Zaa nyimia tana e gare tukpwei toying azaa leere ne, leere yo deya ka ebelo gara le. Konang lengme ya ka ozitǝ ka waya kap ka le.
\c 7
\s1 Tana ecore angmǝ azaa ondo ne
\r (Luk 6:37-38,41-42)
\p 
\v 1 “Tana e core angmǝ azaa ondo ne, adorana tana a core angmǝ azaa oying ne.
\v 2 Nangka e core angmǝ azaa na ondo, nyimia ayo core angmǝ aza oying. Kangza ka epa ogoshe ooka e ezane, ka wai ya ayo eza ying ne.\x - \xo 7:2 \xt Mar 4:24.\x*
\p 
\v 3 “Eyaka oya gonta kapa a liizi le orone o, oota ba laka okuturu a liizi leo ne?
\v 4 Ba wǝnia o bekaa orone o na, ‘Bayang lopau kapa a nyimi liizi leo,’ abo oya ka okuturu a liizi leo?
\v 5 Bo ondo ara ukpwei, bora ka o lope okuturu a liizi leo, arakaname oyo laka maleu ko ama o lopa kapa a liizi le orone o.
\p 
\v 6 “Tana e nya e'ere epa e sangsang ne, tana e tare odembashe akwilǝ acale edang aying ne. Nee era ne itǝzǝ ne ka tobona, ane kuri kane daare ying a lekeleke.”
\s1 O beya angmǝ ka Ashili
\r (Luk 11:9-13)
\p 
\v 7 “Pirǝ na ayo nya ying, geraza na eyo cǝ, gwarazana ayo pari ying abuudu.
\v 8 Pate ondooka wa pirǝ ayo nya wai, ondooka wa gera wayo cǝ, kangza pate ondooka wa gwara, ayo pari wai abuudu.
\p 
\v 9 Mana nyimi oying ana ate, kena ka wai ka bosa oborode, awa nya kai lecale?
\v 10 Koona ka bose bekwala, awa nya kai owa?
\v 11 Na ying ana ara aburu e rose nangka eyo nyaza ayana ying mapapa ma rere, shebari Ate aying o zaa shili wato kala ying aa ama o nyaza mapapa ma rere andaaka ne pirzi ai sang!
\v 12 Azaa nyimi, eza aromo epaaka oya yeme ane ezo, obena ennaa beyo be makili ma Mosa ka ana obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili.”
\s1 Abuudu a seto
\r (Luk 13:24)
\p 
\v 13 Lyǝ na abuudu a seto. Obena abuudu a patarke kaa kang gongha a aleze ka aromo akwilǝ ola, aromo a cake lyǝzǝ a ai.
\v 14 Nyimia orona o cǝsǝ ebeene o dera o maro, waya seto awa kang ya baate, andaa baate ya kalea ai.
\s1 A rose uti ka ebelo ayana wai
\r (Luk 6:43-44)
\p 
\v 15 “Ezana a sauwo ka ana beya angmǝ ka mawo rendaza. Ne deese aying ka madibi ma emande epeng, a nyimi one neye na enama orambo o kala ara aburu.
\v 16 Ebelo ogole ane wayo ote ka rose ne. Ara cǝ ayana inabi\f + \fr 7:16 \fq inabi \ft wa kap na uti a anyong kaa soze ayana wai.\f* uti ekana na, koona ayana osaya a uti ekana?
\v 17 Nyimia konang uti orere wa kareze ayana rere, aa uti oburu wa kareze ayana aburu.
\v 18 Uti orere wa era wata kare ayana aburu ne, anyimia kangza uti oburu wa era wata kare ayana aa rere ne.
\v 19 Pate uti ka wata kare ayana aa rere ne, ayo core wai a tare wai a nyimi ola.
\v 20 Nyimia ayana ane yo ote ka erose ne.”
\s1 Anta maa tukǝ o rosa oying ne
\r (Luk 13:25-27)
\p 
\v 21 Pate ondooka wa beya mi na, ‘Ateokora, Ateokora’ waya to lyǝ a nyimi togomo to zaa shili ne. Soona ondooka wa eza epaaka Ate ang o nyimia o zaa shili ya yeme me.
\v 22 A lengme lenname aromo acake yo beya me na, ‘Ateokora, Ateokora!’ Cai! Te zoole aa nyimi leze leo sang? Te sǝrsǝzǝ mabere maa buru anyimi leze leo sang? Kangza, a nyimi leze leo wa te eze mapapa mo tera ukpwei sang?
\v 23 A were namea eyang bekaa ne a begeshe be komana na, ‘Anta tukǝ orosa oying ne. Arnang na ka me, ying ana o eza epa \x - \xo 7:23 \xt Sel 6:9.\x*e buru.’
\s1 Aromo leere ana osowa
\r (Luk 6:47-49)
\p 
\v 24 “Azaa nyimi pate ondooka wa kona angmǝ ang aana, ka wa eze ogole ka ai, waye na ondoo rosa ka wa sowa akwilǝ wai azaa opoo.
\v 25 Nangka olyi wa ngmeze, na mabeno penze a ngmet, obere kang era nawa tabe akwilǝ me, nyimia na ata oko ne, obena oting ai ya azaa opoo.
\v 26 A pate ondooka wa kona a ngmǝ ang aana, ka wata eza ogole ka ai ne, waye na ondoo dera orosa ka wa so akwilǝ azaa egengge.
\v 27 Na olyi ngmeze, a mabeno penze, kangza obere ere nawa tabe akwilǝ name, naa oko a nyokonyoko.”
\p 
\v 28 Nangka Yeso ka mare o beya mapapa ma name, na epame tere leguki le aromo ukpwei azaa ambela obaala kai.
\v 29 Azaa obena ka baale ne naa ondooka waye ka obare, na ana o baala makili ma Mosa tazane.
\c 8
\s1 Yeso ka womza ondo legangca
\r (Mar 1:40-45; Luk 5:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka jǝpi aza oyara, na aromo cake ne tare kai.
\v 2 Na ogangca yende deya a kai nawa tunggunu aa begeshe be kai awa bena, “Ateokora, oya ka obare o womzang ong kang itǝ a sangsang.”
\v 3 Na Yeso nayi o ara kai naka meke wai aka bekaana, “Ma kabare ma womzau, itǝ a sangsang.” A saseya nawa woma ka leganca le ma.
\v 4 Na Yeso beka a wai, “Kona, tana o bekea ondo epa eka ee manau ne, ale ka o wore ukpwei o ondo magame ma Ashili, oo kang nya epa eka a yo esa nangka Ashili a bele Mosa. Ya nyimi ka o wore aromo bekaana ba woma.
\s1 O kabare kaa Ashili ondo ogong // ana o tesa geza omoole a Roma
\p 
\v 5 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ a Kaparnahum, Na ondo o gong o tesa geza omole o Roma bose kai na,
\v 6 “Ateokora, ozara ong ya tete akwilǝ, a lepung lewai lee gbwǝ aa waya kona o poba ajǝng.”
\p 
\v 7 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Eyang deya kang womza wai.”
\p 
\v 8 Ondo o gong o tesa geza omole name bekena, “Ateokora ang ta bare odeya akwilǝ ang ne, soona o sokoo bekaa angmǝ, ozara ong wayo woma.
\v 9 Mi ang ya taara te ondo, kangza ka ana o tesa geza a moole ba taara tong, maa kang bekaa ondo na, “Ale, awa ale, ondo kangza ang bekaa na, “Deya,” awa de, ang kang bekaa ozara ong na, “Ya epana,” a wa ye.
\v 10 Nangka Yeso ka kone nyimi, na epame tere kai ukpwei, aa ka beka ana o tarea kai na, “Ang dongdong bele ying epeng me, anta ma cǝ ondo a nyimi Isrela kawa o kabare kaa Ashili na oromo na ne.
\v 11 Eyang belo ying, aromo a cake ne yo deesa a dizi ka aza ka ne cikǝ a ne lye epaolya legwa kaa Ibraheng, kaa Ishaku aa Yakubu a nyimi togomo te o zaa shili.\x - \xo 8:11 \xt Luk 13:29.\x*
\v 12 Bangka nyimi, ayo gǝǝzǝ ayana togomo ogomo obere oburu a nyimi maring maa bitibiti. Ara aaka ne yo ruuzi ka o nonza tuuni.
\p 
\v 13 Na Yeso bekaa ondo o gong o tesa geza o moole o Roma na, “Ale, ayo yau nangka o kabare ka Ashili au ze.” Na o ngmere liizi na ozara me woma.
\s1 Yeso ka womza aromo acak
\r (Mar 1:32-34; Luk 4:38-41)
\p 
\v 14 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ akwilǝ a Biturusu naka mana ondawa wai a wata zake ne.
\v 15 Na Yeso meke o ara wai, nawa woma, aa wa era nawa sele kai epaolya.
\p 
\v 16 Nangka ulyǝlu waye, na aromo deese kaa aromo a cake ka ogomo o bere o buru wa taba ne. Kaa angmǝ ka ka beke belle, ka sǝǝrǝ obere oburu me, aka kang womza pate ana o dera o kona a cammo.
\v 17 Ka ye nyimia adorana a panza epa eka ondo beya ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Ishaya wa beke na,
\q1 “Ka ana makono maro,
\q2 kaa pate odera o kona aa zake aro.”
\s1 O zaka o tare o Yeso wa pobe
\r (Luk 9:57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Nangka Yeso ka laka aromo a cake aa nee ringgǝri kai, naka ote nee na ne kuri owulu obeno niini.
\v 19 Na ondo baala angmǝ aaka Ashili nya Mosa wa de nawa beka kai na, “Ondo baala, eyang tare o apate araaka oya ale ne.”
\p 
\v 20 Na Yeso kabare wai na, “E ere o wake neye ka she'o, engmeng o zaa shili kangza neye ka todo, aa Kena ka o Oromo kata ka ara o mora ne.”
\p 
\v 21 Na ondo nyimi ana o tare o Yeso bekena, Ateokora, baya ang ale kang taase ate ang suri.”
\p 
\v 22 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Tareng, baya andaaka ne gbwizǝ ne taase andaaka ne gbwizǝ.”
\s1 Yeso ka zurki obere ka lejǝng le manyi
\r (Mar 4:35-41; Luk 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 23 Nangka Yeso lyǝ a nyimi o onggo o taara manyi, na ana o tare o Yeso ale legwa ka kai.
\v 24 Na o bere ogong era a lepong leme, na sejǝng sheme ere ka legoone na manyi bore o lyǝzǝ a nyimi onggo me, aa Yeso ya malau.
\v 25 Na atoma kai ale nane ara kai, aa ne bekaa kai na, “Ateokora, boza ro, manyi ya lya oro.”
\p 
\v 26 Na ka bekaa ne na, “Eyaka e kerke nyimi? O kabare kaa Ashili aying me baba? Naka ere, aaka zurki obere ka lejǝng le manyi mame. Na keeya itǝ a tiiyi.
\p 
\v 27 Na epame tere aromo ukpwei, aa ne beke na, “Mana waana ka o bere ka lejǝng le manyi kone kai aane tare kai?”
\v 28 Nangka ne de owulu o makeke ma Garasina, na aromo leere ane suri a macau aaka obere o buru wa taba ne, ne wobe Yeso. Legoone lene le itǝ epa e boome maleu nangka aromo ta tareze orona me ne.
\v 29 Na ne rurayi aa ne bekaa Yeso na, “Eya manyi mau kaaro, bo Kena ka Ashili? Ba deya ko ka gǝǝzǝ ro, a were ta aya ne na?”
\p 
\v 30 Aa ma'amo kaa ne edembashe akwilǝ ne rene a cake a neya lya epaolya.
\v 31 Na obere oburu name bose Yeso na, “Baa sǝǝrǝ ro o turki ro a nyimia edembashe akwilǝ me.”
\p 
\v 32 Naka bekaa ne na, “Ale na.” Na ne suri aa ne lyǝ edembashe akwilǝ me. Na edembashe me ne ere ka tesong na ne tǝǝru a lepong leme na manyi lye ne apat.
\p 
\v 33 Na ana o soola edembashe me ne ere ka tosong, aa ne ale apeng, aa ne baale pate epa eka e mane ne, kaa epa eka ee mane ana obere o buru me.
\v 34 Na pate aromo apeng me ne suri na ne wobe Yeso. Nangka ne laka kai, na ne bose kai na ka baya makeke mane.
\c 9
\s1 Yeso ka womza ondooka lepung lewai le gbwǝ
\r (Mar 2:1-12; Luk 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ o onggo manyi, naka tare a Kaparnahum apeng aaka ka gong ne.
\v 2 Na ca kai ondo ka lepung le wai le gbwi aa waya tete a kapengge. Nangka Yeso ka laka okabare kaa Ashili ane, naka bekaa ondooka lepung lewai le gbwǝ na, “Kena kang, zanta, a pisǝ madinǝ mau.”
\p 
\v 3 Na ana o baala ngmǝ aaka Ashili nya Mosa ne bekaa a tukpwei tone na, “Karomo kaana ka tambo Ashili!”
\p 
\v 4 Aa Yeso ka orosa madoola mane, naka pirkǝ na, “Eyaaka eya eza madoola maburu a nyong aying nanna?
\v 5 Eya kala o dera o poba, o beka na, “O bena a pisǝ madinǝ mau na, ‘Koona era ka oyeng na?
\v 6 Eyang yeme e rose obena Kena ka o Oromo kaye ka obare o pisǝ madinǝ a lerambo.’ Naka bekaa ondooka lepung le wai le gbwǝ na, “Era ka o jeke kapengge kau o ale akwilǝ.”
\v 7 Na oromo me ere, nawa ale akwilǝ.
\v 8 Nangka aromo a cake ne laka nyimi, nane kone boome, aa ne sabe Ashili, aaka aa nya aromo ebelo obare oona.
\s1 Yeso ka rare Matiyu
\r (Mar 2:13-17; Luk 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ izi ka teweno, naka laka oromo yende kaa rareze wai na Matiyu, aa waya cikǝ awa eze ogole ara o eese emate makeke. Naka bekaa wai na, “Tareng.” Nawa ere aa wa tare kai.
\v 10 Malo nyimi aa Yeso ya lya epaolya akwilǝ a Matiyu, na ana o eesa emate makeke ka ana madinǝ a cake ne de, na ne cikǝ ka kai kaa ana o tare o kai.
\v 11 Nangka maParisa ne laka nyimi, na ne bekaa atoma kai na, “Eyaka ka ondo obaala o ying waya lya epaolya kaa ana o eesa emate makeke kaa na madinǝ?”\x - \xo 9:11 \xt Luk 15:1-2.\x*
\p 
\v 12 Nangka Yeso ka kone nyimi na ka bekaa na, “Andaaka neya kona azake ta gera ondo onyaza makang ne, seekoona ana o kono.
\v 13 Azaa nyimi ale na ka e gere orosa epaaka nyimi, ‘Egonegonea mi ang yeme aying, onyaza eyapaa tazane.’ Antaa ma deya kang rare andaa woma ne, seena ana madinǝ.”\x - \xo 9:13 \xt Mat 12:7; Hos 6:6.\x*
\s1 Be perǝ azaa opate ongmǝ
\r (Mar 2:18-22; Luk 5:33-39)
\p 
\v 14 Na ana otare Yohana o batisma ne deya Yeso na ne beka kai na, “Awiinia ro ka maParisa te pate o ngmǝ, a na otare o ta ezaza ne?”
\p 
\v 15 Na Yeso kabare nee na, “Anyong a era caro ajaa ondooka wa sure ana ondaye osau a neye legwa na? Tomore ya deya ka ayo jeka ondoo ana ondaaye osau a baya ne. A tomore tonname neyo pate o ngmǝ.
\v 16 “Ondo wa ere wata manka ozani osau ka wa naane odibi oo kozo ne, o naane me yo dara odibi me kawa kala o samba o burǝ.
\v 17 Kangza, ondo wa era wata kare manyi ma o inabi ma sau aa boboto a kozo ne. Waya nyimi a boboto me yo poso ka manyi ma o inabi me oko, a boboto me caro. Manyi ma o inabi ma sau, a kare mai a boboto a sau. Adorana a bisi kaa pate maleere mame.”
\s1 Kagala ka Yariyus // kaa ondaaye ooka manyau ya ooso a wai
\r (Mar 5:21-43; Luk 8:40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Yeso kaya za obeya nyimi naname, na ondoono o dandaro o gwarzanang maYahuda, wa de aa wa tunggunu ating kai aa wa bekaa na, “Nanname na kagala kang surǝ aa gbwǝ, deya ka o eke taara to azaa kai, ka yo era.”
\v 19 Na Yeso ere legwa kaa ana otare kai, nane ale ka oromo me.
\p 
\v 20 Ondaaye yende wa zene arame aa wa ye shenai betuuru ka she leere aa waya kono o ooso manyau, nawa deya a sauwo a dimǝ Yeso nawa eke o ara a bengmǝ be odibi kai.
\v 21 Aa wa bekaa lenyong lewai na, “Maa eke o ara odibi kai belle, eyang woma.”
\p 
\v 22 Nangka Yeso ka ringgǝnu naka laka wai, naka bekaana, “Ondaaye, zanta, o kabare kaa Ashili au, wa womzau.” A saseya na ondaaye me woma.
\p 
\v 23 Nangka Yeso ka de akwilǝ ondoono dandaro gwarzanang maYahuda, naka mana aromo acak aa neya ulbǝ esherowa ka seleera she ma'ade.
\v 24 Naka bekaana, “Erana arakaana! Ogala me taa wa gbwǝ ne waya malauwa belle.” Nane zoze, aa ne zeele kai.
\p 
\v 25 Nangka asǝǝrǝ aromo me o yanga, naka lyǝ aa nyimi aa ka meke o ara ogala me, aaka ara kai.
\v 26 Na orooka me wa ale a kuruwǝ a pate makeke mame.
\s1 Yeso ka womza arǝ kaa orakare
\p 
\v 27 Yeso kaya baya ara me naname, na arǝ aleere tare kai aa ne rare ajǝng na, “Kena ka Daoda kona egonegone ero!”
\p 
\v 28 Nangka ka lyǝ akwilǝ yende na arǝ me deya kai, na Yeso me bekaa ne na, “Ee kabare ka Ashili obena maa erang womza ying na?”
\p Na ne kabare kai na, “Eeye, Ateokora.”
\p 
\v 29 Naka a eke o ara kai aa yizi ane, aaka bekaa na, “Azaa o kabare ka Ashili aying, aa womza ying.”
\v 30 Na a yizi ane pǝrnu. Aa Yeso windi ne teto maleu na, “Tana e bele ondo orooka na ne.”
\p 
\v 31 Pate ka nyimi, na ne suri, aane baale orooka kai aa kuruwǝ aa makeke ma me.
\p 
\v 32 Nangka neya ale, na ca kai orakare yende ka obere oburu wa tabe wai.
\v 33 Malo oka a sǝǝrǝ obere o buru me, na orakare me wa obeke angmǝ. Na epa me tere aromo cak tukpwei aane beyaa na, “Ata aa tuku laka ebelo epa eena a nyimi a Isrela ne.”
\p 
\v 34 Na maParisa bekaana, “Ka legoone le ogomo obere o burua wa ya sǝrsǝzǝ mabere maburu.”
\s1 Yeso ka kone egonegone aromo
\p 
\v 35 Na Yeso ka aleze a topepeng, aaka baale angmǝ a lebo a madandaro ma ogwarzanang maYahuda, aaka zoole azaa togomo te Ashili, aaka womza aromo azaa kombela makono ka o dera o kona a zake.
\v 36 Nangka ka laka o kurkǝnǝng aromo naka kone egonegone, obena neya zitǝ azaa o dera ondo o kangkama, neye na emande epeng zora ondo otare ka ne.\x - \xo 9:36 \xt Abal 27:17; 1 Agom 22:17; 2 Oash 18:16; Ezek 34:5; Mar 6:35.\x*
\v 37 Aka bekaa ana o tare o akai na, “O shende arame gong, aa na o shende me ta gongnga ne.
\v 38 Azaa nyimi, bosana ateokora o shende me kawa tong ana ogole kane shende.”
\c 10
\s1 Yeso ka zake atoma akai
\r (Mar 3:13-19; Luk 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Na Yeso zake ana o tare o akai betuuru kaa leere, a ka nya ne legoone lo sǝǝrǝ mabere maburu, ka o womza koonang makono kaa o dera o kona azake.
\p 
\v 2 Shennaa seze she atoma Yeso betuuru:
\li1 Obora waya Siman ka a beya wai na Biturusu,
\li1 Kaa orone wai Andarawus,
\li1 Kaa Yakubu kena kaa Zabadi,
\li1 Kaa orone wai Yohana,
\li1 
\v 3 Kaa Pilibus,
\li1 Kaa Batilomi,
\li1 Kaa Toma,
\li1 Kaa Matiyu ondo eesa emate makeke,
\li1 Kaa Yakubu kena ka Halpa,
\li1 Kaa Tadiyus,
\li1 
\v 4 Kaa Siman karomo ka Kan'na ka beya kai na kaye kale nyong le makeke ma kai,
\li1 Kangza kaa Yahuda Iskariyoti ooka wa nya Yeso.
\s1 Yeso ka tong atoma betuuru kaa leere
\r (Mar 6:7-13; Luk 9:1-6)
\p 
\v 5 Nee betuuru kaa leere namea Yeso ka tong, aaka bekaa nee na, “Tana ne ale a makeke ma aworme ne, na koonang apeng a Samariya,
\v 6 soona e ale emande epeng ka e wilǝ, aromo a Isrela.
\v 7 A nyimi teweno teying e zoole na, ‘Togomo te zaa shili te amara.’
\v 8 Ee womza ana makono, ee arsaza andaaka ne gbwizǝ, a womza agangca, ee sǝǝrǝ mabere maburu. A nyaza ying zora onya eyapa, ying ma nyaza na nyimi.
\p 
\v 9 Kane monte emate o ozinari, na azorpa, emate epeng a nyimi lejǝng le le'eke.
\v 10 Kangza kane jeke ojeketa a teweno toying ne, kane jeke madibi maleere ne, na tokakau, na lebenda, obena ondo ogole gwara ka epaolya wai.\x - \xo 10:10 \xt 1 Kor 9:14; 1 Tim 5:18.\x*
\v 11 Pate apeng aaka e lyǝ ne, ee gere oromo edang ka e jǝpi akwilǝ wai, a ale a were o baya apeng me.
\v 12 Eeya lyǝ a akwilǝ me ee bekaa na, ‘O cikǝ o cammo itǝ oying.’
\v 13 Akwilǝ me edang aaza, oo cikǝ o cammo ying wa cikǝ ai. Kangza edang waata zane, aa wa kuri a ying.
\v 14 Pate ondooka wa nyana o emba oying, koona wa nyana o kona angmǝ aying, eeya surǝ akwilǝ me, na apeng me e zazame ma sorma ma tobona toying.\x - \xo 10:14 \xt Ogat 13:51.\x*
\v 15 “Eyang dongdong obele oying, a lengme lo core angmǝ ayo kona egonegone makeke ma Sadoma ka ma Gwamrata azaa apeng na.”
\s1 Ozitǝ o deya
\r (Mar 13:9-13; Luk 12:11-12; Luk 21:12-19)
\p 
\v 16 “Laka na, ma tonga ying naa emande epeng a nyimi egana. Azaa nyimi cikǝ na ka o rosana na ewa, kangza e itǝ ana epa erere naa egoma.
\v 17 Ezana a sauwo ka aromo, neyo ale ying abegeshe ana o cora ngmǝ, aane ole ying ane eze ying teyong aa madandaro ma ogwarzanang maYahuda.
\v 18 Aza ong Kangza neyo aleze ka ying abegeshe be andaano kaa agomo, ka e beke angmǝ a lebo aza ong abegeshe be aworme.
\v 19 Awereaka ne meke ying kane ale kaa ying aana togomo, tane gare tukpwei toying aza epa eeka eyo beka, kaa nangka eyo beka ne, ayo nya ying epa eka eyo beka awere me.
\v 20 Aza obena ying ngha ta beya angmǝ ne, Obere orere Ate a ying waya ya beya angmǝ aa tongmǝ toying.
\p 
\v 21 “Orone wayo nya orone wai ka wong, nyimia ate yo ya ka kena ka wai. Ayana kangza neyo girǝ ana ate ane, ane ote ka wongze ne.
\v 22 Aromo neyo nyana ying azaa leze leng. Pate ondooka wa motana aa ale omaare, wayo bisǝ.
\v 23 Nee gǝǝzǝ ying apeng aana, songhana ka e alea apeng a izi. Epeng emea eyang dongdong belo oying, eto mara o aleze a topepeng te Isrela ne, aa Kena ka o Oromo yo deya.
\p 
\v 24 “Ondo tare wata kala ondo baala wai ne, ozara kangza wata kala ateokora wai ne.
\v 25 Wa gwara ondooka a baale wai aa wa itǝ na ondo o baala wai, ozara kangza waye na ateokora wai. Aa ne rare ateokora na Ba'alzebul, nannia aromo akwilǝ wai kangza?”
\s1 Ondooka wa gwara a kone boome be wai
\r (Luk 12:2-9)
\p 
\v 26 “Azaa nyimi kane kone boome bene ne, obena eyapa tazene ka a pate, ka atoo pǝri e ne, kangza eyapa ta zene ka aa baasa ka atoo rosa ee ne.
\v 27 Epa eeka eyang baala oying asuk, beke na e aa pantalang. Aa epa eeka a bele ying a toto, zoola na azaa e ajǝng aa betǝnkǝrǝ.
\v 28 Tana e kone boome be andaaka ne wonze oromo ne, a neta ama o wonga bebuu be wai ne. Soona e kone boome be ondooka waye ka legoone le o wonga bebuu ka lepung apat akwilǝ ola.
\v 29 A lisǝzǝ engmeng e leere okobo sang? Kayende ka era aa kata tǝru aa deze ka ka gbwǝ dera orosa a Ate aying ne.
\v 30 Nyimia waaza pate shepkwai she ying a bala.
\v 31 Azaa nyimi tane kone boome ne. Obena edang eying e kala engmeng acak.”
\p 
\v 32 “Pate ondooka wa kabare kaa mi a begeshe be aromo, mi ma eyang kabare kaa wai a begeshe be Ate ang o zaa shili.
\v 33 Apate ondooka wa sangga o rosa ong a begeshe be aromo, mi ma eyang sangga o rosa wai a begeshe be Ate ang o zaa shili.”
\s1 Anta ma deya ka ocikǝ o cammo ne seena o kara
\r (Luk 12:51-53; 14:26-27)
\p 
\v 34 “Tane eke obena ma deya ka o cikǝ a cammo a lerambo leena ne. Anta ma deya ka o cikǝ ocammo ne, soona okara.
\v 35 Ma deya,
\q1 Kang gwara oromo kaa ate wai,
\q2 Ang gwaara okara kagala kaa iini kai,
\q1 aa iini ka ogiri wai.
\q2 
\v 36 Kangza wa itǝ bena ondoo nyana o wa ya nyimi a kwilǝ au.\x - \xo 10:36 \xt Mek 7:6.\x*
\p 
\v 37 Pate ondooka wa kala yeme ate, na iini wai o kala ong, wata gwara awa itǝ a ong ne. Kangza ondooka wa kala yeme ayana wai alome ka a ai o kala ong, wata gwara awa itǝ aa ong ne.
\v 38 Nyimia ondooka waata ana uti o gendare o wai a wa tareng ne, wata gwara a wa itǝ a ong ne.
\v 39 Pate ondooka wa yeme ebeene wai, wayo dera e. Aa pate ondooka wa dera ebeene wai azaa ong, wayo cǝ e.
\s1 Ogole otaasa
\r (Mar 9:41)
\p 
\v 40 “Ondooka wa kabare kaa ying, wa kabare kami naname. Kangza, ondooka wa kabare kaa mi wa kabare kaa ondooka wa tongang.\x - \xo 10:40 \xt Mar 9:37; Luk 9:48; 10:16; Yoh 13:20.\x*
\v 41 Ondooka wa emba ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo Ashili, ka leze le obena wai ondo obeya ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wai, wayo cǝ o taasa ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili. Ondooka wa kabare kaa ondo o sangsang, ka leze le obena wai ondo o woma wai, wayo cǝ o taasa ondo o sangsang.
\v 42 Komana wa nya kena ka yende a nyimi ayana aa batebate naa kaso kaa manyi, ka leze le obena wai ondo tare ong nga wai wato dongdong dera o taasa wai ne.”
\c 11
\s1 Yeso ka ana o tare o Yohana o batisma
\r (Luk 7:18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Malooka Yeso ka mare ozoola a atoma kai betuuru ka leere name, na ka ere aa rana me na ka ale aaka baale ka o zoola a topepeng to Galili\f + \fr 11:1 \fq Galili \ft Ka leleng le maHelena a eze ogole ka topepeng tone\f*.
\p 
\v 2 A were me Yohana ko batisma kaya apate aa kwilǝ ana o ezaza epa eburu, nawa kone epa eka Almasipu ya eza me, nawa tong ana o tare o wai ara Yeso
\v 3 kane pirkǝ wai na, “Boa ondooka waya deya na, na te kare ayizi a ondo na?”
\p 
\v 4 Na Yeso kabare nee na, “Kurǝna ka e bekaa Yohana epa eeka ee laka kangza ka ee kaa ekone,
\v 5 obena arǝ na cǝ o laka ara, aa agǝdǝ neya teyeno, agangca ne kurǝ a sangsang, arara neya konaza ngmǝ, aa ya arsaza andaaka na gbwizǝ kangza a nya ana o dera cǝ oroka o lebo.\x - \xo 11:5 \xt Ish 35:5-6; 61:1.\x*
\v 6 Ondo okona oleba ondooka waata cǝwǝ aa zaa o eke lenyong le wai aza ong ne.”
\p 
\v 7 Nangka ne ale, na Yeso bore obeya angmǝ ka aromo a cake a zaa Yohana na, “E ale owake nee laka eya? E laka mawake maaka obere ya paba me na?
\v 8 Na ee surǝ ka e laka eya? Ondo ka wa amba madibi maa rere na? Aromo akwilǝ ogomo neya ambaza madibi maa rere.
\v 9 Na eya ee surǝ a laka me? Ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili na? Nyimia, eyang bele oying na, wa dongdong kala ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili.
\v 10 Ondo ona a wele aa zaa wai na, “Laka na, ma tong ka o otoma ong kawa kala a izi au, ondooka wayo babarau orona zongka o de.\x - \xo 11:10 \xt Mal 3:1.\x*
\p 
\v 11 Eyang dongdong belle oying, ata a tukǝ o ngmenga ondo a nyimi lerambo leena ka wa dukǝ Yohana o batisma ogonga ne, pate kaa nyimi, ondooka kala a be baate a togomo te zaa shili wa kala wai.
\v 12 O era a were o Yohana o batisma a deya o ngmeengme togomo te zaa shili teya kala o ara ozitǝ, ana o ote o zitǝ me neya yeme o emba togomo teme ka legoone.
\v 13 Nyimia apate ana o baya ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili kaa makili maa kaa Ashili a nya Mosa ne beke angmǝ aa zaa togomo te me zongka Yohana de.
\v 14 Kangza ee yo kabare ka letoma leena, Yohana waya a beka angmǝ aa zaa wai kaa a bena Iliya ya deya.\x - \xo 11:14 \xt Mal 4:5; Mat 17:10-13; Mar 9:11-13.\x*
\v 15 Pate ondo teto to kona, awa kone.
\p 
\v 16 “Ma erang kedeya aromo awere na keeya? Naa ayana aka neya cikǝ ara ejamane, aane rare eja eceya ene aane beyana,
\q1 
\v 17 “‘Te ulubǝ ying tejebe,
\q2 na eta e yowa leera ne,
\q1 te beya leera le ma'ade
\q2 na eta ee ruuzi ne.
\p 
\v 18 Lakana, Yohana wa de wata wa lyeeze aa wa soze ne, nane bekaana, ‘Cai! Waya ka o obere oburu.’
\v 19 Nangka Kena ka Oromo ka de na ka lyeeze aka soze nane bekaana, ‘Laka na ondo okala o ara o lyeeza ka o soza, beja bena o eesa emate makeke ka ana madinǝ!’ Pate kaa nyimi, a ebelo orosa Ashili, aa zaa gole o ai waya a rose edang.”
\s1 O lyǝ udi o topepeng te odera kabare kaa Ashili
\r (Luk 10:13-15)
\p 
\v 20 Naka bore ozurki a topepeng teeka ka kala ara o eza ogole o kai o tera ukpwei ne, obena aromo me neta ne kuri aa Ashili ne.
\v 21 E lyǝ udi Korasiya! E lyǝ udi Betsaida! Obekaana ogole o tera ukpwei ooka a eze a nyimi ying aa ezea Taya ka Sidon, eeya nee samba o kurǝ aa Ashili ka o rabo aane amba majankale ka o kareze mato apung ane.\x - \xo 11:21 \xt Ish 23:1-18; Ezek 26:1-28:26; Joy 3:4-8; Emo 1:9-10; Zak 9:2-4.\x*
\v 22 Azaa nyimi, eyang belo ying, a lengme lo core angmǝ, ayo kala aa kona egonegone aromo a Taya ka Sidon azaa oying.
\v 23 Bo ma Kaparnahum, oya gonta o bena aya zalara o aa zaa shili na? Nyimia taza ne, aya jǝpǝrǝ o araaka ana o gbwizǝ zene. Epa otera ukpwei ka a eze aa nyimi oo, eya aa eze a Sadoma, Sadoma me waayo tata a deya o ngmeengme.\x - \xo 11:23 \xt Ish 14:13-15; Obo 19:24-28.\x*
\v 24 Aza nyimi, eyang bele oying, a lengme le o core angmǝ, ayo kala aa kona egonegone o makeke ma Sadoma baa zaa o.”
\s1 Deyana a mi adorana e cǝ o teeseke
\r (Luk 10:21-22)
\p 
\v 25 A were namea Yeso ka bekaana, “Ate maa kona oleba o, Ateokora o zaa shili kaa deze, aa zaa obena ba baasa epaana a na o ama ka o rosa, na ba pari ara andaaka neta rosa eyapa ne.
\v 26 Nyimia Ate, enna eya epa eeka e kala o rera aa bo.
\p 
\v 27 Ate ang wa nya ekeeya aa taara tong. Ondo ta rosa kena kame ne soona Ate me, kangza ondo ta rosa Ate me ne soona kena kame, kaa pate ondooka kena kame kaa yeme owore o wai.\x - \xo 11:27 \xt Yoh 3:35; 1:18; 10:15.\x*
\v 28 Deyana me pate o ying ana o zitǝ, ying ana o kona kaa be dengdeng, eyang nya ying o teseke.
\v 29 Lyǝ na a lezara leng, ee eze epa eeka ang eze, obena mi ondo o nata ukpwei ya wai, ondooka wata ara ukpwei ne, eyo cǝ o nata anyong.
\v 30 Obena lezara leng ta poba ne, magogoro mang kangza ta dengdeng ne.”
\c 12
\s1 Ateokora Lengme le o teseke maYahuda
\r (Mar 2:23-28; Luk 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 1 A were name a lengme le o teseke le maYahuda, Yeso ka dare aa nyimi turu te eyuu. Atoma kai neya kona ekomo, na ne torbe makpwe ma eyuu na ne lye.
\v 2 Nangka maParisa ne laka nyimi, na ne beka kai na, “Ba laka atoma au neya eza epa eeka makili ma Mosa ma nare eze a lengme le o teseke le maYahuda.”
\p 
\v 3 Naka bekaa nee na, “Eta e kone epa eeka Daoda ye a were aka ka kone ekomo, kai kaa aja teweno te kai sang?
\v 4 Nangka ka lyǝ akwilǝ Ashili naka lye borode emea kata gwara aaka lye, na aja teweno te kai ne lye ne, soona ana magame ma Ashili belle.\x - \xo 12:4 \xt Mag 24:9; 1 Sam 21:1-7.\x*
\v 5 Ying eta e soole a ngmǝ aaka Ashili nya Mosa, nangka ana magame ma Ashili, aa akwilǝ Ashili ne cakate makili ma lengme lo teseke maYahuda aa zaa nyimi ne tambo na?\x - \xo 12:5 \xt Abal 28:9-10.\x*
\v 6 Eyang bele oying, kando kamea ka kala akwilǝ Ashili kaana.
\v 7 Ayya e rose epa eeka a ngmǝ Ashili ya beyame, ‘Mi o cikǝ egonegonea mi ang yeme aying, o nayi Ashili enama tazane,’ etaa eeyo laka madinǝ mana odera madinǝ ne.
\v 8 Obena Kena ka Oromo kaya Ateokora o lengme le o teseke le maYahuda.”
\s1 Ondooka o ara wai wa waka
\r (Mar 3:1-6; Luk 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Na Yeso baya araname aaka lyǝ odandaro o gwarzanang maYahuda.
\v 10 Aa mana oromo yende a rame ooka o ara wai wa waka. Nane pirkǝ Yeso na, “Obaala Mosa wa wore obena wa gwara a womza a lengme le o teseke le maYahuda na?” Ne pirkǝ kai nyimia adorana ne cǝ kai ka o tambo.
\v 11 Naka bekaa nee na, “Mana a nyimi oying waaya ka omande openg, na wa taru a leo a lengme lo teseke le maYahuda, wato meke wai kawa sǝǝrǝ ne na?
\v 12 Oromo kala omande epeng edang maleu. Azaa nyimi ata aa nara ogole o rere aa lengme teseke maYahuda ne.”
\v 13 Naka bekaa oromo me na, “Niyi o ara o!” Nawa niyi ora me, aa wa kuri a zak na o leere me.
\v 14 Na maParisa suri, a ne gwaara madoola ma nangka neyo wongha kai.
\s1 Yeso ozara ka Ashili a zake
\p 
\v 15 Nangka Yeso rose nyimi, na ka ere arame. Na aromo acake tare kai naka womza ne apat.
\v 16 Aa ka windi ne toto na kana ne bele ana ondo ne.
\v 17 Aye nyimia ka panza o bekaa ondo beya ngmǝ ka mawo Ashili Ishaya na,
\q1 
\v 18 “Kazara kang ang kaana kamea ma zake!
\q2 Epa oyeme ong, kamea ang kone oleba kai ba cak.
\q1 Eyang nya kai o bere ong, aa kayo beka ngmǝ a masanto a makeke ma aworme.
\q1 
\v 19 Ka too beya masanggo koona ka beye angmǝ a jǝng ne,
\q2 Kangza ondo too kona lengmelo le kai aza orona ne.
\q1 
\v 20 Legaaga leeme le tunggunu katoo pora leene,
\q2 Beru be masanto bemea bee amara ka o lambu katoo limbǝ be ne,
\q1 Ka ka ote epeng eme ke lya izi.
\q2 
\v 21 Aa nyimi leze le kai aworme kangza neyo eke lenyong a kai.”\x - \xo 12:21 \xt Ish 42:1-4.\x*
\s1 Yeso kaa Ba'alzebul
\r (Mar 3:20-30; Luk 11:14-23)
\p 
\v 22 Na ca Yeso orakare ka urǝ waze ka wa kang ya ka obere o buru, naka womza wai, nawa bore beya ngmǝ awa kang gonta ara.
\v 23 Na epame tere aromo me ukpwei, na ne bekaana, “Kanna Kena Daoda tazane na?”
\p 
\v 24 Nangka maParisa ne kone nyimi na ne bekaana, ka legoone le Ba'alzebul ogomo obere oburua kando kaana kaya sǝrsǝzǝ mabere maburu.”
\p 
\v 25 Nangka Yeso ka rose madoola mane, naka bekaa nee na, “Pate togomo teeka te arnang to dǝkǝni to leere a neya kara ka tukpwei, teyo caro. Kangza apeng koona akwilǝ aaka a arnang to dǝkǝni to leere a neya kara ka tukpwei, ayo rizi.
\v 26 O Shetan wa sǝǝrǝ o Shetan waya kara ka ukpwei wai naname. Togomo te wai yoya legoone nannia?
\v 27 Ma sǝrsǝzǝ obere oburu ka legoone le Ba'alzebul, ana o tare o ying ne sǝrsǝzǝ ka legoone le mana? Aa zaa nyimi ana otare oying neya yo core ying angmǝ me.
\v 28 A ma sǝrsǝzǝ bere o buru ka legoone le obere Ashili na togomo te Ashili te deya aying naname.
\p 
\v 29 A era ta lyǝ aa kwilǝ ondo legoone ka bese magogoro ma wai ne, soona a tese wai suri, aa amaa ama o besa magogoro ma akwilǝ a wai.
\p 
\v 30 Ondooka wata ya legwa kami, ondo o nyana ong nga wai. Kangza ondooka wata kangkamang a kurǝ me ne, waya bacakaraa.\x - \xo 12:30 \xt Mar 9:40.\x*
\v 31 Aa zaa nyimi eyang bele oying, ayo pisǝ madinǝ ma aromo apat, ondooka wa sopa o obere Ashili, a to pisǝ madinǝ ma wai ne.
\v 32 Ondooka wa beya a ngmǝ ma zeelakong aa Kena ka Oromo, ayo pisǝ madinǝ ma wai. Ondooka wa beya a ngmǝ ma zeelakong aa obere Ashili, a to pisǝ madinǝ ma wai a nyimi lerambo leena nanname ka o ale a izi ne.
\s1 Uti kaa ayana wai
\r (Luk 6:43-45)
\p 
\v 33 Uti o rere wa ngmenze ayana a rere. Uti oburu wa ngmenze ayana aburu. A rose uti ayana wai ya.
\v 34 Ying okurkǝnǝng ewa ee buru! Ee wiinia ee beye angmǝ edang, a ying naana ana ara buru ne? Obena epa emea eya nyimi lenyong eya susi o ngmǝ.
\v 35 Oromo edang, a nyimi lenyong le wai wa eke epa eeke eye ka edang, ondo ara buru o eke lenyong lewai le eburu eya susi a lenyong le wai.
\v 36 Eyang bele oying, aa lengme le o core angmǝ, pate angmǝ aburu ka oromo wa beya ayo pirkǝ wai.
\v 37 Angmǝ au aya ayo sǝǝrǝu, aa kangza aya ayo core angmǝ aza o.
\s1 O gera o laka epa o tera ukpwei
\r (Mar 8:11-12; Luk 11:29-32)
\p 
\v 38 Na ana obaala angmǝ aaka Ashili nya Mosa kaa maParisa ne bekaa kai na, “Ondo baala, teya yeme aa te laka epa otera ukpwei aa bo.”
\p 
\v 39 Naka kabare na, “Ying aromo tomore teena, ana leyau ka ara aburu, neya gera o laka epa otera ukpwei, a era ta wore ne epa otera ukpwei ne! Soona epa o tera ukpwei ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo Ashili Yonana.
\v 40 Nangka Yonana wa more awa were ka taaro a nyimi lebangi le bekwala bee gong, nyimia Kena ka Oromo kayo ya tomore to taro nyimi ocau.
\v 41 A lengme le core angmǝ aromo o Neneba neyo era ka aromo tomore teena, ka ne toze aromo a tomore teena kane ta ne ya epa e woma ne, azaa o bena nee kurǝa Ashili aa kazo o ozoola o Yonana. Kangza ondo ka wa kala Yonana waya raana.
\v 42 A Lengme le o core angmǝ, Aya ogong o makeke ma o Sheba wayo era kaa aromo a tomore teena, ka wa toze ne, o bena wa deya a wa suri a macangcang ma lerambo leena, kawa kone o rosa ogomo Suleimanu. Ondo ka wa kala Suleimanu naana.
\s1 O kurǝ o bere o buru
\r (Luk 11:24-26)
\p 
\v 43 Obere o buru wa surǝ nyimi oromo, aa wa kaale araaka manyi ta zane ne azaa o gera ara o teseke. Aa wa ta ocǝ ne,
\v 44 malo nyimi aa wa bekaana, “Eyang kurǝ akwilǝ aa kaa maa surǝ ne.’ Wa kurǝ wayo mana akwilǝ amea zora ondo nyimi me aa a besa ai aa babare aa sangsang.
\v 45 A wayo kurǝ kawa jeke mabere maa buru o sondaare maaka ma kala o bora me ara aburu, kane lyǝ ba oromo me aa ne cikǝ a nyimi owai. O maare oromo me wayo kala o bora wai o buru. Nyimia wayo itǝ kaa ana ara aburu a tomore teena.”
\s1 Iini Yeso ka arone kai
\r (Mar 3:31-35; Luk 8:19-21)
\p 
\v 46 Nangka Yeso kaya beya angmǝ kaa aromo a cak naa mana iini ka arone kai aa neya itǝ oo yanga, a neya yeme o beya a ngmǝ kaa kai.”
\v 47 Na oromo yende bekaa kai na, “Iini kaa arone au, neya oo yanga aa neya yeme o beya a ngmǝ kaa bo.”
\v 48 Na Yeso kabare na, “Mana iini ong, kaa arone ang?”
\v 49 Naka niyi o ara kai ana o tare kai, aa ka bekaana, “Andaana iini ong kaa arone ang.”
\v 50 Komana wa eza epa eeka Ate ang o zaa shili waya yeme me, waya arone ang kaa iini ong.”
\c 13
\s1 Angmǝ gerpo aa aza ondo owaale ebelo
\r (Mar 4:1-9; Luk 8:4-8)
\p 
\v 1 A lengme leme na Yeso suri akwilǝ me, naka ale aa ka cikǝ o wulu o lepong.
\v 2 Na leguki le aromo leegong deya a kai, naka lyǝ o onggo o tara manyi naka cikǝ. Aa leguki le aromo me kangza ne itǝ o wulu lepong le me.\x - \xo 13:2 \xt Luk 5:1-5.\x*
\v 3 Naka bele ne mapapa cake aa nyimi angmǝ a gerpo na, “Ondo ogole ara yende wa ale ara aa waale ebelo.
\v 4 Nangka waya waale me, na ebelo eyende taru a za orona, na engmeng de nane donge e.
\v 5 Na eyende taru aa za acale araaka makeke ta gongha ne. Na e suri a saseya obena makeke arame taa gerpo ne.
\v 6 Nangka ongme wa tamana na ma ya rauwo, na ma waka obena madǝrǝ mame taa gerpo ne.
\v 7 Ee belo yende kangza taru a nyimi ekana, na ekana me gong na e gatakale e.
\v 8 Ee yende kangza taru a makeke ma rere, na ekare eyo, na eye eyo liwinu, liwunu, eyende etuuru taashe, taashe, eyende kangza etuuru taaro, taaro.
\v 9 Pate ondooka waye ka toto to konaza a wa kone angmǝ aa na.”
\s1 Masanto ma angmǝ aa gerpo aa na
\r (Mar 4:10-12; Luk 8:9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Na atoma Yeso de, aa ne pirkǝ kai na, “Eyaaka o beya angmǝ aa gerpo ka aromo?”
\v 11 Naka kabare ne na, “Ying aa kabare o bena e rose o ela o togomo te Ashili, aa ne ata a nya nee ne.
\v 12 O bena ondooka waya ka eyapa waya ayo wala wai ne, ka wa cǝ a cake. Kangza ondo odera eyapa, ee baate kawa ye ka e, ayo emba e a wai.
\v 13 Epa eeka e ote na eyang beya ngmǝ gerpo kane,
\q1 ‘Adorana na ne gonte a neta laka ne,
\q2 aa ne rakara a neta a kona ne,
\q2 obena epa eme e lyǝ aane amaring.’
\p 
\v 14 Azaa one ayo panza epa eeka ondo beya ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Ishaya wa beke na,
\q1 “Eyo konaza,
\q2 aa eto rosa ne dakememe,
\q1 eyo kang gonta
\q2 aa eto laka ne ko babate.
\q1 
\v 15 Obena anyong aromo ana aya katakau,
\q2 aa teto tene ta konaza ne.
\q1 Kangza ne pate ayizi ane,
\q2 obena kana ne gonte ka ayizi ane ne,
\q1 kana ne kone ka teto tene ne,
\q2 obena kana ne cǝ orosa ne,
\q2 kane kuri a mi kang womza nee ne.’
\p 
\v 16 Ana o kona oleba ying obena ayizi aying aya gonta, a teto teying kangza taya konaza.
\v 17 Eyang dongdong baala oying ana obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili ka ana o kona boome Ashili a cake ne yeme olaka epana eeya gonta me, na ne ta laka ne, aa ne kone epa eeka eya konaza me, na ne ta kona ne.
\p 
\v 18 “Anna masanto ma angmǝ a gerpo ondo o waale ebelo na.
\v 19 Pate ondooka wa kona ngmǝ a togomo nawa ta rosa ne, ogomo o bere oburu deese kawa kwagale epaaka a waale a lenyong le wai. Enna ebelo eeka a wale a za orona.
\v 20 Ebelo eeka ee tǝru ara acale, eya naa ondooka wa kona angmǝ Ashili, nawa embe ka o kona o leba.
\v 21 Oo bena wata ka oting ne, nawa ta rabo aa cake ne. A were aka o kedeya na opoba wa era, azaa a ngmǝ Ashili, aa oromo me kuri sidimǝ.
\v 22 Ebelo ee ka e taru a nyimi ekana, eya na ondooka wa kona ngmǝ Ashili, na madoola ma ocǝ ka o kona oleba awere na a nare angmǝ o gongha, ka ngmǝ me itǝ o dera edang.
\v 23 Ebelo eemea ee tǝru a makeke ma rere, waya na ondooka wa kone ngmǝ Ashili na wa rose ai, awa eze ogole ka ai. Kangza awa cǝ eyapa aza ame, eyende lewinu, lewinu, eyende etuuru taashe, taashe, ee yende etuuru taaro, taaro.”
\s1 A ngmǝ a gerpo azaa mawake a nyimi o alkama
\p 
\v 24 Na Yeso kang bele ne angmǝ a gerpo yende na, “Ayo kedeya togomo ta shili ka oromo ooka wa waale ebelo e rere ara awai.
\v 25 Awere aka aromo neya malau, na oja okara wai ale na wa waale a belo o wake yende ara o alkama me, awa sokoo ale.
\v 26 Nangka ebelo me e ere na eye eyo, na owake me kang gongha.
\v 27 Na azara ateakwilǝ me ne de, na ne bekaa wai na, ‘Ateakwilǝ, teya beya na ebelo erere ba waale ara au sang? A wiinia na mawake ma surǝ ara ame?
\v 28 Nawa kabare ne na, ‘Oja okara waya nyimi.’ Na azara me pirkǝ wai na, ‘Oya yeme aa te ale kate lope mawake mame na?
\p 
\v 29 Aa wa bekaa nee na, ‘Nyimia dai, bayana, tana azaa olopa mawake e gwaara ka o alkama me ne.
\v 30 Baya na ne aa gong legwa a ale awere o shende. A were o shende me kangza eyang bekaa ana o shende me, kane bore ka oshende mawake mame, a ne kurki mawake mame, aane tese kane ese, aane shende o alkama me ka ne kare aa benga.’ ”
\s1 A ngmǝ a gerpo azaa o yisti ka o mosta
\r (Mar 4:30-32; Luk 13:18-19)
\p 
\v 31 Na Yeso bekaa ne a ngmǝ a gerpo kangza na, “Togomo te shili teya baate na beyo be o mosta, emea oromo yende wa ale kawa kpeene ara awai.
\v 32 Eya kala a bee baate a nyimi eyo, aa ee gongha, e kala kombela uti o marane, kawa itǝ uti oo gong, ka engmeng soze todo ee bana me.
\p 
\v 33 Kangza Yeso ka bele ne angmǝ gerpo yende na, “Togomo te Ashili teye na o yisti, ooka ondaye yende wa jeke nawa sakale ka maso ma taaro ma'ena ma o alkama, na ma sakalnang ka ma o yisti me.
\p 
\v 34 Na Yeso bele okurkǝnǝng aromo, pate epaname a nyimi angmǝ aa gerpo. Kata ka baaleze eyapa ne soona aa nyimi angmǝ gerpo.
\v 35 Aye nyimia ka panza o bekaa ondo beya ngmǝ mawo Ashili Ishaya na,
\q1 “Eyang beya angmǝ a nyimi ngmǝ a gerpo,
\q2 Eyang beka epa eeka a baasa obora lerambo.”\x - \xo 13:35 \xt Sel 78:2.\x*
\s1 Masanto azaa mawake a nyimi o alkama
\p 
\v 36 Na Yeso baya aromo acake me, aaka lyǝ akwilǝ. Na atoma kai kangza ne deya kai, na ne bekaa na, “Bele ro masanto ma angmǝ gerpo aza mawake ara.”
\p 
\v 37 Aaka kabare na, “Ondo owaale ebelo erere name, waya Kena ka Oromo.
\v 38 Aa ara ame, aya lerambo leena, ebelo erere name, neya ayana a togomo te Ashili, kangza mawake mame maya ayana ogomo ara a buru.
\v 39 Oja okara ka wa waale owake, waya ogomo ara a buru. Awere oshende me aya lengme le maare o lerambo leena, ana o shende me neya atoma Ashili o surǝ azaa shili.
\v 40 Nangka kurki mawake ka ese mai, nyimia wayo itǝ a lengme le omaare.
\v 41 Kena ka Oromo kayo tonga atoma kai o surǝ azaa shili, kane shende ana o ote aromo kane rizi, kangza kaa pate ana o eza epa eburu, kane sǝǝrǝ ne a nyimi togomo te kai,
\v 42 kangza kane tare ne a nyimi ola o kpwaiye. A saname neya ruuzi ka o nonza tuuni.
\v 43 A were namea ana o eza epa erere, masanto mane mayo surǝ na ongme a nyimi togomo te Ate ane. Ondooka waya ka toto to kona, awa kone.”
\s1 A ngmǝ a gerpo azaa ocǝ ka a baasa
\p 
\v 44 Togomo te Ashili teye na ocǝa ka a baasa nyimi ara, ooka ondo wa cǝ nawa kang baasa. A nyimi zanta wai, nawa ale nawa lishi pate epa eeka waye ka e nawa embe ara me.”
\p 
\v 45 Kangza togomo te Ashili teye na ondo ejamanea, ooka waya gera acale aa rere ka aye kaa emate.
\v 46 Nangka wa cǝ lecale le yende lee rere acak, na wa ale nawa lishi pate epa eeka waye ka e, na wa embe ai.”
\s1 A ngmǝ a gerpo azaa ojara o meese ekwala
\p 
\v 47 Kangza Togomo te Ashili teye na ojara o meese ekwala ooka tare a lepong, nawa meke kombela ekwala.
\v 48 Nangka wa pene, naa windi wai o wulu lepong, nane cikǝ ane zake e kwala ee rere e me nane kare a nyimi o kende, aa ne oke eburu me.
\v 49 Nyimia wayo itǝ a lengme le omare. Atoma Ashili o surǝ azaa shili neyo sǝǝrǝ ana ara aburu nyimi aromo a rere.
\v 50 Ka ne tare ana ara aburu a nyimi ola o kpwaiye, aa sanamea neyo ruuzi ko nonza tuuni.
\p 
\v 51 “E rose epaena pate na?”
\p Na ne kabare na “Eeye.”
\p 
\v 52 Naka bekaa nee na, “Pate ondo o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili nya Mosa wa itǝ ondo tare togomo te Ashili, wa itǝ na ateakwilǝ, ondooka wa mangka ocǝ osau ka o kozo ara a le'eke lewai.”
\s1 A nyane Yeso ba Nazarat
\r (Mar 6:1-6; Luk 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Nangka Yeso ka mare obeya angmǝ aa gerpo name naka baya arame.
\v 54 Ko deya a peng kai, naka bore o baala aromo oo dandaro o ogwarzanang one. Na epa me tere ne ukpwei na ne beke na, “Karomo kaana ka cǝ orosa ka epa o tera ukpwei aa ba?
\v 55 Teya beyana kanna, kena ka o ondo cocoza sang? Iini kai kaya Mariya sang? Arone kai neya Yakubu, Yusupu, ka Saminu, kangza kaa Yahuda sang?
\v 56 Arone kai andaye neya ara yendea kaa ro sang? Karomo kaana ka cǝ epa eena ba?
\v 57 Na ne kone oburǝ okai.
\p Na Yeso bekaanee na, “Ondo obeya ngmǝ ka mawo Ashili ata kabare ka wai a nyimi apeng awai kaa kwilǝ awai ne.
\v 58 Naka ta eza epa otera ukpwei a cake a saname ne, a za odera okabare ka Ashili one.
\c 14
\s1 O gwǝ o Yohana o Batisma
\r (Mar 6:14-29; Luk 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 1 A were name Ogomo Hiridus Antipas wa kone oroka azaa Yeso.
\v 2 Nawa bekaa azara wai na, “Ondoonaa Yohana o Batisma, waya a ara wai malo ogwǝ, nyimia wa ote na waya kaa o bare o eza epa otera ukpwei na.”
\v 3 Obena Hiridus wa meke Yohana na tere wai, aa ote wai a akwilǝ andaleme azaa Herodiya ondaye orone owai Pilibus.
\v 4 Azaa bena Yohana wa beeze awai na wa ta gwara awa ana Herodiya ka ka itǝ ondaye wai ne.
\v 5 Pate ka o bena Hiridus waya yeme wonga Yohana, aa waya kona boome be aromo, aa ne jeke o bena Yohana ondo beya ngmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wai.
\p 
\v 6 Nangka lengme le o ngmenga o Hiridus le dukǝ, na kagala ka Herodiya ka yo leera a begeshe be aromo kane de ara o zǝnggǝ me, na Hiridus kone oleba maleo,
\v 7 nawa tono a kai na wayo nya kai pate epa eeka ka bosa.
\v 8 Na iini kai bekaa kai na ale ka o bekaana, “A nyau ukpwei o Yohana o Batisma nannameena a nyimi oso.”
\v 9 Na ogomo kone oburu, aza obena wa tono abegeshe be ageng wai, nawa ote na a nya kai epa eeka kaa bosa.
\v 10 Nawa tong na core ukpwei o Yohana a akwilǝ andaleme,
\v 11 na de ka ukpwei me a nyimi oso na nya kagala ka me, na ka ca iini kai.
\v 12 Na ana o tare Yohana de nane ana ekeze me, na ne taashe, aa ne ale na ne beka Yeso.
\s1 Yeso ka lye ka aromo magu esu
\r (Mar 6:30-44; Luk 9:10-17; Yoh 6:1-14)
\p 
\v 13 Nangka Yeso ka kone nyimi, naka ere naka lyǝ o onggo o taara manyi aaka ale ara aaka aromo ta rene ne ka ka cikǝ a yende. Nangka aromo acak ne kone nyimi, na ne surǝ a topepeng na ne tare kai a tobona.
\v 14 Ka o surǝ kai o onggo o tara manyi naka laka leguki le aromo. Naka kone egonegone o ne, naka womza ana makono nyimi o ne.
\p 
\v 15 Nangka ulyǝlu waye, na atoma kai de akai na ne bekaa na, “Ara na a aromo ta rene ne, a waana ulyǝlu waya. Baya aromo ana ane ale a topepeng kane gere tukpwei tone epaolya.”
\p 
\v 16 Na Yeso bekaa ne na, “Wata gwara aane ale ne, nyana ne eyapa ka ne lye.”
\p 
\v 17 Na ne kabare na, “Teta ka eyapa arakaname, soona maborode esu ka ekwala e leere.”
\s1 Maborode esu ka ekwala leere
\p 
\v 18 Na ka bekaa na, “Deyana ka e arakaana.”
\v 19 Aaka ote aromo me na ne cikǝ azaa mawake. Naka jeke, maborode esu ka ekwala leere, naka ara ukpwei aaza shili, aaka sabe Ashili, naka pose maborode mame aaka nyaza atoma kai, a atoma me kangza aa ne nyaza aromo.
\v 20 A pate one ne lye na ne tiyǝ, na ne kurki o dangare me, nawa panza makende betuuru ka maleere.
\v 21 Andaaka ne lye ne dukǝ andaleme magu esu bangka andaye ka ayana.
\s1 Yeso ka yeng azaa manyi
\r (Mar 6:45-52; Yoh 6:16-21)
\p 
\v 22 Ka o mara me naka ote atoma kai na ne lyǝ o onggo o tara manyi ka ne kaana kai a ale owulu o sara yende. Aa kai ka itǝ a dimǝ ka ka laka o aleze a tokwilǝ te aromo me.
\v 23 Malo ale aromo me, naka zale oyara kai a yende kaka beye angmǝ ka Ashili. Na ulyǝlu ye aa kaya yende saname.
\v 24 A wereme o onggo o taara manyi waya tera lepong, na sejǝng se manyi se ere ka legoone, obena obere me waya kara ka ne.
\p 
\v 25 Aa ra aa dukǝ beru bo taaro be lelere, na Yeso yeng azaa manyi aaka dore ne.
\v 26 Nangka atoma ne laka kai aa yenga azaa manyi na boome meke ne nane bekaana, “Bebua be!” Nane gware bekoko azaa obena nee kona boome.
\v 27 A saseya naka bekaa nee na, “Kane kone boome ne Mea. Kane kone boome ne.”
\v 28 Na Biturusu kabare wai na, “Ateokora boa baaza, oteng kang deya bo aa yenga azaa manyi.”
\p 
\v 29 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Deya.” Na Biturusu suri o onggo o taara manyi, nawa yeng azaa manyi a wa dore Yeso.
\v 30 Awereaka wa laka obere wa ere a jǝng nawa kone boome. Nangka manyi ma bore dongha wai nawa rurai, awa bekaa na, “Ateokora bozang!”
\v 31 Aa saseya na Yeso nayi o ara naka meke wai, aaka bekaa wai na, “Bo o kabare ka Ashili au wa sawa, eya e ote na ba dambaraza?”
\v 32 Ka o lyǝ one o onggo o taara manyi na obere me tete.
\v 33 Andaaka neya a nyimi onggo o tara manyi ma me na ne girwǝ ane bekaa na, “Bo dongdong, Kena ka Ashili kai!”
\s1 Yeso ka womza ana o dera o kona zake aa Janasarata
\r (Mar 6:53-56)
\p 
\v 34 Nangka ne tare opong ome, na ne lyǝ a makeke ma Janasarata.
\v 35 Nangka aromo apeng me ne rose bena Yesoa kai, na ne tongze a kombela aromo apat a topepeng te ma'amo, na ne casa kai ana makono,
\v 36 Na ne boshe kai na ka kabare aa ne cocome edǝki odibi kai. Pate andaaka ne cocome na ne woma.
\c 15
\s1 Makili ma anateandaasau
\r (Mar 7:1-13)
\p 
\v 1 Na ana ondo ba nyimi maParisa kaa ana o baala angmǝ aka Ashili a nya Mosa nane deya Yeso a ne surǝ ba Urushalima nane bekaa na,
\v 2 “Eyaaka atoma au neta tare makili mana Anateandaasau ne? O bena neta sabozo zongka ne lye epaolya ne.”
\p 
\v 3 Na Yeso kabare nee na, “Eyaaka ying eta tare makili ma Ashili ne e tare makili maying?
\v 4 Ashili a bekaa na, ‘Tare ate au, ka iini au, kangza pate ondooka wa zeela ate ka iini wai wa gwara aa wongha wai.’\x - \xo 15:4 \xt Osur 20:12; 21:17; Otik 5:16; Mag 20:9.\x*
\v 5 Ying e baale na, ‘Pate ondooka wa bekaa ate ka iini wai na, epaaka maa ya kankama oying ka e, ma nya Ashili,’
\v 6 wa nyana otare ate kaa iini wai ka e ne, azaa nyimi ee cakate angmǝ Ashili azaa makili maying naname.
\v 7 Ying ana rendaza, Ishaya ondo beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wa beke oroka Ashili aza oying aa kap na,
\q1 
\v 8 “Aromo ana, ne tareng ka ongmǝ belle,
\q2 aa nyimi anyong ane neya macangcang kaa mi.
\q1 
\v 9 O girwǝ one aa mi taa ka edang ne,
\q2 obaala one o tare makili ma aromo,
\q2 o bena aya angmǝ Ashili.”
\s1 Mapa maaka ma care oromo
\r (Mar 7:1-13)
\p 
\v 10 Na Yeso rare o kurkǝnǝng aromo acak, aa ka bekaa nee na, “Konana ekang rosa.
\v 11 Epa eeka e lyǝzǝ ongmǝ oromo eta ote ka wa ye ka madinǝ ne, soona epa eeka e susi ba ongmǝ eya ote ka oromo wa itǝ ka madinǝ.”
\v 12 Na atoma kai ne deya kai nane bekaa kai na, “Orose obena maParisa ne kona o burǝ ka ne kona a angmǝ aa na?”
\v 13 Na Yeso kabare na, “Pate epa eeka Ate ang o zaa shili ta wa gata ne, ayo mukǝ.
\v 14 Arnang ka ne, ne arǝ ne ka neya windǝ arǝ lebenda. Urǝ wa windǝ urǝ lebenda, pate one neya kala a le'o.”\x - \xo 15:14 \xt Luk 6:39.\x*
\p 
\v 15 Na Biturusu bekaa na, “Bele ro masanto ma angmǝ aa gerpo ana ka ba beka.”
\p 
\v 16 Na Yeso pirkǝ nee na, “A alea aa were aana e tata a maring na?
\v 17 Eta rosa obena pate epa eeka e lyǝ ongmǝ e ale a lebangi e suri ba lepung sang?
\v 18 A epaaka e susi ba ongmǝ e suri ba lenyong. Epa o susǝ a lenyong leme eya ote oromo ka wa itǝ ka madinǝ a begeshe ba Ashili.
\v 19 Azaa o bena aa nyimi lenyong leyaa sǝrsǝzǝ madoola maa buru. Naa, o wongha oromo, o mora kaa ondaye ondo, o mora kaa Ogala, o eza bekǝri, o ana angmǝ, ka o cara leze.
\v 20 Ennaa ote oromo kawa itǝ ka madinǝ a begeshe ba Ashili, o lya epa olya zora o sabo waya ta ote ka oromo waye ka madinǝ a begeshe ba Ashili ne.”
\s1 O eke lenyong a Ashili ondaaye o makeke ma Kan'ana
\r (Mar 7:24-30)
\p 
\v 21 Nangka Yeso ka baya arakaname, naka ale a makeke ma Taya ka Sidon.
\v 22 Na ondaye yende ka makeke ma Kan'ana deya a Yeso ka oruuzi na, “Kona egonegone eng Ateokora, kena ka Daoda, bozang, kagala kang obere o buru ooka waya nyimi kai waya zo gara kai.”
\p 
\v 23 Na Yeso ta beka eyapa a wai ne. Aza nyimi na atoma kai ne deya a kai nane bosa kai na, “Tarangga wai kawa ale waya tare oro awa gare ro ka be koko.”
\p 
\v 24 Naka kabare na, “Mi aa tonghang azaa emande epeng e Isrela kane wilǝ belle.”
\p 
\v 25 Na ondaye ome wa deya nawa girwǝ ba ting kai aaka bose kai kangza na, “Ateokora kangkamang!”
\v 26 Na Yeso kabare na, “Wata gwara a jeke epa olya ayana ka kare e ere ne.”
\p 
\v 27 Na ondaaye me bekaa na, “Nyimia Ateokora, pate kaa nyimi, e ere donge ma ngmeskarong maaka ma taaru ba deze araaka ateakwilǝ lyeeze epa olya ne.”
\s1 Yeso ka lye ka aromo magu ma naaze
\p 
\v 28 Na Yeso kabare naka bekaa ondaye me na, “Ondaye o eke lenyong leo ba Ashili wa gong, baya epa eeka oya gera me, e itǝ nyimi.” Ka o bekaa nyimi na obere oburu me wa arnang ka kagala kame.
\s1 Yeso ka womza aromo aa cake
\p 
\v 29 Nangka Yeso ka baya a rame naka tare bee dǝki lepong le Galili. Naka zale ba zaa oyara naka cikǝ ba saname.
\v 30 Na aromo acak ne deya kai. Nane de kaa ana ozantǝ, arǝ, agǝdǝ, ka arara, aa ana ondo ba cak, nane eke ne aa begeshe be Yeso naka womza ne.
\v 31 Na epame tere apate aromo tukpwei azaa obena arara neya beya ngmǝ, agǝdǝ ya teweno, arǝ neya gonta, na pate one ne saba Ashili a maIsrela.
\s1 Yeso ka lye kaa aromo magu ma naaze
\r (Mar 8:1)
\p 
\v 32 Azaa nyimi na Yeso ka rare atoma o kai naka bekaa nee na, “Eyang kona egonegone aromo aana, tomore to taaro naana o ngmeengme teye legwa kaane aa neta ne lya epa olya ne, kangza anta yeme o baya one aane ale ekomo ne adorana tana ne sau orona ne.”
\p 
\v 33 Na atoma kai ne kabare nane bekaa kai na, “A baba te era a te cǝ epaolya a nyimi lerambo leena kate nya aromo acake aana?”
\p 
\v 34 Na Yeso pirkǝ nee na, “Ma borode ma wondaa eye kaa mai?”
\p Nane kabare na, “O sondaare kaa ekwala a baate.”
\p 
\v 35 Naka ote aromo aa cake name nane cikǝ ba deze,
\v 36 Nangka ka jeke maborode o sondaare ka ekwala me, naka wore o kona oleba ba Ashili, aaka pose mai aaka nya atoma kai, na nee kangza ne arseze aromo amea ne kurkǝnǝng.
\v 37 Pate one ne lye na komana one tii, na atoma kurki ma ngmeskarong maaka ma lyǝ nama panza makende ma moole sondaare.
\v 38 O gongha aromo aaka ne lye epaolya me ne dukǝ andaleme magu ma naaze bangka andaye kaa ayana.
\v 39 Malo arnang ka aromo me, naka zale o onggo o taara manyi naka ale a makeke ma magadan.
\c 16
\s1 Ogera epa otera ukpwei
\r (Mar 8:11-13; Luk 12:54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Na maParisa kaa maSadukiya ne deya a Yeso adorana ne kedeya kai, nane bose kai ka ka wore ne epa o tera ukpwei ooka wayo wore o bare o kai.
\v 2 Naka kabare nee na, “Ulyǝlu waaya, ke laka azaa shili aaya aa ganggo e bekaana, ‘Ahaa, ara yo ya aa sangsang leere.’
\v 3 Ara a sana a leleere kangza e laka azaa shili aya a ganggo, na masanto mame maa kabare kuruwǝ ee bena, ‘Ulyi wayo ngmeza o ngmeengme.’ E ama orosa nangka zaa shili ze, aa eta ama orosa epaeka awere ana ya nyimi me ne.
\v 4 Aromo awere ana, ana odera o tare Ashili, ana leyau, ana a nyong aburu, ana ogera epa otera ukpwei, aa ato wore ne epa o tera ukpwei ne, soona e Yonana.
\p Na Yeso arnang ka ne a ka ale.
\s1 O yisti o maParisa ka maSadukiya
\r (Mar 8:14-21)
\p 
\v 5 Nangka atoma Yeso ne cakate aa ale owulu lepong leme, nane winǝ o jeka oborode.
\v 6 Na Yeso bekaa ne naa, “Eza na ba sauwo, ka o yisti o maParisa kaa o maSadukiya.”
\p 
\v 7 Na ne bore o pirǝ tukpwei tone na, “Ka beka epaana ba eza azaa obena teta te deya ko borode ne na?”
\p 
\v 8 Nangka Yeso ka laka nyimi, a ka rose madoola mane naka beka nee na, “Ying ana o kabare kaa mi aa baate, eyaaka eya masanggo obena eta ka o borode ne?
\v 9 Aa deya wereena e tata a maring na? E winǝ nangka ma lye ka aromo magu esu ka a agwataka ma o borode maaname esu sang? Makende ma wonda e panza kaa maa epa eeka e lyǝ?
\v 10 Koona awere aaka ma lye ka aromo magu ma naaze ka ma borode o sondaare, makende ma wonda e panza kaa epa eeka e lyǝ?
\v 11 Eyaka eta ama o rosa obena anta beya oroka aza o borode ne? Epa eka eyang yeme e rose eya ezana ba sauwo ka o yisti o maParisa kaa maSadukiya.”
\v 12 Arakanamea atoma Yeso ne rose obena kataa beya a zo yisti o kareze ba o borode ne, aa kaya beya kane eza ba sauwo kaa obaala maParisa kaa maSadukiya.
\s1 Biturusu wa wore o kabare kaa Kiristi
\r (Mar 8:27-30; Luk 9:18-21)
\p 
\v 13 Nangka Yeso ka de aa bekazo be makeke ma Kaisariya o Pilibi, naka pirkǝ atoma kai na, “Aromo ne beya kena ka oromo na mana kai?”
\p 
\v 14 Na ne kabare na, “Ana ondo ne beya na Yohana o Batisma, aana ondo beya na Iliya, aana ondo kangza beya naa, Irimiya, na ondo ba nyimi ana o beya angmǝ kama mawo ma Ashili.”
\p 
\v 15 Naka pirkǝ nee na, “A ying pa, e beye na mia mana?”
\v 16 Na Siman Biturusu kabare na, “Boa Almasipu, Kena ka Ashili ondo ebeene.”
\v 17 Na Yeso kabare naka bekaa wai na, “Bo ondo kona oleba wai, Siman kena ka Yonana! Obena oromo ka lepung ka manyau waya ta waa belo ne, soona Ate ang omea waya nyimia shili.
\v 18 Eyang bele au, boa Biturusu, azaa lecale leena eyang sowa akwilǝ ang, aaka legoone le ogbwǝ leto ama kaa ai ne.
\v 19 Eyang nyau becapa be togomo to shili. Kangza epaaka ba tera a lerambo leena, eyo itǝ nyimi ba zaa shili, a epaaka ba dinggǝ a lerambo leena eyo itǝ ka o dinggǝ a nyimia shili.”
\v 20 Naka windi atoma kai toto na tana ne bele ondo na kai ya Almasipu ne.
\s1 Yeso ka bele nangka kayo gbwǝ
\r (Mar 8:31-9:1; Luk 9:22-27)
\p 
\v 21 Oo era lengme lenname na ka bore o wore atoma kai na kayo dongdong ale ba Urushalima, a sanamea kayo lyǝ kombela o zitǝ aa taara te anateandasau, kaa ana magame ma Ashili, kaa ana obaala angmǝ ka Ashili a nya Mosa, kangza aane wongha kai, aa lengme le o taaro aaka era ka ebeene.”
\p 
\v 22 Na Biturusu kuri ka Yeso aa sara yende nawa zurki kai na, “Tana Ashili baya epaana eye ne, Ateokora! Enna to manau ne.”
\v 23 Na Yeso ringgarnu naka beka a Biturusu na, “Arnang kaa mi, Shetan! Bo epaa o ote ong kang cǝwǝ, bo o eze madoola mau ma oromoa, ma Ashili ta za ne.”
\p 
\v 24 Na Yeso ka bekaa atoma kai na, “Pate ondooka waya yeme o tare ong, awa nyane ukpwei o wai a wa ana uti o gendare o wai a wa tareng.
\v 25 Pate ondooka waya yeme o boza ebeene e wai, wayo dera e. Aa ondooka wayo dera ebeene e wai a za ong, wayo cǝ e.
\v 26 Ebelo epa edang ngha oromo yo cǝ, wa cǝ pate lerambo leena a wa dera ebene e wai? Eya oromo wa era wa nya aa bekazo be ebeene e wai?
\v 27 Kena ka oromo kaya deya ka togomo te Ate o kai kaa aa toma ozaa shili, kangza kayo nya komana epaaka e itǝ e wai a zo ogole omea komana wa eza.
\v 28 “Ang dongdong bele ying, ana ondo ka neya itǝ arakana neto gbwǝ ne, seeka ne laka o deya kena ka Oromo ba nyimi togomo te kai.”
\c 17
\s1 Lepung le Yeso sara
\r (Mar 9:2-13; Luk 9:28-36)
\p 
\v 1 Malo tomore o taashe na Yeso ka jeke Biturusu, ka Yakubu, a orone kai oka a beya wai na Yohana, naka ale kaa ne o oyara o yende oo zaati, na ne cikǝ saname ne belle.
\v 2 Na nangka kaze, sara aa begeshe bene, na mainu ma kai ma santo na ongme, aa madibi maaka ka amba, na ma itǝ maa peng.
\v 3 Na ongmere liizi, na ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Mosa ka Iliya ne surǝ baa tera one a neya beya angmǝ ka Yeso.
\p 
\v 4 Na Biturusu beka Yeso na, “Ateokora, wa gwara ka teye arakana. Ba kabare ang sowa mapuki ma taaro arakana, oyende a au, a oyende o Mosa a oyende kangza o Iliya.”
\p 
\v 5 Waya zo beya angmǝ naname na owere yende oma santo wa urǝ ne, aane kone lengmelo le yende ba nyimi owere me a le beka na, “Kando kaana kena kang, ka oyeme ong maleo, ang kang kona oleba kai. Konana kai!”
\p 
\v 6 Nangka atoma kai ne kone nyimi na boome moke ne maleu, na ne rizi baa deze.
\v 7 Na Yeso ka de naka cokome ne aaka bekaa nee na, “Erana a itǝ, tane kone boome ne.”
\v 8 Nangka ne ara tukpwei, nane ta laka ondo ne soona Yeso kai aa yende.
\p 
\v 9 Aa neya zo jipi oyara me, na Yeso ka windi ne toto na, “Tane bele ondo epaaka e laka ne, soona aa ara Kena ka Oromo malo ogbwǝ kai.”
\p 
\v 10 Na atoma kai ne pirkǝ kai na, “Nyimia waaza, eyaka ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nyana Mosa ne beeze na dongdong Otoma Ashili Iliya waya yaa deya o bora?”
\p 
\v 11 Na Yeso kabare na, “Iliya wayo dongdong deya kawa babara ekeeya.
\v 12 Pate ka nyimi eyang bele oying, Iliya wa samba o deya, na eta ee rose naa waya ne, nane eze wai epaaka ne ama o ezaa me. Nyimia kangza Kena ka Oromo yo zitǝ ba taara tone.”
\p 
\v 13 Na atoma Yeso ne rose obena kaya beya one a ngmǝ ba zaa Yohana ondo batisma.
\s1 Yeso ka womza kena kamea obere o buru wa taba kai
\r (Mar 9:14-29; Luk 9:37-43)
\p 
\v 14 Nangka ne dukǝ araaka aromo ne gwarnang ne, na oromo yende wa deya Yeso nawa girwǝ ba begeshe be kai awa bekaa na,
\v 15 “Ateokora, kona egonegone kena kang, ka ya ka letaranggi, kangza leya gǝǝzǝ kai maleo. Le rabo aa peere okai a nyimi ola kaa nyimi manyi.
\v 16 Nang ale ka kai a atoma au, nane ta ama o womza kai ne.”
\p 
\v 17 Na Yeso kabare naka bekaa na, “Ying aromo awereena, ana o dera o kabare ka Ashili, kangza ana ara aburu! Aa alea aa werea yemea eyang cikǝ ba nyimi oying? Aa alea aa werea yemea ang motana ka ying? Deyana ka kai arakana.”
\v 18 Na Yeso ka zurki obere oburu me, na obere oburu me wa arnang ka kena kame. Na o ngmere liizi na kena kame ka woma.
\p 
\v 19 Na atoma Yeso ne deya kai ba sara yende, na ne pirkǝ kai na, “Eyaka teta te ama o sǝǝrǝ obere oburu me ne?”
\v 20 Na Yeso bekaa nee na, “O kabare ka Ashili oying wata gongha ne. Eyang dongdong bele oying, eeya ka o kabare kaa Ashili na beyo bee baate be o mosta, eyo ama bekaa oyara na wa mukuru araaka wa zene, kawa ye nyimi. Eyapa eto girǝ ying ne.
\v 21 Ebelo onname, wata susǝ ne soona ka obeya angmǝ ka Ashili kangza ka opate ongmǝ.”
\s1 Yeso ka wale o beka angmǝ azaa o gbwǝ kai
\r (Mar 9:30-32; Luk 9:43-45)
\p 
\v 22 Nangka atoma Yeso ne kurkǝnǝng a makeke ma Galili, na Yeso ka bekaa nee na, “Ayo nya Kena ka Oromo ba taara ta aromo,
\v 23 neyo wongha kai. Aa lengme lo taaro kangza ayo ara kai.” Na pate one ne kone oburǝ.
\s1 O ara emate makeke
\p 
\v 24 Malooka Yeso kaa atoma kai ne dukǝ Kaparnahum, na ana o eesa e mate akwilǝ Ashili nane mana Biturusu, na ne pirkǝ wai na, “Ondo baala oying wata nyaza emate akwilǝ Ashili ne na?”
\p 
\v 25 Nawa bekaa na, “Ka arseze. “Nangka wa kurǝ ba akwilǝ, na Yeso bora o beya angmǝ ka wai naka beka na, “Ba laka nannia Siman Biturusu azaa be pirǝ beena? Aana mana agomo lerambo leena ne eesa emate e makeke ne, ara ayana anea naa, ana ondoai?”
\v 26 Na Biturusu kabare na, “Aana ondo,” na Yeso bekaa na, “Obena ayana ane ta arsaza ne.
\v 27 Pate ka nyimi, adorana tana aromo me ne mungi kaa ro ne, ale ba lepong ka o tare beruu be omeese ekwala, bekwala beeka baa bora a moke me o pǝri ongmǝ be oyo cǝ emate eeka eyo bare. O jeke mate me ka o are e mate makeke mau kaa a‘eng.”
\c 18
\s1 Be pirǝ azaa ondo o kala o gongha
\r (Mar 9:33-37; Luk 9:46-48)
\p 
\v 1 Awere name na atoma Yeso ne deya akai, nane pirkǝ na, “Mana kala o gongha a nyimi togomo te zaa shili?”
\v 2 Naka rare kena ka baate ka yende, naka eke kai baa tera one,
\v 3 aka bekaa na, “Eyang dongdong bele oying, eeta kurǝ ka e itǝ naa abana ayana aana ne, eto lyǝ ba togomo ta zaa shili ne.
\v 4 Pate ondooka wa jipǝrǝ ukpwei wai naa ka bana kena kaana, waya wa kala o gongha a togomo te zaa shili.
\v 5 Pate ondooka wa kabare ka kabana kena naa kaana, mia wa embang.”
\s1 Mapapa ma o ote o cǝwǝ
\r (Mar 9:42-48; Luk 17:1-2)
\p 
\v 6 Pate ka nyimi, ondooka wa ote kena ka yende ba nyimi abana ayana aaka ne kabare kaa mi ka ka ye madinǝ, wayo kala aa tere wai onyanto aa lengmelo, a tare wai ba nyimi o pong o gerpo.”
\p 
\v 7 Ee lyǝ udi lerambo, aza epa eeka e oteze aromo kane ye madinǝ! Dongdong ngha ebelo epaana eye, pate ka nyimi ondo ote ka a cǝwǝ, wa lyǝ udi.
\v 8 Aa o ara o, na obona o, wa ote ka o lyǝ a madinǝ, mara o core wa ka opere. Wa kala o lyǝ ara e ebeene o dera o maro kaa o ara yende, na obona yende, na ka legǝdǝ, koo bena tareo ola kaa wata lumbuzu ne ka tobona to leere, ka taara te leere teo a pate.
\v 9 Kangza Liizi leo le otezeo ko lyǝ a madinǝ lopa le ka o pere. Wa gwara o lyǝ ara ebene o dera o maro ka liizi le yende, ka o bena o ale akwilǝ ola ka yizi leere.”
\s1 A ngmǝ aa gerpo azaa o mande openg kawa wilǝ
\r (Luk 15:3-7)
\p 
\v 10 “Ekena toto, tane zeele kena ka yende baa nyimia ayana na ne. Eyang belo ying, atoma ane o dera apung o nyimia shili ne gonte mainu ma Ate ang omea waya nyimia shili konang were.
\v 11 Obena Kena ka Oromo ka deya ka ka boze andaaka ne wilǝ.
\v 12 “Eya madoola maying? Ondo waya ka emande lewinu, na kayende ka wilǝ, wato baya etuuru torai ka o torai name aa ting oyara aa wa ale ba gera ka yende kanname sang?
\v 13 Wa cǝ kai, eyang dongdong bele oying, wayo kona oleba maleo o kala etuuru torai ka otorai eeka eta e wilǝ ne.
\v 14 Nyimia, Ate oying azaa shili wato kona oleba a kena ka yende ba nyimi ayana na ka wili ne.”
\s1 Orone ka wa tambo
\r (Luk 17:3)
\p 
\v 15 “Aa orone o wa yau tambo bo, o ale ka o bele wai epaaka wa yau, ying ngha leere belle. Wa kona epaaka ba bele wai, baa kuriyǝ orone o orona naname.
\v 16 Waata konau ne, o ale ka oromo yende na a leere kane laka aane kone, adorana angmǝ me itǝ ka ma ganggang a begeshe be aromo leere, na a taaro.
\v 17 Wa nyana kona one, o bele akwilǝ ana o tare Ashili, kangza waata kona nee ne, o kuriyǝ wai a nyimi andaaka neta rosa Ashili ne na ondo eesa emate o makeke.”
\p 
\v 18 “Eyang dongdong bele oying, pate epaaka e tera a lerambo leena, awa itǝ epaaka a samba o tera me ba zaa shili. Pate epaaka e dinggǝ a lerambo leena, eyo itǝ ka o dinggǝ a zaa shili.
\p 
\v 19 “Eyang dongdong wala o bele oying na, aromo leere ba nyimi lerambo leena ne kabare ka tukpwei tone ba za epaaka neya bosa me, Ate ang omea waya nyimia zaa shili wayo nya ne.
\v 20 Pate araaka aromo leere, na a taaro ne gwarnang ba nyimi leze leng, eyang cikǝ legwa kaa ne.”
\s1 Ozara ooka wata pisǝzǝ epa eeka ya wa ne
\p 
\v 21 Na Biturusu paka ting Yeso nawa pirkǝ na, “Ateokora, ka wondaa orone ong wa tambo a mi ang pisi wai? Ka o sondaare na?”
\v 22 Na Yeso bekaa na, “Ka o sondaare belle dai, ka o sondaarea o dukǝa etuuru sondaare.
\p 
\v 23 “Aza nyimi ayo kedeya togomo te a zaa shili ka ogomo omea waya yeme o eza abalo ocǝ wai ka eeya taara te azara wai.
\v 24 Nangka wa bore obala ocǝ wai me, naa de ka ondo omea ogomo me tare wai emate magu betuuru.
\v 25 O bena wato ama o ara me ne, na ateakwilǝ wai wa ote ka a lishi wai ka ondaye wai ka ayana wai ka pate magogoro ma wai, ka a are uduru me.
\v 26 Na ozara me tunggunu a begeshe be wai a wa bose wai na, “Ateakwilǝ tana o mungi ne, eyang arau ba pat.”
\v 27 A aza obena ateakwilǝ me wa kone egonegone ozara me, nawa baya a wai kaa uduru me.
\v 28 “Nangka ozara me wa ere arakaname, ka o surǝ wai nawa laka oja lezara awai, ka wa tare wai uduru o kap, emate lewinu. Nawa moke lengmelo le wai, a wa beka wai na, “Arang pate epaaka ang taroo.”
\v 29 Na oja lezara me bose wai naa tana wa mungi ne eyang arau.”
\v 30 Na ozara me ta kabare ne, nyimia na wa ale ka wai na pate wai akwilǝ andaleme, seena wa are emate uduru me.
\v 31 Nangka aja lezara le wai ne kone epaaka eya ale, neta ne kone oleba nyimi ne. Nane ale ba ateakwilǝ one nane bele wai epaaka ozara name wa ya.
\v 32 Na ateakwilǝ me wa rare wai, nawa beka wai na, “Bo ozara oburua wai. Ma bayau ka uduru ooka ang taro aza obena ba de na obosheng,
\v 33 wa ta gwara o kone egonegone o beja be lezara lo nangka maa kona egonegone o sang?”
\v 34 Na ateakwilǝ wai wa mungi ka wai, aa wa ote na a gǝǝzǝ wai, aa wa ote wai na wa are pate epaaka a tare wai.
\v 35 Nyimia kangza Ate ang o nyimia zaa shili wayo ya kaa komana o ying, eeta pisǝ andaa ying kaa lenyong le yende ne.”
\c 19
\s1 Be pirǝ azaa o maro o amare
\r (Mar 10:1-12; Luk 16:18)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka mare obeya angmǝ me a pate, naka baya makeke ma Galili aaka lyǝ aa makeke ma Yahudiya, mamea mayo o tara obeno Urdung.
\v 2 Na aromo a cak ne tare kai, naka womza ana makono aa saname.
\p 
\v 3 Na maParisa ma yende ne deya a kai adorana ne kedeya kai, nane pirǝ na, “Azaa o baala makili Mosa, wa gwara obena oromo wa pere ondaye o wai aza ekeeya na?”
\p 
\v 4 Naka kabare nee na, “Eta tukǝ soola obena, ondooka wa ye ne o bora, wa ye nea ondaleme kaa ondaye sang?”
\v 5 Na akang bekaana, “Aza nyimi, oromo wa arnang kaa iini wai kaa ate a wai, a wa gwarnang ondaye wai. Neya leere kane itǝ lepung le yende.\x - \xo 19:5 \xt Obo 2:24.\x*
\v 6 A ale a izi neto itǝ apung a leere ne, leyendea yo za. Epaaka Ashili a gwaara tana oromo wa are ne.”
\v 7 Nane beka kai na, “Nyimia waaza, eyaaka Mosa wa ote na a nya e wela omaro o amare, akang pere ondaaye?”
\p 
\v 8 Na Yeso kabare naka bekaa nee na, “Azaa obena eye kaa anyong a katakau waya wa ote na Mosa kabare na e nya e wela opere amare, obora nyimia ta za ne.
\v 9 Eyang bele oying kangza, pate ondooka wa arnang ka ondaye wai, azaa leyau lee taza ne, awa kang ale kawa ana ondaye yende kawa ote odo, wa ya epa e madinǝ naname. Ondooka wa ote ondaye omea a pere wai ba odo, wa ya leyau.”
\p 
\v 10 Na atoma kai bekaa kai na, “Nyimia waaza a tera ondaleme kaa ondaye wai, odera o ana ondaye me wa kala.”
\v 11 Naka bekaa nee na, “Komana wa era wata kabare ka oroka me ne, soona andaaka Ashili a kangkama ne.
\v 12 Ana ondo ne zene ka a ngmeng ne agbele, ana ondo aromoa ne ote ne nane itǝ agbele. Ana ondo kangza ne tere o bena neto ana andaaye ne obena neya yeme togomo te zaa shili. Pate ondooka wayo ama o jeka orokaana, awa jeke.”
\s1 Yeso ka ayana a batebate
\r (Mar 10:13-16; Luk 18:15-17)
\p 
\v 13 A were name, na ca Yeso ayana aa batebate adorna ka eke ne o ara, a kakang beye angmǝ kaa Ashili aa za one, na atoma kai ne zurki ba andaaka ne deya ka ayana me.
\v 14 Na Yeso bekaa nee na, “Bayana ayana a batebate aa ne deya mi, tane nara nee ne, obena togomo te zaa shili te ebelo ene te.”
\v 15 Na ka eese taara to kare o leba ba za one, aaka ale teweno te kai.
\s1 Ondaasau ooka waye ka ocǝ
\r (Mar 10:17-31; Luk 18:18-30)
\p 
\v 16 Aya zaa nyimi na ondo paka ting Yeso nawa bekaa na, “Ondo baala, obelo edang ka maa eze ang cǝ ebeene o dera o maro?”
\v 17 Na Yeso kabare wai naa, “Eyaaka oya pirǝ ong ba zaa epa edang? Ashili aya belle aye ka edang. Baaya yeme o cǝ ebeene odera o maro, o tare makili ma Ashili maana.”
\p 
\v 18 Nawa beka Yeso na, “Makili ma Ashili maa yeme?” Na Yeso bekaa na, “Tana o wong ondo ne, tana o eze leyau, tana o eze bekǝri ne, tana o beye majǝkǝri ne.
\v 19 Nya ate au ka iini o ogongha one. Kangza oo yeme ondooka wa cikǝ ating au, na ukpwei o.”
\p 
\v 20 Na Ondasau me bekaa kai na, “Ma eza nyimi ba pat, eya tata mi kangza?”
\p 
\v 21 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Ba ya yeme o cikǝ zora madinǝ, ale ka o lishi pate magogoro mau, o jeke emate me ka o nya ana o dera eyapa oyo itǝ ondo ocǝ aa zaa shili. O ama o de ka o tareng.”
\p 
\v 22 Nangka ondasau me wa kone nyimi, nawa sokoo ale ka o caro lenyong, obena waya ka ocǝ maleu.
\p 
\v 23 Na Yeso bekaa atoma kai na, “Eyang dongdong bele oying, wayo poba kaa ondo ocǝ wa lyǝ ba nyimi togomo ta zaa shili.
\v 24 Eyang kang bele oying. Mara orongkoome wa lyǝ a le'o beberkena ka obena ondo ocǝ wa lyǝ ba nyimi togomo to Ashili.”
\p 
\v 25 Nangka atoma Yeso ne kone nyimi, na epame tera ne tukpwei maleo, nane bekaana, “Nyimia waaza, mana wa era wa cǝ o boza?
\p 
\v 26 Na Yeso laka ne aaka bekaa na, “Enna ara aromo e pobe oya, ara Ashili ekeeya e era eye.”
\p 
\v 27 Na Biturusu kabare nawa bekaana, “Ro naana, te arnang ka ekeeya azaa o tare o. Eya teyo cǝ?
\v 28 Na Yeso bekaa nee na, “Eyang dongdong bele oying, a tomore to deya, awereaka Kena ka Oromo yo cikǝ aa ledǝndǝ lee gong le togomo to kai, ying ka e tareng, eyo cikǝ ara to cikǝ be tuuru ka leere, e core angmǝ ba zaa tokwilǝ be tuuru ka leere a maIsrela.
\v 29 Kangza pate ondooka wa baya tokwilǝ, kaa arone andaleme, na arone andaaye, kaa ate, kaa iini, na ayana, na turu, ba za leze leng, wayo cǝ o ripitini liwinu, a wa kang cǝ ebene odera omaro.
\v 30 Bangka nyimi, aromo a cak ana o bora neyo itǝ ana o maare, aa ana o maare neyo itǝ ana o bora.”
\c 20
\s1 Ana ogole ara o inabi
\p 
\v 1 “Togomo ta zaa shili a kedeya te kaa ateakwilǝ yende, omea wa suri ba leleere nawa jeke ana ogole ba nyimi ara a wai a mati ma inabi.
\v 2 Nangka wa beye ejamane kaa ne ba za o dinari yende konang owere, nawa turki ne ba nyimi ara me.
\v 3 Aa ya gera beru be torai be leleere nawa suri kangza, nawa laka ana ondo ba cikǝ zora epa o eza a bengmǝ ba ara ejamane.
\v 4 Nawa beka ne na, “Ying kangza ale na ba ara a mati ma inabi mang, eyang nya ying epaaka wa gwara a nya ying.” Nane ale.
\v 5 Nangka wa kang surǝ a ongme wa dukǝ tera, kangza kaa beru be o taaro ulyǝlu, nyimia nawa kang jeka ana ogole.
\v 6 Nangka beru be esu beye, nawa kang surǝ nawa laka ana ondo ba itǝ, nawa beka nee na, ‘Eyaka e were ba cikǝ zora epa o eza?’
\p 
\v 7 Nane kabare wai na, “Ondo taa wa nya ro ogole ne.” Nawa bekaa nee na,
\p “Ying kangza ale na ba ara a mati ma inabi mang.”
\p 
\v 8 Nangka ulyǝlu waye baa cuwu, na ondo ara o mati ma inabi wa bekaa ondo o kangkama o wai a soola ogole o me na, ‘Rare ana ogole me ka o arseze ne epa eka e itǝ e komana, o bore ba ana o maare ba ale ana o bora.’
\v 9 Nangka andaaka ne bore ogole ba ulyǝlu ba cuwu ne de, na komana one a nya wai be dinari be yende.
\v 10 Nangka andaaka a jeke ne ba obora ne de, nane eke lenyong oo bena neyo cǝ o kala o nyimi. Neema na komana one wa cǝ be dinari be yende.
\v 11 Nangka komana one wa cǝ epaaka a nya wai nane wore odera o kona oleba ba ateakwilǝ me,
\v 12 aane beye na, “Andaaka a jeke ne oo maare ogole o beru be yendea belle ne eze, na ba ara ro nangka ba ara ne, ro ka tee were ba aa gole aa nyimi ongme.”
\p 
\v 13 Nawa kabare ondo ba nyimi one na, “Oja, anta ma iru ne. Teta te beya na eyang nyau o dinari yende ne?
\v 14 Emba epaeka te beya kaa bo o ale. Mia maa zaka na ma nya ana o maare ba kap ka nangka ma nyau.
\v 15 Anta ka obare kang ye epaaka ang ama oya me ka epa eng sang? Aa bo ota ba kona oleba epaeka ma ya e rere naname ne na?”
\p 
\v 16 Baa zaa nyimi ana o maare neyo itǝ ana obora, aa ana obora neyo itǝ ana o maare.”
\s1 Yeso ka sukǝ o bekaa nangka kayo gbwǝ
\r (Mar 10:32-34; Luk 18:31-34)
\p 
\v 17 Awereaka Yeso kaa atoma kai neya zala ba Urushalima, na Yeso itǝ kaa ne be daki orona aka beka nee na,
\v 18 “Teya ale ba Urushalima. Aya nya kena ka oromo ba taara ta andaamoole ama magame ma Ashili, kaa ana o baala angmǝ aka Ashili a nya Mosa, neyo core angmǝ ba zaa kai ka a wong kai.
\v 19 Neyo niyi kai ba taara ta maYahuda kane zeele kai, aane ole kai, aane kang gendare kai ba zaa uti. A lengme lo taaro kangza ayo ara kai.”
\s1 Lebose le iini Yakubu kaa Yohana
\r (Mar 10:13-45)
\p 
\v 20 Na iini ayana Zabadi paka ba ting Yeso kaa ayana kai, naka girwǝ ba begeshe be kai, aa ka bose eyapa ba kai.
\p 
\v 21 Na Yeso beka kai na, “Eya oya yeme me?”
\p Naka beka kai na, “Ote ayana ang a leere aana ka ne cikǝ, ka yende o ara ore o, aa ka yende o ara o guri o, a nyimi togomo teo.”
\p 
\v 22 Na Yeso kabare naka beka ba ayana me na, “Eta rosa epaeka eya bosaza me ne, eyo ama o sa o gǝǝzǝ omea eyang sa na?”
\p Nane bekaa kai na, “Teyo ama.”
\p 
\v 23 Naka bekaa ne na, “Eyo dongdong sa a ka poto kang, a obena e cikǝ ba o ara o re na o guri, mia taza ka o bare nya me ne. Ate ang o zaa shili wa babara araname azaa andaaka aa zaka.”
\p 
\v 24 Nangka o dangare atoma kai be tuuru ne kone nyimi, na ne mungi ka ayana leere name.
\v 25 Na Yeso rare ne na ka bekaana, “Erose obena agomo a worme ne wore ne legoone, aa na o kangkama agomo me kangza ne wore ne obare.
\v 26 Wato itǝ nyimi ba nyimi oying ne. Ba zaa nyimi pate ondooka waya yeme o itǝ ondo gong ba nyimi oying, seeka wa itǝ ozara oying.
\v 27 Kangza ondooka waya yeme a wa itǝ ondo tare ka ying, seeka wa itǝ ozara oying.
\v 28 Nyimia kangza Kena ka Oromo kata ka deya ka aromo eze kai lezara ne, ka deye adorana kai ka itǝ ozara, na ka nya ebene kai adorana ka boze aromo ba cak.”
\s1 Arǝ leere ne cǝ o gonta
\r (Mar 10:46-52; Luk 18:35-43)
\p 
\v 29 Nangka Yeso kaa atoma kai neya baya a nyimia Yariko na aromo ba cak ne tare kai.
\v 30 Arǝ a leere neya cikǝ a be dǝki be orona. Nangka ne kone na Yeso yaa kala, nane ara lengmelo nane bekaana, “Ateokora, kona egonegone oro, Kena ka Daoda!”
\p 
\v 31 Na aromo ne zurki baa ne kane kome. Kangza nane wale ara lengmelo ne maleo, aane beya na, “Ateokora, kona egonegone oro, Kena ka Daoda!”
\p 
\v 32 Na Yeso itǝ aa ka bekaa nee na, “Eya eya yeme ang ye ying?”
\p 
\v 33 Nane beka kai na, “Ateokora, teya yeme a te cǝ o gonta!”
\p 
\v 34 Ba nyimi okona egonegone one, na Yeso ka moke ayizi ane, na ongmere liizi nane cǝ o gonta, aane tare kai.
\c 21
\s1 Yeso ka lyǝ aa Urushalima
\r (Mar 12:1-11; Luk 19:28-40; Yoh 12:12-19)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso kaa atoma kai ne dukǝ kapeng ka Betapaji kamea ka amara ka Urushalima, ba kulǝ oyara o mati ma Zaitun, na Yeso ka tong atoma kai a leere,
\v 2 naka beka nee na, “Lyǝ na ba kapeng kaa niini ba izi oying. Ee lyǝ eyo laka kurungzǝ baa tera, ka kabana kame. Dinggǝ na e ka ecang.
\v 3 Ondo wa pirkǝ, ying e beka wai na, Ateokora ya yeme one. Wayo kuriyǝ ee aa rabokoro.”
\p 
\v 4 A ye nyimia adorana a panza epa eeka ondo beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Zakariya beke obena,
\q1 
\v 5 “Ee bekaa kagala ka Sihiyona na,
\q2 laka, Ogomo oying waya zo deya ba ying!
\q1 Ondo o nata ukpwei wai,
\q2 Waya zaa kabana kurungzǝ.”\x - \xo 21:5 \xt Zak 9:9.\x*
\p 
\v 6 Na atoma Yeso ne ale, nane ye epaaka Yeso ka bekaa ne.
\v 7 Nane de kaa kurungzǝ ka kabana kame, nane nata ne madibi aa zaa one, a ka zale.
\v 8 Na aromo ba cak ne nata madibi mane ba zaa orona, aana ondo gera marane ma mati nane eese ba zaa orona.
\v 9 A okurkǝnǝng aromo ka neya teweno ba izi ka kai kaa andaaka neya dimǝ kai, nane ara angmelo aane beya na,
\q1 “Hosana Kena ka Daoda!
\q2 Okona oleba wa itǝ
\q1 o kando ko deya ba nyimi leze le Ateokora!
\q2 Hosana o Ashili!”\x - \xo 21:9 \xt Sel 118:25-26.\x*
\p 
\v 10 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ baa nyimi Urushalima na pate apeng me a bitǝkǝrnu, aane beya naa, “Mana waana?”
\p 
\v 11 Na aromo aaka neya tare o Yeso bekaana, “Kanna kando ka o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Yeso kamea ka surǝa Nazarat o makeke ma Galili.”
\s1 Yeso ka tarangga ana ejamane aa akwilǝ Ashili
\r (Mar 11:15-19; Luk 19:45-48; Yoh 2:13-22)
\p 
\v 12 Na Yeso ka lyǝ akwilǝ Ashili naka tarangga ana o lisǝzǝ kaa ana o eesa magogoro baa nyimi me, naka bitǝkǝri pate matara mana o saara emate me, kaa matara ma o lisǝsǝ egoma e akwilǝ.
\v 13 Naka bekaa nee na, “A wele obena,
\q1 ‘Ayo rara akwilǝ ang aro beya angmǝ kaa Ashili,
\q2 na ying e kuriyǝ ai aro baasaza ana o tǝǝru aromo.’ ”\x - \xo 21:13 \xt Irim 7:11.\x*
\p 
\v 14 Na arǝ kaa agǝdǝ ne deya baa kai a nyimi akwilǝ Ashili naka womza ne.
\v 15 Nangka andaamoole magame ma Ashili, kaa ana o baala angmǝ aka Ashili a nya Mosa ne laka epa o tera ukpwei eeka ka eza, aa ayana yaa saba Ashili ba nyimi akwilǝ Ashili a ne beya na, “Hosana Kena ka Daoda!” Na ne kone oburǝ maleo.
\v 16 Nane bekaa kai na, “Oya konaza epaeka andaana ya beya me sang?
\p Na Yeso beka ne naa, “Ma kona, azaa nyimi eta rosa obena a wele na,
\q1 “Ba nyimi ongmǝ a abana ayana kaa akaa tata a asa,
\q2 boa baa ote ka ne saboo sang?\x - \xo 21:16 \xt Sel 8:2.\x*”
\p 
\v 17 Naka arnang kaa ne, aaka suri ba nyimi apeng me, naka ale ba Betanya, aaka more saname.
\s1 Yeso ka ye uti o ulǝ angmǝ
\r (Mar 11:12-14,20-24)
\p 
\v 18 Nangka ara a sane a kaya kurǝ ba nyimia apeng, na ekomo moke kai.
\v 19 Nangka ka laka uti o uli ba ting orona, naka ale ba uti me naka ta cǝ eyapa o uti me ne soona marane belle. Naka beka uti me na, “Otoo ya ayana kangza ne!” Na ongmere liizi na uti me wa waka.
\p 
\v 20 Nangka atoma kai ne laka nyimi, na epame e tere ne ukpwei nane bore be pirǝ na, “Eyaka uti uli na wa waka ba saseya?”
\p 
\v 21 Na Yeso ka kabare naka beka ne naa, “Eyang dongdong bele oying maganggang maame, eeya ka o eke lenyong ba Ashili, zora madoola ma yende, epaaka e mana uti uli ona, eya eto eza belle ne, eyo ama o beka ba oyara ona, era, ka o taru ba nyimi opong ogong, a wayo itǝ nyimi.
\v 22 Eeya ka o eke lenyong ba Ashili, pate epaaka e bosa ba Ashili eyo cǝ e.”
\s1 Aya masanggo azaa o bare o Yeso
\r (Mar 11:27-33; Luk 20:1-8)
\p 
\v 23 Nangka Yeso ka lyǝ ba nyimi akwilǝ Ashili, kaya aza obaala naname, na andaamoole magame ma Ashili, ka magonggong ma aromo nane deya kai ka be pirǝ na, “Ka legoone le mana oya eza magogoro maana? Kangza mana wa nyau legoone le me?”
\p 
\v 24 Na Yeso ka kabare naka bekaa na, “Mima eyang eza o ying be pirǝ. E kabareng, mima eyang bele oying ka legoone le mana ang eze magogoro maana.
\v 25 O batisma o Yohana, wa surǝ babaa? Ba zaa shili naa, ba aromoi?”
\p Nane dambaraza a tukpwei tone obena, “Te bekaana, wa surǝ shili, kayo bekaa aro na, na eyaka eta e kabare kaa kai ne?”
\v 26 Kangza te bekaana, “Wa surǝ ba aromo, teya kona boome be aromo, obena komana wa rose obena Yohana ondo beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili wai.”
\p 
\v 27 Nane kabare Yeso na, “Teta rosa ne.”
\p Na Yeso beka ne naa, “Nyimia mima anta a bele oying ka legoone le mana ang ezeze magogoro maana ne.”
\s1 Angmǝ a gerpo azaa ayana leere
\p 
\v 28 “E laka nannia? Oromo yende wa zene kaa ayana leere andaleme. Nawa ale baa ka o bora, nawa beka kai na, “Kena kang ale ka o eza ogole ba ara o inabi.
\v 29 Na kena kame beka na, “Anta ale ne.” Nangka a rabokoro naka sara madoola, aaka ale.
\v 30 Na ate ame wa ale baa ka o leere kame, nawa beka kai epaaka wa beka a ka o bora. Na ka o leere bekaana, “Ma kona ate, eyang ale,” na kata ale ne.
\p 
\v 31 Ba nyimi ayana leere me mana wa ye epaeka ate me wa yeme?
\p Nane bekaana, “Ka o bora.”
\p Na Yeso bekaa nee na, “Eyang bele o ying epeng eme, ana o eesa emate e makeke kaa andaaye o lisǝzǝ apung ane neya kaana oying o lyǝ ba togomo ta Ashili.
\v 32 Obena Yohana o batisma wa de nawa wore ying orona o rere, neeta kabare ka wai ne. Ba zaa nyimi na ana o eesa emate makeke kaa andaaye o lisǝzǝ apung ane ne kabare ka wai, aa ying pate ka o laka enna, malo nyimi na eta kabare a pisǝ madinǝ maying ne.”
\s1 Angmǝ aa gerpo azaa ana ogole // ara ka neye kaa araa buru
\r (Mar 12:1-12; Luk 20:9-19)
\p 
\v 33 “Angmǝ aa gerpo yendea aana kangza. Oromo yende wa zene ka waye kaa ara o inabi, nawa ringǝri ara me ka odarne, nawa kau le'o le noke ayana inabi a ara me, a kangza wa so odankee ona soola ara me. Malo nyimi nawa nya ana ogole yende lebose le ara me, a wa ale begere.
\v 34 Nangka awere o sende e inabi me wa ye, nawa tong azara wai baa ana ogole me kane embe epaaka e itǝ e wai baa ne.
\p 
\v 35 Na andaaka a bose ne ara me, ne meke azara me, nane ole o yende, aa ne wong o yende, aa ne teeze o taaro me.
\v 36 Nawa kang tongha azara yende, amea ne kala obora, na andaaka a bose ne ara me, nane ye ne epaeka ne ye ana obora name.
\v 37 Malo nyimi nawa tong kena ka wai baa ne, a wa eke obena, ‘Neyo laka o gongha kena kang.’
\p 
\v 38 Nangka andaaka a bose ne ara ame ne laka kena ka oromo me, nane bekaa tukpwei tone na, “Aha, kando kaana ekeeya ara me aya itǝ a kai. A te wongha kai adorana ara me itǝ a aro.”
\v 39 Na ne moke kai, aane tare kai ba malo o darne, nane wongha kai.
\p 
\v 40 O ara aana wa deya, eya wayo ya kaa andaaka a bose ne ara ogole me?”
\p 
\v 41 Nane beka kai na, “Wayo wongza ana anyong a buru me, awa bose ana ondo a ara me, andaaka neyo nyaza wai epaaka e itǝ e wai aa nyimi epa eeka ne cǝ.”
\p 
\v 42 Na Yeso beka ne naa, “Eta tukǝ kona epaaka a wele ba nyimi angmǝ Ashili sang? O bena,
\q1 “Lecale leeka ondo sowa wa nyana,
\q2 leya lee itǝ le o kala ee dang o sowa odo.
\q1 Onna o eza Ashilia wai,
\q2 Epa o tera ukpwei aa yizi aro.”\x - \xo 21:42 \xt Sel 118:22-23.\x*
\p 
\v 43 “Ba zaa nyimi eyang bele oying, ayo emba togomo ta Ashili ba ying, ka nya a aromo makeke ma yende amea neyo wore o cikǝ o rere.
\v 44 Ondooka wa rizi aza le cale leena, wayo poso. Aa ondooka le cale leme le taru ba zaa wai leyo nyanta wai naa ma'ena.”
\p 
\v 45 Nangka ana magame ma moole kaa maParisa ne kone angmǝ me, nane rose obena, kaya beya baa za onea.
\v 46 Na ne gere o moke okai, na boome ba aromo nara ne, obena pate aromo ne jeka kai ondo beya angmǝ kama mawo ma Ashili kai.
\c 22
\s1 Angmǝ a gerpo azaa ozǝnggǝ o amare
\r (Luk 14:15-24)
\p 
\v 1 Na Yeso kang beka ne angmǝ a gerpo na,
\v 2 “A era kedeya togomo ta shili kaa ogomo yende ooka wa eze kena ka wai ozǝnggǝ amare.
\v 3 Na wa tong azara wai kane rare aromo aaka a baale ne o ozǝnggǝ me, na aromo amea a baale ne neta deya ne.
\p 
\v 4 Na wa kang tongha azara wai yende nawa beka ne na, “Alena ka e bekaa andaaka a baale ne o ozǝnggǝ na, maa goro na ma core bena be lome be mate eena, epaolya ee yengha, amara ekeeya ane de.”
\p 
\v 5 “Na andaaka a belene o amare me ta bala nee ne, na komana ale o ale awai, ondo wa ale ara awai, aa ondo ale ba ara ejamane awai.
\v 6 O dangare one moke azara ame nane ole ne, a ne wong ne.
\v 7 Ogomo me wa munggi aa cak, na wa tong ana otesa ageza aa moole awai, na ne wong aromo me, aane ese apeng ame ka ola aa pat.
\p 
\v 8 Na wa bekaa azara awai na, ‘Amara ekeeya o amare me, aa andaaka a bele ne ta gwara ne de ne.
\v 9 Tareze na marona, apate ondooka e laka ee bekaa wai na wa de ara o zǝnggǝ o amare me.’
\v 10 Na azara me ale na ne rare apate andaaka nee laka, ana edang kaa ana odera edang, nyimia na apanza ogiishi me ka ageng.
\p 
\v 11 “Aa nangka ogomo me wa lyǝ kawa laka ageng me, na wa laka ondo zora madibi ma ozǝnggǝ.
\v 12 Na wa pirkǝ wai na, ‘Oja, aa wiinia na ba lyǝ arakaana zora o amba madibi ma ozǝnggǝ ne?’ Na oromo me ta ama obeka eyapa ne.
\p 
\v 13 “Na ogomo me bekaa azara awai na, ‘Tera na taara ka tobona te wai, e tare wai a nyimi maring maa bo, ara aka ayo ruuzi ka ononza tuuni.’
\p 
\v 14 “O bena aromo acakea aa rare, aa aromo a baate aa zaka.’ ”
\s1 Be pirǝ azaa o arsaza emate makeke aa Kaisar
\r (Mar 12:13-17; Luk 20:20-26)
\p 
\v 15 Na maParisa gere orona ooka neyo moke kai aa nyimi angmǝ a kai.
\v 16 Na ne tong ana otare one ka aromo a Hiridus yende, na ne beka ana, “Ondo baala, te rose beka ana bo ondo baala epengngha, o kang baala komaname orona Ashili, ota zaka ondo ne, ba jeka komaname oyende a bo.
\v 17 Na beka aa ro epa eka ba laka, wa gwara te nya Kaisar emate makeke naa, na tana te nya nea?”
\p 
\v 18 Yeso ka rose ara aburu aaka aya anyong ane, naka bekaana, “Ying ana anyong aburu! Eya ka eya kedeya ong?
\v 19 “Worenna bemate beeka a arseze oma makeke mane.” Nane ca kai be dinari be me.
\v 20 Na Yeso pirkǝ nee na ‘Mainu ka leze le mana ba azaa benna?’
\p 
\v 21 Nane kabare kai na, “Ma Kaisar.”
\p Na Yeso bekaa nee na, “Na nya na Kaisar epa eka e Kaisar e, ee nya Ashili epa eka a Ashili e.”
\v 22 Nangka ne kona nyimi, na epa eme tere ne ukpwei, aane ale o ale one.
\s1 Be pirǝ azaa o era malo ogwǝ
\r (Mar 12:18-27; Luk 20:27-40)
\p 
\v 23 A lengme leme, na maSadukiya ka ne beyaana ata eere malo ogwǝ ne, na ne pirkǝ kai,
\v 24 nane bekana, ‘Mosa wa bekaa na oromo wa gbwǝ zora ayana, orone o wai cikǝ kaa kandaye kame ka ka ngmengze wai ayana.’\x - \xo 22:24 \xt Otik 25:5.\x*
\v 25 Arone sondaare zene aa nyimi oro. Obora wa ana ondaaye, nawa gbwi zora kena, na ondaadimǝ wai cikǝ kaa ondaaye me.
\v 26 Nyimia ondaadimǝ wai o leere, kaa o taaro, nyimia epame e ale a dukǝ pate one aa sondaare.
\v 27 O maare apat, na ondaye me ma wa gbwi.
\v 28 Na nannameena, aa lengme le o era malo ogbwǝ, wayo itǝ ondaaye mana a nyimi one, ka pate one nee cikǝ kaa wai?
\p 
\v 29 Na Yeso bekaa nee na, madoola maying ta orona ne, ka eta rose angmǝ Ashili ka awela ne, kangza eta rose legoone le Ashili ne.
\v 30 Lengme le o era malo ogbwǝ, o anza ondaye ta rene ne, aa onya ondaye kaa o oteze one a todo to rene ne, aza obena neyo kurǝ na atoma Ashili odera lepung aaza shili.
\v 31 Azaa o era malo o gbwǝ, eta ee tukǝ o soola epaeka Ashili a beke aying ne na? A bekaana,
\v 32 ‘Mia Ashili a Ibraheng, Ashili a Ishaku, kaa Ashili a Yakubu.’\x - \xo 22:32 \xt Osur 3:6.\x* Ashilia a pate andaaka neya ka ebeene, ana o gbwizǝ tazane.”
\p 
\v 33 Nangka aromome ne kona nyimi, na epa eme tere ne ukpwei.
\s1 Makili ma okala dengdeng
\r (Mar 12:28-32; Luk 10:25-28)
\p 
\v 34 Nangka maParisa ne kone ana Yeso ka toza maSadukiya, nane gwaara tukpwei,
\v 35 ondo o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa aa nyimi one, wa eze Yeso be pirǝ adorana wa cǝ kawa meke kai.
\v 36 Nawa bena, “Ondo o baala, oyeme kala ogongha a nyimi makili ma Mosa?”
\p 
\v 37 Na Yeso kabare wai na, “Yeme Ateokora Ashili au kaa pate lenyong leo, kaa pate ebeene o, ka opate madoola mau.”\x - \xo 22:37 \xt Otik 6:5.\x*
\v 38 Onna obora kawa kala aa gongha apate.
\v 39 Makili o leere ome kang ya na obora, ‘Yeme ondooka waya ating o na ukpwei o.’
\v 40 Pate o baala o Mosa ka ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili, ma ya azaa makili ma leere maana.”
\s1 Be pirǝ azaa Almasipu
\r (Mar 12:35-37; Luk 20:41-44)
\p 
\v 41 Nangka maParisa ma yende ne kurkǝnǝng ara yende, na Yeso ka pirkǝ ne na,
\v 42 “Eya madoola maying aza Almasipu? Kai kena ka manaa?”
\p Nane kabare kai na, ‘Kena ka Daoda kai.’
\p 
\v 43 Na Yeso bekaane na, “Na a wiinia na Daoda beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Obere o Sangsang, na wa rare kai na ‘Ateokora’? Aa wa bekana,
\q1 
\v 44 ‘Ateokora wa beka aa Ateokora ong na,
\q2 “Cikǝ o ara o re ong,
\q1 seeka ma eke ana o nyana o,
\q2 aa tetau te tobona teo.” ’
\p 
\v 45 Na Daoda wa rara Almasipu na ‘Ateokora’, aa wiinia aaka itǝ kena ka wai?
\v 46 Ondo ta wa ama kabare a Yeso ne. O era a lengme leme, ondo ta wa kang ama o pirkǝ okai ne.
\c 23
\s1 Yeso ka banggali o ela o andaano
\r (Mar 12:38-39; Luk 11:43-46; 20:45-47)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka aromo ne kurkǝnǝng ba cake kaa atoma kai, na Yeso bekaane na,
\v 2 “Ana obaala makili ma Mosa ka maParisa neya a nya ne uwǝri baala makili ma Mosa.
\v 3 Azaa nyimi, tare na, eza pate epa eka ne beka ying, se na tane ezeze epa eka ne eze ne, ka ne baala aa neta ezeze epa eka ne baala ne.
\v 4 Ne tesa aromo magogoro ma dendeng ka ma poba ana ba o malo, zora bekaana ne kankama ne ko ka lebo.
\p 
\v 5 “Ekeeya ene ne ezaa ka aromo laka. Ne ezaza a gwada a molemole ka angmǝ a Ashili aaka a wele kane tese a madong mane ka taara tone, ne dozeze se jǝng se eewo ka ma dukǝ tulung te ne, ba taara te madibi mane.
\v 6 Ne kala ara o eme ne cikǝ ara cisǝ anda mole ara o zǝnggǝ, a ne kang cikǝ ba izi aa nyimi o dandaro Ashili.
\v 7 Aa ne kang yeme a beeze ne okoo ba ara ejamane, aa kang rara ne na, ‘Ana obaala’.
\p 
\v 8 A ying, tana a rara ying ana ‘Ana obaala’ ne, ka ondo obaala o ying o yendea wai, aa pate oying arone ai.
\v 9 Tana e rare ondo orambo na ana ‘Ate’ ne. Eya ka Ate a yendea ka aya zaa shili.
\v 10 A tana rara ying ‘Andaano’ ne, obena eya ka ondoono o yendea belle, kaya Almasipu.
\v 11 Wai ka wa kala ogongha ba nyimi oying wayo itǝ ozara oying.
\v 12 Pate ondo oka wa ara ukpwei, ayo jǝpǝrǝ wai. Aa pate ondo oka wa jǝpǝrǝ ukpwei, ayo ara wai.
\p 
\v 13 Eyo zitǝ, ying ana o baala makili ma Mosa ka maParisa, kaa ana rendaza! E pate aromo abuudu o lyǝ aa togomo te zaa shili, yingha tukpwei teying eta lyǝ ne, aa kang nara ana o eme ne lyǝ.
\p 
\v 14 Eyo zitǝ, ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa ka maParisa, ana o rendaza! E lyeeze magogoro ma andaye aka andaleme ane a gbwizǝ, e beya angmǝ ka Ashili o eo adorana aa laka ying. Azaa nyimi, o zitǝ oying wayo kala o komana.
\p 
\v 15 Eyo zitǝ, ana obaala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa ka maParisa, kaa ana o rendaza! E taare manyi ma gong, e aleze a makeke macangcang ba ogera ondo o kurǝ Ashili oyende. Aa e cǝ wai, e kang ote wa kala ying o wilǝ.
\p 
\v 16 Eyo zitǝ, ying arǝ aaka ne windǝ aromo. E beeze na, ‘Ondo wa tono ka akwilǝ Ashili, eyapa taza ne, aa wa tono ka ozinari o akwilǝ Ashili, otono me yo lya wai.’
\v 17 Ying arǝ, a rara! Oyeng ome kala ogongha, ozinari na, akwilǝ Ashili oka wa kwizǝzǝ ozinari e?
\v 18 E beeze na, ‘Ondooka wa tono kaa ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mo waze, eyapa taa ne, aa pate ondooka wa tono ka epa eka a nata azame, le tono leyo moke wai.’
\v 19 Ying arǝ! O yemea kala ogongha, epa eka aa nya Ashilia na, na a ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mo waze oka wa kwizǝzǝ epa eka a nya mea?
\v 20 Azaa nyimi, oromo wa tono ka ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mo waze, wa tono ka ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mo waze aa pate epa eka a nata azame.
\v 21 Aa Pate ondooka wa tono ka akwilǝ Ashili, wa tono ka wai ka Ashili ka aya nyimi ai.
\v 22 Pate ondooka wa tono ka zaa shili kanza, wa tono kale dǝndǝ le Ashili ka ondo oka waya cikǝ aaza me.\x - \xo 23:22 \xt Ish 66:1; Mat 5:34.\x*
\p 
\v 23 Eyo zitǝ, ying ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa ka maParisa, ying ana o rendaza! E nyaza Ashili le yende a nyimi betuuru epa e ecete ka ma nanggo, aa e pere epa eka ekala edang e makili ma Mosa, na obeya epeng, egonegone, ka o eza epa ee kap. Epa eka wa gwara e eza naname zora o baya ma dangare mame.\x - \xo 23:23 \xt Mag 27:30.\x*
\v 24 Ying arǝ aka ne windǝ aromo, e lobeze ecǝngci, aa e dongze orankome!
\p 
\v 25 Eyo zitǝ, ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa ka maParisa, ying ana o rendaza! E kwizǝzǝ malo topoto ka teso toying, a nyimi a pena le iri, ka o yeme ukpwei.
\v 26 Bo, urǝ oParisa! Bora kwizǝ a nyimi oso ka opoto, adora a malo me ya a sangsang.
\p 
\v 27 Eyo zitǝ, ana obaala makili ma Mosa ka maParisa, ying ana o rendaza! Eye na macao maaka a leleme ka egengge epeng. Ma rere olaka oo yanga, aa nyimi a pena kaa cako andaaka ne gbwizǝ kaa kombela madinǝ.\x - \xo 23:27 \xt Ogat 23:3.\x*
\v 28 Nyimia ba ayizi aromo ying ana okona boome be Ashilia, aa nyimi anyong aying ana o rendaza, kaa ana ara aburu.
\p 
\v 29 Eyo zitǝ, ana obaala makili ma Mosa ka maParisa, ying ana o rendaza! E sooze ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili macao, kangza ezeze ejaaga a macau ma ana o kona boome be Ashili.
\v 30 E beeze na, ‘Eya te rene a were a samba, te ta teyo gwara taara kane ba o wonghza ana obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili mame ne.’
\v 31 Nyimia e wore bena ying ayana andaaka ne wonghza ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili.
\v 32 Lya na izi, maare na epa eka ma gonggong maying ma bore!
\p 
\v 33 Ying ewa, kaa o kurkǝnǝng ewa e buru! Aa wiinia e bisi o gǝǝzǝ Ashili akwilǝ ola?
\v 34 Azaa nyimi ma tongha ying ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili, kaa ana orosa, kaa ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa. E yo wongha ana ondo one, ee gendare ana ondo o uti, aa na ondo eyo ola ne aa nyimi ma dandaro maying, ee tarze ne aa topepeng ee gǝǝzǝ ne.
\v 35 Nyimia aaza oying ayo gera manyau mana o dera madinǝ maaka a oke a lerambo, aa era a manyau ma ondo o sangsang Habila aa ale a Zakariya kena ka Berekiya, kamea e wongha aa tera akwilǝ Ashili ka ara o esaza Ashili mapapa mayo kurǝ aaza oying.
\v 36 Na eyang baala oying, pate manna ma yo mana ayana nanname.
\s1 Yeso ka kone egonegone e Urushalima
\r (Luk 13:34-35)
\p 
\v 37 Urushalima! Urushalima! Bo ka ba wongze ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili, aa o kang teeze andaaka aa tongha ba bo ka cale! Ka wondaa ma yeme o kurǝ oying nangka katokoro kuruzi ayana kai aa ma beko ma kai, na ee nyana.
\v 38 Na awa nanname aa ba ying akwilǝ me na a itǝ makansǝng!
\v 39 Mi sang eyang baala oying, eto kang lakang ne, se lengme leeka e bekaana ‘Ondo o kona leba ondooka waya deya ka leze le Ateokora.’
\c 24
\s1 O oko Akwilǝ Ashili
\r (Mar 13:1-2; Luk 21:5-6)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka suri Akwilǝ Ashili me, kaya nyimi teyeno, na atoma akai de nane wore kai masosowa ma Akwilǝ Ashili me.
\v 2 Na ka bekaa nee na, ‘Eya gonta pate masosowa maana? Eyang dongdong obele ying, ata baya le cale leyende kaa ayo baya aza leyende ne. Ayo bacakare ai aa pat.’
\s1 Obora ozitǝ
\r (Mar 13:3-13; Luk 21:7-19)
\p 
\v 3 Yeso ka ya cikǝ oyara o Zaitun, na atoma akai ne deya kai aa suk, nane beka kai na, ‘‘Bele ro, ngmǝyamea aya eza mapa maana? Eya kangza eyo wore ro odeya o, ka omare lerambo?”
\p 
\v 4 Na Yeso kabare nee, naka bekaana, “Eza na a sauwo, tana ondo rende ying ne.
\v 5 Obena aromo a cake neyo deya aa nyimi leze leng, aane beyaa na, ‘Mia Almasipu’, ka ne rendeze aromo aa cak.
\v 6 Eyo kang konaza marooka ma okara kaa ngmǝ acak azaa makara. Tana ekone boome ne, azaa obena dongdong nyimi yo ya, aa omaare tata suri.
\v 7 Aromo apeng neyo gera aromo apeng yende bete, togomo teyo gera togomo te yende bete. Ayo eza ekomo kangza, kaa o zukǝrzu adeze, a kuruwǝ.
\v 8 Aa pate ka nyimi, onna obora o zitǝa belle.
\p 
\v 9 “Malo nyimi neyo niyi ying ka gǝǝzǝ ying, aa kang wongha ying. Pate aromo yo nyana ying aza leze leng.
\v 10 A were na mea aromo acake yo rizi, neyo iri tukpwei, aa ne nyana tukpwei.
\v 11 Atoma o rendaza a cake yo susǝ, aa ne rendeze aromo a cak.
\v 12 Azaa waale ogongha araaburu, o yeme aromo acake yo kasarno.
\v 13 Aa pate ondooka wa motana aa ale omaare wayo bisǝ.
\v 14 Ayo kang baala orooka o leba o togomo te Ashili teena a pate kuruwǝ a nyimi lerambo leena. Malo o nyimi o maare de.”
\s1 Ozitǝ oo jǝng
\r (Mar 13:14-23; Luk 21:20-24)
\p 
\v 15 “Azaa nyimi, pate awere aaka e laka epa e berebere, o deesa ka ocara, oo ka ondo obeya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Daniyel wa beye angmǝ azaa me, aa waya itǝ ara aa sangsang. Ondo o soola awa rose.\x - \xo 24:15 \xt Dan 9:27; 11:31; 12:11.\x*
\v 16 Aa andaaka neya makeke ma Yahudiya songha ne lyǝ aa mayara.
\v 17 Tana ondooka wa ya azaa akwilǝ jipi a jeka eyapa a nyimi akwilǝ me ne.
\v 18 Ondooka waya ara kangza, tana wa kuri aa jeka odibi owai ne.\x - \xo 24:18 \xt Luk 17:31.\x*
\v 19 Andaye aaka neya ka etumǝ ka ana lewanyo, neyo zitǝ.
\v 20 Bosa na Ashili tana tesong teying de aa lekoze na lengme le o teseke ne.
\v 21 Aa werename ayo kala o ara ozitǝ, ombela ooka ata aa tukǝ ezame o era obora lerambo aa deya awereena ne. Ato kang sukǝ nyimi ne dakemeeme.\x - \xo 24:21 \xt Dan 12:1; T.Yoh 7:14.\x*
\p 
\v 22 Bangka a kashe shengme sheme ne, ondo ta zene ka waa yoo bisǝ ne, obena andaaka Ashili a zaka ne rene, ayo kashe shengme sheme.
\v 23 Awere name pate ondooka wa beka aying na ‘Almasipu waana!’ Koona, ‘Awa niini!’ Tana e kabare ne.
\v 24 Ma Almasipu kaa ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili ma orenda kaa neyo deesa, kane ezeze mapapa ma o tesa ukpwei, adorana ne wilǝrǝ pate ka andaaka Ashili a zake, nyimi waayo ya.
\v 25 Konanna! Ma bekaa ying ka orabo.
\p 
\v 26 “Nee bekaa ying na ‘Lakana, awa niini a owake, tana e ale ne.’ Nee kang bekaa ying na, ‘Awaana ara o baasa,’ tana e kabare ne.
\v 27 Nangka malmi eze masanto aa surǝ aa dizi aa alea aza, nyimi o kurǝ o Kena ka Oromo yo itǝ.
\p 
\v 28 Pate ara aaka ekeze rene, aya ejogaale kurkǝnǝzǝng ne.
\s1 O kurǝ Kena ka Oromo
\r (Mar 13:24-27; Luk 21:25-28)
\p 
\v 29 “A saseya malo tomore te ozitǝ oo jǝng me,
\q1 ‘ongme to kang ya masanto ne,
\q2 oreka kangza wato nya masanto ne.
\q1 Aa ewerewere yo tǝǝrǝ aa surǝ azaa shili,
\q2 ayo zukǝ pate obare ooka waya azaa shili.’\x - \xo 24:29 \xt Ish 13:10; 34:4; Ezek 32:7; Joy 2:10; 3:4; 3:15; T.Yoh 3:12-13.\x*
\p 
\v 30 Awere namea ayo laka o surǝ o Kena ka Oromo aaka surǝ aza shili, pate aleng aa lerambo leena neyo ruuzi, neyo laka Kena ka Oromo aa kaya deya aza mawere, ka obare kaa togomo tee gong.\x - \xo 24:30 \xt Dan 7:13; Zak 12:10-14; T.Yoh 1:7.\x*
\v 31 Wayo tongha atoma kai o dera lepung kane ulbi tojebe ajǝng, aa ne kurki andaaka aa zaka o era aa ara o susǝ ongme, kaa ara o tǝǝru ongme, aa kulu arungji kaa kulu ayarbawa o lerambo leena.
\s1 Epa eeka o eka oo baala azaa uti uli
\r (Mar 13:28-31; Luk 21:29-33)
\p 
\v 32 Jeka na eyapa a uti uli. Aa e bana ee obara o sara, kane sǝǝrǝ marane maa sau, ee rosa obena lekoze le amara naname.
\v 33 Nyimia awereaka ee laka pate epanana, eyo rosa obena awere a amara, aa bengmǝ be abuudu.
\v 34 Ang dongdong ya baala oying, awereena ta kala ne seeka epanana apate eye.
\v 35 Shili kaa deze yo maro, aa angmǝ ang to tukǝ omaro ne dakemeeme.
\s1 Ondo ta rosa lengme na awere ne
\r (Mar 13:32-37; Luk 17:26-30,34-36)
\p 
\v 36 “Ondo ta rosa lengme leme na awereme ne, koona atoma odera lepung ka neya azaa shili, koona Kena kame, seena Ate me belle.
\v 37 Waye na nangka a eze awere a Nuhu, nyimia o kurǝ Kena ka Oromo yo za.
\v 38 Wa kang ya na tomore tennamea zongka manyi maa gong bore, aya lyelyeeza, aa sosoza, aya nyaza aa angza andaaye, aa dukǝ lengme leeka Nuhu wa lyǝ o onggo o taara manyi.
\v 39 Zongka ne rose epa eka eya ale ne, seena manyi maa gong mame lye ne apat. Nyimia o kurǝ o Kena ka Oromo yo za.
\v 40 Awerenamea, ayo mana aromo leere ara a ogole, ayo jeka oyende, aa baya oyende.
\v 41 Ayo laka andaaye leere aa neya nyanta o nyanto, ayo jeka oyende, aa baya oyende.
\p 
\v 42 Azaa nyimi, cikǝ na a le'enda, ka eta rosa lengme leeka Ateokora oying ya kurǝ ne.
\v 43 Rosana bena, eeya ateakwilǝ yo rosa awere aka okǝri ya deya akwilǝ wai aa lelyaare, waa yo mora aa le'enda tana a lyǝ akwilǝ awai ka eze bekǝri ne.
\v 44 Ying kangza cikǝ na ka ogoro, Kena ka Oromo ya deya awereaka ata madoola ma nyimi ne.
\s1 Ozara edang kaa o dera edang
\r (Luk 12:41-48)
\p 
\v 45 “Ozara o yemea o eza epa edang aa waye ka orosa, ka ateakwilǝ awai yo nya wai le onta le akwilǝ awai, ka wa nyaza odangare azara me epaolya a were aka wa gwara?”
\v 46 O kona oleba ya aza ozara oka ateakwilǝ awai yo kurǝ awa mana wai awa ya eza nyimi.
\v 47 Eyang dongdong baala oying, wa yo ote wai aza ekeeya e wai.
\v 48 Aa ozara name ondo araaburu wa za, wa yo bekaa ukpwei wai na, ‘Ateakwilǝ ta amara ka o deya ne.’
\v 49 Aa wa bore olaza odangare azara me, awa lye, awa soze kaa ana ososoza.
\v 50 Ateakwilǝ ozara me yo deya a lengme leeka ata madoola ma o deya wai ne, awere aka wata rosa ne.
\v 51 Ka wa daara wai lepung ka lesaro, aa wa nya wai epa eka e gwara ka ana araaburu. Aa arame ayo ruuzi ka o nongza tuuni.”
\c 25
\s1 A ngmǝ gerpo azaa agala betuuru
\p 
\v 1 Awere name ayo kedeya togomo te shili na agala be tuuru ka ne jeke eru masanto na ne ale a wobe ondaasau.
\v 2 Esu a nyimi one ya ka orosa, aa ondanggare esu ta neye ka wai ne.
\v 3 Ana o dera orosa ne jeke eru masanto mane, aa neta ne onte manau ne.
\v 4 Aa ana orosa kangza ne monte eru masanto mane kaa kagwi ka manau.
\v 5 Ondaasau me ta wa dusung deya ne, pate one na ne bora ungzǝ, na malau jeke ne.
\p 
\v 6 “Aa sanini tera le lyaare, na ne kona lengmelo aa rara na, ‘Ondaasau me a waana wa dukǝ! Surǝ na ka e wobe wai!’
\p 
\v 7 “Pate agala name na ne ere na ne diisi eru masanto mane.
\v 8 Na ana odera orosa name bekaa ana orosa na, ‘Nyapana ro a manau maaying aa baate, eru masanto maro ya limbuzu!’
\p 
\v 9 Na ana orosa bekaana, ‘Ba eza manau maro to bare ro kaa ying ne. Mara e ale ana lisǝzǝme ke embe.’
\p 
\v 10 “Aane tata ara o emba manau mame, na ondaasau me dukǝ. Na andaaka neye ka ogoro ne lyǝ ara o zǝnggǝ ka wai, aa kang pate abuudu me.
\p 
\v 11 “Malo nyimi na ondanggare agala name dukǝ, nane bekaana, ‘Ateokora, Ateokora, pǝri ro abuudu!’
\p 
\v 12 “Na wa kabare nee na, ‘Ang dongdong bele oying, mi anta rosa ying ne.’
\p 
\v 13 “Na Yeso maare ka o bekaana, ‘Azaa nyimi, cikǝ na ka ogoro ka eta rosa lengme na awereme ne.’ ”
\s1 A ngmǝ a gerpo azaa talenti
\r (Luk 19:11-27)
\p 
\v 14 “Togomo te Ashili teyo itǝ naa oromoa ka waya ya ale aa teweno, nawa rare azara wai aa wa eke pate epa eka waya ka e a taara te ne.
\v 15 Wa nya oyende ma talenti esu, oyende ma talenti ma leere, aa oyende o talenti oyende. Wa nya komaname nangka legoone lewai leze. Aa wa ale.
\v 16 Wai ondooka wa emba ma talenti esu mame wa era a saseya nawa ale nawa wanggare nawa cǝ esu aa zame.
\v 17 Nyimia ondooka wa emba ma talenti ma leere, wai kangza wa cǝ ma leere aa zame.
\v 18 Wai ka wa o talenti o yende, wa ale nawa kau le'o a deze na wa baasa o talenti a ateakwilǝ a wai.
\p 
\v 19 “Malo rabo, na ateakwilǝ me wa kuri kane bale epa eka nee cǝ.
\v 20 Na ondo name kawa emba ma talenti esu wa paka nawa de ka ma talenti ma yende esu, awa bekaana, ‘Ateakwilǝ, ba nyang ma talenti esu, mi naana ama cǝ esu yende kangza.’
\p 
\v 21 “Na ateakwilǝ beka wai ana, ‘Kondo ogole, ozara edang, o dera araaburu. Ba eza edang aza epa e baate, eyang ote o aza epa ecake. Deya ka o cikǝ o kone oleba kaa ateakwilǝ o.
\p 
\v 22 “Na ondooka wa embe ma talenti ma leere wa paka, na wa bekaana, ‘Ateakwilǝ, ba nyang ma talenti ma leere, a maana aa ma cǝ ma leere aa zame.’
\p 
\v 23 “Na ateakwilǝ bekaa wai na ‘Kondo ogole, ozara edang, odera araaburu. Ba ya edang aza epa a baate. Eyang ote aza epa cake. Deya ka o cikǝ o kone oleba kaa ateakwilǝ o.’
\p 
\v 24 “Wai kangza kawa emba o talenti o yende name, nawa paka, nawa bekaana, ‘Ateakwilǝ, ang rose obena bo oromo oka wata eza eceya ka aromo ne, o yeme o senda a ara aka boa ota ba kweene ne, bo ondo o yeme epa eka ota ba zitǝ a zamea ne.’
\v 25 Waya na ma kona boome, na ma ale nama kawa le'o a deze namaa baasa o talenti ooka ba nyang. Na opa owaa waana!’
\p 
\v 26 “Na ateakwilǝ kabare wai na, ‘Bo, ozara araaburu, ondo be nau! Orose bena ang shende ara aka mia ta ma kweene ne, aa mi ondo o yeme epa eka anta maa zitǝ azame ne na?’
\v 27 Wa gwara eeya ba eke o talenti ong ara le'eke ka ma deya ang emba opa ong ka eyapa aza me!
\p 
\v 28 “Azaa nyimi, emba na o talenti onname a tara te wai, ka e nya ondo betuuru onname.
\v 29 Pate ondooka waya ka epa, ayo wala wai, ka e wala gongha. Ondooka wata ka e ne kangza, kapa kaa baate kamea wa zene, ayo emba a wai.
\v 30 Tare na ozara odera edang oona a nyimi maring maa bitibiti. Arakanamea wayo ruuzi ka onongza tuuni.
\s1 O core angmǝ azaa aworme
\p 
\v 31 “Awereaka Kena ko Oromo ya deya nyimi togomo te kai ka pate atoma o dera lepung, awere namea kayo cikǝ a ledǝndǝ le togomo te kai.”
\v 32 Ayo kurki pate aromo lerambo aa begeshe be kai, ayo kang arsaza ne, nangka ana otare ka emande zauze emande epeng aa nyimia ee bo.
\v 33 Ka yo eke emande epeng o ara ore o kai, aa emande ee bo o ara oguri kai.
\p 
\v 34 Awerenamea, Ogomo ya bekaa andaaka yo ara ore owai, ‘Deya na, ying ka Ate ang a eke taara azaa oying, emba na togomo teeka Ashili a eke ying ka o rabo obora lerambo.’
\v 35 Oo bena ma kone ekomo, na e nyang epaolya. Ma kone lewe, na e nyang manyi nang se. Ma deya legeng, na e nyang ara ojǝpi akwilǝ ying.
\v 36 Ma ye ngmata, na e ambang madibi. Ma kono na e sooleng. A pateng akwilǝ andaleme, na e de aa laka ong.
\p 
\v 37 “Awerenamea andaa sangsang a begeshe be Ashili yo kabare ko bekaana, ‘Ateokora, ngmǝyamea te lakau ka ekomo na te nyau epaolya, na ngmǝyamea te lakau a kona lewe na te nyau manyi ma o sa?’
\v 38 Kangza ngmǝyamea te lakau ogeng na te nyau ara ujǝpi, koona ngmǝyamea te lakau ngmata nate ambau madibi?
\v 39 Ngmǝyamea te lakau a ota zake ne, koona aa pate akwilǝ andaleme, na te de aa laka o?
\p 
\v 40 “Ogomo ome yo kabare nee na, ‘Ang dongdong bele oying, pate epa e erere eka e eza arone ang ana, ka o kala aa be baate, aa ee ezangngha.’
\p 
\v 41 A werenamea wayo bekaa andaaka ne yo o ara oguri na, ‘Arnanna kaa mi, andaamea neya enda ogǝzǝ Ashili, lyǝ na ola ooka wata lambu ne kaa babare ogomo obere oburu kaa atoma wai.’
\v 42 Ka ma kona ekomo, eta e nyang epaolya ne. Ma kona lewe, eta e nyang manyi ma o sa ne.
\v 43 Ma ya legeng, eta e nyang ara ujǝpi ne. Ma ye ngmata, na eta ambang madibi ne. Ma kono, a pateng akwilǝ andaleme, na eta e balang ne.
\p 
\v 44 “Awerenamea neema neyo kabare na, ‘Ateokora, ngmǝyamea te lakau ka ekomo, koona ka lewe, na aa legeng, na ngmata, koona oya kono, koona oyaa akwilǝ andaleme, na teta balau ne?’
\p 
\v 45 “Wayo kabare nee na, ‘Ang dongdong bele oying, nangka eta e eze ka yende aa nyimi andaa batebate aana nyimi ying ne, mia eta e ezanne.’
\p 
\v 46 “Andaana ya lyǝ ozitǝ o dera omaro, aa andaa sangsang a begeshe be Ashili neya yo lyǝ a ebeene o dera o maro.”\x - \xo 25:46 \xt Dan 12:2.\x*
\c 26
\s1 O gwaara kpwai o wongha Yeso
\r (Mar 14:12; Luk 22:1-2; Yoh 11:45-53)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka Yeso ka mare o beya apate epaname, na ka bekaa atoma akai ana,
\v 2 “Erose na Ozǝnggǝ Ocakate tata kaa amora aleerea, ayo kang nya Kena ka oromo ka gendare kai a uti.”
\p 
\v 3 Na andaamoole magame ma Akwilǝ Ashili kaa andaano aromo ne gwarnang akwilǝ ondo ogong o magame ma Akwilǝ Ashili, ka aa rare wai na Kayafa.
\v 4 Na ne tere nangka neya moke a Yeso asuk ka ne wong kai.
\v 5 Aa ne bekaana, ‘‘Wato gwara awere ozǝnggǝ me ne, adorana tana aromo ne ara o kara ne.”
\s1 A kare Yeso manau ma o waze o lebo aa Betanya
\r (Mar 14:3-9; Luk 7:37-38; Yoh 12:1-8)
\p 
\v 6 Aa, Yeso kaya apeng a Betanya akwilǝ Siman, ondooka samba waye ka legangca,
\v 7 na kandaaye ka yende de ara Yeso ka kagwi ka a eze kai kaa acale onis aa ka pena ka manau ma owaze olebo ma emate ecake. Awere aaka kaya lya epaolya naka kare kai manau mame ukpwei.
\p 
\v 8 Nangka atoma kai ne laka nyimi, na ne kone oburǝ aane bekaa tukpwei tone na, “Onna ocara emate wai!”
\v 9 “Ayya aa lisǝ manau maana, aa yo ci emate acake ka nya ana odera.”
\p 
\v 10 Aa nangka Yeso ka rose epa eka neya beyame, na ka bekaa nee na, “Eyaka eya gera kandaye kaana? Enna, epa ererea kaya eza ong.
\v 11 Ana o dera neye legwa kaa ying koonang were, aa koonag werea anto ya legwa kaa ying ne.
\v 12 Okare manau maana aa kaa ezang, kaya goro ongngha o matasakong mang.
\v 13 Ang dongdong ya baale oying, pate ara aka ayo baala orooka olebo ona aa lerambo aa pate, ayo beya orooka azaa epa eeka kandaye kaana kaya ka rintǝ ka kai.”
\s1 Yahuda wa kabare awa nya Yeso
\r (Mar 14:10-11; Luk 22:3-6)
\p 
\v 14 Na ondo a nyimi atoma Yeso lekuri, ka a beya wai ana Yahuda Iskariyoti, wa ale andaamoole magame ma Akwilǝ Ashili,
\v 15 na wa pirkǝ nee na, “Eya nya ong eya maa nya ying kai?” Na ne bale o azorpa etuuru taaro, nane nya wai o azorpo etuuru taaro.
\v 16 O era awere namea wa gere orona ooka wayo nya Yeso.
\s1 Yeso ka lye epaolya Ozǝngǝ Ocakate kaa atoma kai
\r (Mar 14:12-21; Luk 22:7-14; 21-23; Yoh 13:21-30)
\p 
\v 17 Nangka lengme le o bora le Ozǝnggǝ Oborode Odera o Yisti, na atoma Yeso de nane pirkǝ kai na, “Aruwǝ me oya yeme a te babarau ara olya epaolya ozǝnggǝ ocakate me?”
\p 
\v 18 Na Yeso kabare nee na, “Ale na aa nyimi peng ara oromo yende ka e bekaa wai na, ‘Ondo obaala wa bekaana awere a kai a amara, kayo lya epaolya Ozǝnggǝ Ocakate a akwilǝ au kaa atoma a kai.’ ”
\v 19 Na atoma me ne eze akap nangka Yeso ka ote ne, nane kang goro ekeeya azaa Ozǝnggǝ Ocakate me.
\p 
\v 20 Nangka ulyǝlu waye, na Yeso cikǝ a lya epaolya ka atoma kai betuuru ke leere.
\v 21 Neya nyimia olya epaolya, naka bekaana, “Ang dongdong bele oying, ondo aa nyimi oying wayo naying.”
\p 
\v 22 Na anyong ane caro ajǝng, na komana one bore o pirǝ o kai ayeyende, aane beyaa na, “Anyya, mia na, Ateokora?”
\p 
\v 23 Na Yeso kabare na, “Ondooka waya pasa taara oso yende kaa mi, waiya ya nayi ong.
\v 24 Kena ka Oromo kayo gbwǝ nangka a wele angmǝ Ashili azaa kai. Pate ka nyimi, ondooka waya nayi Kena ka Oromo wa lyǝ udi! Wa kala o bena mara taa a ngmengha wai ne.”
\p 
\v 25 Na Yahuda ka wa ya nayi kai pirkǝ na, “Ondo obaala, mia na,?’’ Na Yeso kabare wai na, “Bo ma baa beka.”
\s1 Olya epaolya Ateokora
\r (Mar 14:22-26; Luk 22:14-20; 1 Kor 11:23-25)
\p 
\v 26 Neya za olya epaolya, na Yeso jeka oborode, na ka wore okona oleba Ashili, aa ka nyeskare, na ka nya atoma akai, aa ka bekaana “Emba, ka e lya. Leena lepung lengha le.”
\p 
\v 27 Na ka jeke kaso ka manyi ma o inabi. Malo owore okona oleba Ashili, na ka nya ne aka bekaana, “Sa na aa pate oying.
\v 28 Obena manna manyau mangngha mai, ma owore opanza okabare otono osau, ka ayo oka aza aromo a cake, ka opisǝ madinǝ mane.
\v 29 Eyang baala oying, anta kang sa manyi ma o inabi na ne, seena lengme lenname ka teyo sa ma yende ma sau ka ying a togomo te Ate ang.”
\p 
\v 30 Nangka Yeso kaa atoma kai ne beye leera, nane suri, aane ale a oyara o mati ma o Zaitun.
\s1 Biturusu yo sangga orosa o Yeso
\r (Mar 14:27-31; Luk 22:31-34; Yoh 13:36-38)
\p 
\v 31 Na Yeso bekaane na, “Pate oying eyo songha e bayang aa lelyaare leena, azaa epaeka eyo manang, nangka a wele na,
\q1 “‘Eyang taba ondo otare ka enama,
\q2 legwa le emande epeng me yo bacakarna.’
\p 
\v 32 Aa malo ara ong malo o gbwǝ, eyang kaana ying a ale a makeke ma Galili.”
\p 
\v 33 Biturusu wa bekaa Yeso, “Pate one ne songha azaa epa eeka eyo manau, mi antang tukǝ songha ne.”
\p 
\v 34 Na Yeso beka wai na, “Ang dongdong bele o, aa lelyaare leena, zongka orunǝ sene, oyo sangga orosa ong ka taaro.”
\p 
\v 35 Na Biturusu bekaa kai na, “Ayaa wongha ong, anto sangga orosa o ne.” Nyimia apate odangare atoma kai ne beke.
\s1 Yeso ka beye angmǝ kaa Ashili aa Gasamani
\r (Mar 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46)
\p 
\v 36 Malo o nyimia, Yeso kaa atoma kai ne alea ara kaa beya ai na Gasamani. Ara aaka a pilizi ayana o zaitun ne. Naka bekaa atoma kai, “Cikǝ na arakaana, eyang alea sanini kang beye angmǝ kaa Ashili.”
\v 37 Na ka ale ka Biturusu, a ayana Zebadi aleere, Yakubu kaa Yohana, naka bore o caro anyong kaa o kona o burǝ maleu.
\v 38 Aaka kang bekaa nee na, “O caro a nyong ka waya lenyong leng wa era aa wa wongngeng. Cikǝna arakaana ee eza le'enda ka mi.”
\p 
\v 39 Nangka ka lya izi a baate, na ka taru ka mayinu a deze, aa ka beye angmǝ kaa Ashili na, “Ate ang, nyimi waayo ya, saareng kaso ka ozitǝ kaana. Pate ka nyimi sang, epa eeka eyang yeme me eya ato yeme ne, soona epa eeka bo oya yeme me.”
\p 
\v 40 Ka o kurǝ ara atoma akai, naka mana ne aa aneya malau, na ka bekaa Biturusu na, “E era eta ama le'enda kaa mi, na awere yende ne na?
\v 41 Cikǝ na aa le'enda, ee kang beya na angmǝ kaa Ashili adorana tana e rǝzi aa nyimi okedeya ne. Dongdong lenyong lee kabare, aa lepung kangza leya nyana.”
\p 
\v 42 Naka kuri o leere, na ka beye angmǝ kaa Ashili aaka bekaana, “Ate ang, ozitǝ ona waata kala ne seeka ma se wai, a baya aa eze apa eeka bo oya yeme me.”
\p 
\v 43 Nangka ka kang kurǝ, aa ka kang mana ne a malau, azaa obena ayizi ane a pena ka malau.
\v 44 Naka sukǝ o baya one, na ka kuri aa beya angmǝ kaa Ashili o taaro, na ka tikǝri angmǝ aaka ka be samba.
\p 
\v 45 Na ka kuri ara atoma kai, aaka bekaa nee na, “Etata a malau nanna, eeya teseke na?” Laka na, awere aya, ka ayo nya Kena ka Oromo a taara te ana madinǝ.
\v 46 Erana ka ale. Laka na, ondo nya ong awaana, wa dukǝ.”
\s1 A meke Yeso
\r (Mar 14:40-43; Luk 22:47-53; Yoh 18:3-12)
\p 
\v 47 Zongka ka pate o ngmǝ, na Yahuda, oyende a nyimia atoma betuuru kaa leere name, dukǝ ka aromo a cake, ka masagali, ka sebenda. Andaamoole magame ma Akwilǝ Ashilia kaa andaano aromoa ne tongha ne.
\v 48 Aa ondo o nayi okai wa samba o wore one obena, “Kondo kamea ma beya kai oko ang gambare kai, kaiya karomo kame. Moke na kai.”
\v 49 Ka o dǝkǝ wai na wa paka a Yeso, aa wa bekaana, “Oya cammo na, Ondobaala!” Aa wa beye kai oko ka o gambare.
\p 
\v 50 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Oja ong, eza epa eka e deya ka bo.”
\p Na aromo de na ne meke Yeso, nane monte kai.
\v 51 Ka o laka nyimi, na ondo a nyimi andaaka Yeso kaye legwa ka ne sǝǝrǝ osagali na wa lope oto o ozara andoo ogong ona magame ma Ashili.
\p 
\v 52 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Kuriyǝ osagali o a nyimi opano wai. Pate ondooka wa lopa osagali, osagali yo wongha wai.
\v 53 Eya gonta na anta ka o bare kang gera okangkama Ate ang, kangza aa saseya a kawa turki legwa le atoma Ashili o dera lepung, kane kala legwa le ana o tesa geza a moole be tuuru ka leere sang?
\v 54 Na, a wiinia a ngmǝ Ashili itǝ maganggang aaka a wele, ka aa beyaa na dongdong nyimi mea yo ya?
\p 
\v 55 Awere name, na Yeso beka a aromo me na, “E surǝa ka masagali ka sebenda ka e mokeng na ondo o tǝǝru a aromo na? Koonang lengme ang ciisǝ a akwilǝ Ashili ang baaleze na eta mekeng ne.
\v 56 Aa pate a eze nyimia adorana a panza epa eka ana o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili ne wela.”
\p Ka o kona nyimi na pat atoma kai ne song aane baya kai.
\s1 Yeso a begeshe bena anaateandaasau
\r (Mar 14:53-65; Luk 22:54-55,63-71; Yoh 18:13-14; 19-24)
\p 
\v 57 Na andaaka ne moke Yeso ale ka kai a Keyafa, ondoo gong ana magame ma Ashili, ara aka ana baala a ngmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa kaa andaano ne kurkǝnǝng ne.
\v 58 Na Biturusu tarze kai aa macangcang aa alea nyimi akora ondoo ogong magame ma Ashili. Nangka wa lyǝ nawa cikǝ kaa ana le'enda, ka wa laka nangka ayo maare.
\p 
\v 59 Na andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa anatendaasau, pate one nane gere angmǝ majǝkǝri kaa ayo eza Yeso adorana ne cǝ orona o wongha kai.
\v 60 Pate kaa nyimi na ne ta cǝ ne, o bekaana aromo a cake ne ya beya majǝkǝri azaa kai. Malo me na aromo leere surǝ,
\v 61 ne bekaa na, “Karomo oona wa bekaana, ‘Wa era wa oke akwilǝ Ashili ana, aa wa sowa ai a nyimi tomore te taaro.’ ”
\p 
\v 62 Na ondo gong magame ma Ashili ere aa itǝ na wa bekana, “Ota ke epa o beka ne na? Epa ena aa neya beyaa na ba beke pa?”
\v 63 Na Yeso sokong kome. Na ondo o gong magame ma Ashili beka a kai na, “Ma gwarau ka Ashili aka ya ka ebeene, bele ro, ‘Boa Almasipu, Kena ka Ashili.”
\p 
\v 64 Na Yeso bekaa wai na, “Nangka ba beka. Aa eyang bele ying, ba ale a izi, eya laka Kena ka Oromo a cikǝ o ara oree Ondo Keeya, aa ka kang deya aza mawere.”
\p 
\v 65 Na ondo o gong magame ma Ashili daara madibi ma wai azaa o caro a nyong, aa wa bekaana, “Ka sopa! Eya teya gerame kangza? Ee kona o sopa ooka kaya.
\p 
\v 66 Eya madoola maying?
\p Nane kabare na, “Ka gwara a wong kai.”
\p 
\v 67 Nane karze kai mawo a mainu, aa ne ola kai, ana ondo kangza nane kpweze kai to maare.
\p 
\v 68 Aane beya ana, “Bele ro epa eka ayo eza aa izi, boa baa ya Almasipu. Mana wa olau?”
\s1 Biturusu wa sangga orosa o Yeso
\r (Mar 14:66-72; Luk 22:56-62; Yoh 18:15-18,25-27)
\p 
\v 69 Aa Biturusu ya cikǝ o yanga a tatara akwilǝ ogomo, na ka kazara kagala de naka zundǝ wai, aa ka bekaana wai na, “Bo kangza oya legwa ka Yeso ka o Galili!”
\p 
\v 70 Na Biturusu wa sangga a begeshe bene apate, aa wa bekaana, “Mi anta rose epa eka oya beya me ne.”
\p 
\v 71 Nangka wa surǝ aa tatara akwilǝ ogomo, na kazara ka ai yende kangza laka wai, na ka beka andaaka ne ya itǝ arame na, “Oromo na waye legwa ka Yeso ka Nazarat!”
\p 
\v 72 Na wa kang sangga ka otongzo na, “Anta rosa oromo name ne.”
\p 
\v 73 Ka o rabo a baate, na andaaka neya itǝ arame de ane bekaa Biturusu na, “Ma shango tarenene, bo ma oya nyimi one. Obelo angmǝ au, aa pǝro.”
\p 
\v 74 Na wa bora angmǝ aburu aza ukpwei wai, aa wa tongzo, aa wa beyaana, “Anta rosa oromo me ne!”
\p Awerename na urunǝ sene.
\v 75 Na Biturusu rintǝ angmǝ a Yeso na, “Zongka orunǝ sene, oyo sangga orosa ong ka taaro.” Na wa surǝ o yanga na wa ruzii a maleo.
\c 27
\s1 Yeso aa begeshe be ogomo Bilatus
\r (Mar 15:1; Luk 23:1-2; Yoh 18:28-32)
\p 
\v 1 Nangka ara asane, na pate andaamoole magame Ashili kaa andaano aromo gwaara angmǝ azaa nangka neya wongha Yeso.
\p 
\v 2 Nane tere kai, aane ale ka kai aa begeshe be Ogomo Bilatus.
\s1 Ogbwǝ o Yahuda
\r (Ogat 1:18-20)
\p 
\v 3 Awere aka Yahuda ooka wa nayi kai wa laka aa core Yeso angmǝ wongha, na wa kone oburǝ, nawa kuri ara andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa andaano, nawa kuriyǝ ne ma azorpa tuuru taaro name.
\v 4 Awa bekaana, “Ma ya madinǝ ka ma nya ondooka wata tambo ne ka wongha kai.”
\p Nane bekaana, “Eya manyi maro? Onna a owa wai.”
\p 
\v 5 Na Yahuda me bacakare o azorpa me a akwilǝ Ashili, na wa suri, na wa ale aa wa ye lesara.
\p 
\v 6 Azaa nyimi na andaamoole magame Ashili ne shende emate me aa ne bekaana, “Wata gwara aa eke emate eena e a lebengga le akwilǝ Ashili ne, obena emate me e manyau e.”
\v 7 Azaa nyimi na ne nya tukpwei madoola na, ne embe adeze a ondo sowa madaka ka emate me ka a itǝ adeze o taasa a ageng.
\v 8 Nyimia wa ote, a deya o ngmeengme a rareze arame na ugiishi manyau.
\v 9 Azaa nyimia a panza angmǝ a Ondo o beya angmǝ ka mawo ma Ashili Irimiya ka wa beke na, “Ne jeke emate tuuru taaro, emate eeka aromo a Isrela ne kabare na are azaa kai naname,\x - \xo 27:9 \xt Zak 11:12-13.\x*
\v 10 nane embe adeze ondo o sooza madaka ka e, nangka Ateokora ka oteng.”
\s1 Bilatus wa eze Yeso be pirǝ
\r (Mar 15:2-5; Luk 23:3-5; Yoh 18:33-38)
\p 
\v 11 Na Yeso itǝ a begeshe be ondo togomo, na ondo togomo teme kang pirkǝ kai na, “Boo na, boa Ogomo maYahuda na?”
\p Yeso ka kabare na, “Nangka baa beka.”
\p 
\v 12 Nangka ne andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa andaano ne beye kai majǝkǝri, naka ta beke eyapa ne.
\v 13 Na Bilatus bekaa akai na, “Ota ba kona e pate epa eena ane beyau majǝkǝri azame ne?”
\v 14 Na Yeso ta ka kabare na be pirǝ be yende ne, na nyimi tere ogomo ukpwei aa bote.
\s1 A core Yeso o gǝǝzǝ o gbwǝ
\r (Mar 15:6-15; Luk 23:13-25; Yoh 18:39-19:16)
\p 
\v 15 Koonang awere Ozǝnggǝ Ocakate, ondo togomo wa mena aa peere oromo yende aa nyimia andaaka a pate a akwilǝ andaleme, ooka aromo ne zaka.
\v 16 Awere name, ondo zene a akwilǝ andaleme ka a rose wai ka ogirǝ, ka a beya wai na Barabas.
\v 17 Nangka maYahuda ne kurkǝnǝng, na Bilatus pirkǝ nee na, “Mana eya yeme ang pere ying wai? Barabas naa, na Yeso kamea arareze kai na Almasipu?”
\v 18 Obena wa rose na le'ero le ote nane turki Yeso awai.
\p 
\v 19 Bangka nyimi kangza, awere aka wa ya cikǝ a ledǝndǝ le cora angmǝ, ondaye wai wa tong na abele wai na, “Karomo kana ta kaa ya eyapa ne. Sǝǝrǝ taara to orooka karomo kaana obena ma zitǝ a tolau kaya kai.”
\p 
\v 20 Andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa andaano ne tarze aromo aa ne baale ne na ne zaka Barabas ka ne cǝ kane wong Yeso.
\p 
\v 21 Na ogomo me kang pirkǝ aromo me na, “A nyimi aromo leere aana, mana eya yeme ang pere ying wai?”
\p Na ne bekaana, “Barabas.”
\p 
\v 22 Na Bilatus bekaa na, “Na ang wiinia ka Yeso ka rareze kai na Almasipu?”
\p Na pate one kabare na “A gendare kai a uti!”
\p 
\v 23 Na Bilatus pirkǝ ne, “Azaa eya? Ombela araaburu ka eza?” Na ne waale o ara angmelo na, “A gendare kai a uti.”
\p 
\v 24 Nangka Bilatus wa laka wa era wata ya eyapa ne, kangza a nyong aromo ya waale o caro, na wa mangka manyi na wa kwizǝ taara tewai aa aromo ya gonta, aa wa bekaana, “Mi, ma kwizǝ a taara teng aa manyau ma karomo ka o dera madinǝ kaana. Onna zitǝ oying wai.”\x - \xo 27:24 \xt Otik 21:6-9.\x*
\p 
\v 25 Na pate aromo me kabare na, “Baya ozitǝ ome itǝ azaa aro kaa ayana aro.”
\p 
\v 26 Awere namea wa pere ne Barabas. Malo oka wa ote na ole Yeso, aa wa nayi kai ka gendare.
\s1 Ana o tesa a geza a moole ne zeele Yeso
\r (Mar 15:16-20; Yoh 19:2-3)
\p 
\v 27 Na ana otesa ageza aa moole o ogomo ale ka Yeso a akwilǝ togomo, nane kurki pate legwa le ana otesa ageza a moole o makeke mame azaa kai.
\v 28 Na ne lope madibi maaka maya lepung le kai, aa ne amba kai odibi o ganggo o togomo.
\v 29 Na ne pi betageya be ekana, aa ne amba kai ukpwei, aa ne nya kai lebenda le yende o ara ore o kai, na ne kang tungunu a begeshe be kai aa ne zeele kai, aa ne beyaana kai na, “Ashili waloo ne, Ogomo maYahuda!”
\v 30 Aa ne karze kai mawo, nane jeke lebenda lenname nane ola kai kaa le o ukpwei.
\v 31 Nangka ne mare o zeela kai, nane lope kai odibi o togomo te me, aa kuriyǝ kai madibi maaka maya kai a lepung, nane ale ka kai ka ne gendare uti.
\s1 A gendare Yeso
\r (Mar 15:21-32; Luk 23:26-43; Yoh 19:17-27)
\p 
\v 32 Ne ya teweno naname, nane gwarnang ka Saminu, oromo a Siyarin. Waya ne ote nawa ana uti o gendare a Yeso.
\v 33 Nangka ne dukǝ ara aka arareze ai na Golgota, araaka a rose ai na ara o cako ukpwei,
\v 34 nane nya kai manyi ma inabi maaka a sakale ka ka o ngmangmang ka ka se. Nangka ka lembe ka leleng, naka nyana o sa me.\x - \xo 27:34 \xt Sel 69:21.\x*
\v 35 Malo o gendare a Yeso, nane eze o zawa azaa madibi ma kai kane laka mana yo jeka odibi me.\x - \xo 27:35 \xt Sel 22:18.\x*
\v 36 Malo nyimi nane cikǝ arame aa le'enda le kai.
\v 37 A aza uti me, aza kaa ukpwei o kai, nane wele aa kati ka patarake ka yende na, “KANNAA YESO, OGOMO MAYAHUDA.”
\v 38 Nane kang gendare kai legwa kaa akǝri o tǝǝru aromo a leere, oyende o ara ore, aa o yende o ara uguri kai.
\v 39 Ana o kaale ne ne zeele kai, aa ne zuu ukpwei,
\v 40 aa ne beyaana, “Bo ka baa bekaana, ba era o oka akwilǝ Ashili, oo kang sowa ai a nyimi amora taaro, na boza o ukpwei o! Na bo Kena ka Ashili baaza, jipi a uti ogendare me!”
\v 41 Nyimia kangza andaamoole magame ma Ashili ka ana o baala angmǝ aaka Ashili a nya Mosa ka andaano aromo ne zeele kai, aa ne beyaana,
\v 42 “Ka boza ana ondo, aa ka girǝ o boza ukpwei kai. Kai ya Ogomo Isrela sang? Kaa jipi a uti ogendare na nannameena, awere namea te yo kabare ka kai.
\v 43 Ka eke lenyong a Ashili, baya a Ashili me boza kai nanname, aaya yeme a kai, obena ka bekaana kai Kena ka Ashilia kai.”\x - \xo 27:43 \xt Sel 22:9.\x*
\v 44 Pate a akǝri o tǝǝru a aromo ka a gendare ne ka Yeso ne beya akai angmǝ a aburu.
\s1 Ogbwǝ o Yeso
\r (Mar 15:33-41; Luk 23:44-49; Yoh 19:28-30)
\p 
\v 45 Na maring meke pate makeke mame aa era o tera ongme aa dukǝ beru be o taaro ulyǝlu.
\v 46 Nangka ongme wa amara ka otaru, na Yeso ara lengmelo ajǝng, na ka bekaana, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabatani?” Obena, “Ashili ang, Ashili ang, eyaaka ba nyang o malo?”\x - \xo 27:46 \xt Sel 22:1.\x*
\p 
\v 47 Aromo aa ka neya itǝ a ting arame ne kone nyimi na ne bekaana, “Karomo kaana kaya orara Ileya!”
\p 
\v 48 Na ondo a nyimi one song nawa jeke lesuni nawa tǝkǝzǝ a manyi ma marara, nawa ote a lebenda, aa wa nayi Yeso na ka se.\x - \xo 27:48 \xt Sel 69:21.\x*
\v 49 Azaa nyimi odangare me bekaana, “Bayana te laka na Ileya yo deya kawa boza kai.”
\p 
\v 50 Na Yeso kang ara lengmelo a jǝng, aa ka pere ebeene e kai.
\p 
\v 51 Nyimia oyambati ka waya a akwilǝ Ashili wa daro a tera madǝkǝni ma leere, o era obora aaza a jǝpi dizi. Na adeze a zukǝru, aa acale poso.
\v 52 A pǝǝri macao, andaaka ne gbwizǝ kaa ne ye ka boome be Ashili, ne ere ka ebeene,
\v 53 aa komana one susi a ocao o wai. Malo o era Yeso, nane lyǝ a nyimi apeng aa sangsang, aromo acake ne laka ne.
\p 
\v 54 Awere aka ondo gong ana otesa geza o Roma, kaa andaaka neya legwa aa enda Yeso ne laka adeze a zukǝrnu kaa pate epa eka ne laka, na pate one kone boome maleo, aa ne bekaana, “Kanna dongdong Kena ka Ashilia kai!”
\p 
\v 55 Andaye yende acake ka ne tare Yeso aa surǝ aa Galili aane kangkama kai, ne itǝ aa macang a gontaka pate epa eka eya ale.
\v 56 Aa nyimi one neye, Mariya ka o Magadala, kaa Mariya iini na Yakubu ka Yusupu, aa iini ayana Zabadi kangza.
\s1 O taasa o Yeso
\r (Mar 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Yoh 19:38-42)
\p 
\v 57 Nangka o ulyǝlu waye, na Yusupu, oromo o Arimatiya ka waya ka o cǝ, wai kangza ondo o tare Yeso waze.
\v 58 Nawa ale aa Bilatus nawa bose na nya wai lepung le Yeso. Na Bilatus ote na nya wai.
\v 59 Yusupu wa jeke lepung leme, nawa pate le ka betu,
\v 60 aa wa lyǝǝrǝ lepung leme a nyimi ocau osau oka wa she eke ukpwei wai ka wa kau a lecale. Nawa turki lecale legong leyende nawa pate begmǝ be ocau me, aa wa ale.
\v 61 Mariya ka o Magadala, kaa Mariya kayende, ne ya zaa ocikǝ a izi ocau me.
\s1 Ana le'enda ocau
\p 
\v 62 Ka o sana ara, malo Lengme le Ogoro, na andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa maParisa gwarnang a begeshe be Bilatus,
\v 63 nane bekaana, “Ogomo, te rintǝ nangka karomo kaaname ka o rendaza aa ka tata a bengma ka beeze na malo tomore to taaro kayo era ka ebeene.
\v 64 Azaa nyimi, ote ka eza le'enda ocau me maleo aa dukǝ tomore te taaro, tana atoma akai de kane kpwi ekeze kai aa ne bekaa aromo na ka era malo ogbwǝ ne. Orenda o maare wayo kala obora o buru.”
\p 
\v 65 Na Bilatus bekaa nee na, “Besa na ana otesa geza aa moole, ka e ale kaa e eze le'enda nangka wa gwara.”
\v 66 Nane ale nane ende ocau ome, aa ne ote bewela becapa be ogomo, aa ne baya ana otesa geza me aa le'enda.
\c 28
\s1 O era o Yeso a nyimi ocau
\r (Mar 16:1-8; Luk 24:1-12; Yoh 20:1-10)
\p 
\v 1 Malo Lengme le Oteseke lee kala, aa lelere lengme le obora, na Mariya ka o Magadala, kaa Mariya kayende, ne ale a olaka ocau me.
\p 
\v 2 Na adeze zukǝrnu a jǝng o otoma Ashili o dera lepung wa sura a zaa shili nawa kinkǝri o cale me aa wa cikǝ aaza me.
\v 3 Waya masanto na o malmi, aa madibi ma wai maya apeng aa pauwo na adoka.
\v 4 Nangka ana le'enda ne laka wai, na boome moke ne maleo, nane kerkeze aa ne tǝǝru aa deze naa nee gbwizǝ.
\p 
\v 5 Aa otoma Ashili o dera lepung leme wa bekaa andaaye me na, “Tana e kona boome ne, ang rose obena Yeso kamea a gendare kaya eya gerame.
\v 6 Kata rene ne. Ka era nangka ka beke. Deyana ke laka ara aka a eke kai.
\v 7 Alena a saseya ka e bekaa otoma akai na, obena ka era malo ogbwǝ. Akaname aa ka yo kang kaana oying o ale a makeke ma Galili. Aa sanamea eyo laka kai! Epa eeka ma deya aa bele oying naname.”
\p 
\v 8 Nane baya ocau ome a kwarte a nyimi boome, ka okona oleba aa cake, nane song nane bele atoma akai oroka ome.
\v 9 Na Yeso ka o upkwai kai gwarnang ka ne, naka bekaa nee na, “O cikǝ o cammo itǝ ka ying!” Nane paka aa ma'amo aa ne garme tobona te kai, nane girwǝ a begeshe be kai.
\v 10 Na Yeso bekaane na, “Tane kona boome ne, alena ka e bekaa arone ang, ane ale aa makeke ma Galili, asanamea ne yo lakang.”
\s1 Orooka ooka ana o enda ocau ne de ne
\p 
\v 11 Nangka andaaye me neya nyimi teweno, na ana ondo aa nyimi ana o enda ocau me, nane bele andaamoole ana magame ma Ashili orooka o pate epa eka ee ale.
\v 12 Na andaamoole magame ma Ashili kaa andaano ne kurkǝnǝng, nane tere madoola ma yende, nane nya ana otesa geza aa moole me emate aa cak,
\v 13 aa ne bekaane na, “Bele na aromo na, atoma kai ya ne deya aa lelyaare aa teya malau nane kpwi kai.
\v 14 Orooka ona wa dukǝ teto te ogomo, teyo nya wai angmǝ te kang itǝ ka ying aa nyimia pate o zitǝ.”
\v 15 Nane embe emate me, nane ye epa eka a bekaa nee na ne eze. Orooka ona wa ale kurǝwa a maYahuda aa deya o ngmeengme.
\s1 Ogole ka Yeso ka nya atoma kai
\r (Mar 16:14-18; Luk 24:36-49; Yoh 20:19-23)
\p 
\v 16 Na atoma akai be tuuru kaa leyende name ale a makeke ma Galili, a oyara ooka Yeso ka bekaa ne na ne gwarnang arame.
\v 17 Nangka ne laka kai, na ne girwǝ aa ne sabe kai, aa na ondo ne dambaraza.
\v 18 Na Yeso paka na ka bekaa nee na, “A nyang pate obare azaa shili ka adeze.”
\v 19 Azaa nyimi, ale na ka e baale pate aromo lerambo ka ne tareng, e eza ne batisma a nyimi le ze Ate, ka Kena, ka Obere o Ashili,
\v 20 e baala ne kane tare pate epaeka ma ote ying. Mi naana kangza ang ye legwa ka ying aa ale ka ying o omaare lerambo.
